(2074, 'Alarum', 'Michael Polish', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Two married spies caught in the crosshairs of an international intelligence network will stop at nothing to obtain a critical asset. Joe and Lara are agents living off the grid whose quiet retreat at a winter resort is blown to shreds when members of the old guard suspect the two may have joined an elite team of rogue spies, known as Alarum.', 95, 'Scott Eastwood, Sylvester Stallone, Willa Fitzgerald, Mike Colter, D.W. Moffett', '2025-01-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v313aUGmMNj6yNveaiQXysBmjVS.jpg', '', '', '', 5.79, 0, 0),
(2075, 'The Gardener', 'David Charhon', 'Action, Comedy', 'Belgium, France', 'fr', 'Every year the Prime Minister has a list of all kinds of troublemakers eliminated in the name of the famous Reason of State. Serge Shuster, Special Adviser to the President of the Republic, finds himself on this list, better known as the Matignon List.  Condemned to certain death and at the heart of an implacable plot and a state secret that also put his family in danger, Serge, his wife and children have only one hope left - their gardener, Léo, who hates it when « slugs » invade his garden... Especially those that want to kill innocent families.', 110, 'Jean-Claude Van Damme, Michaël Youn, Nawell Madani, Carla Poquin, Jérôme Le Banner', '2025-01-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5T9WR7vIOnHm6xhVt5zBuPbBgt1.jpg', '', '', '', 6.291, 0, 0),
(2076, 'Squad 36', 'Olivier Marchal', 'Action, Crime, Drama, Thriller', 'France', 'fr', 'Forced out of his elite unit, a troubled cop launches his own rogue investigation when mysterious killings claim the lives of his former colleagues.', 124, 'Victor Belmondo, Tewfik Jallab, Soufiane Guerrab, Juliette Dol, Yvan Attal', '2025-02-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/AnDwpI8dY8iqJVUwVS5UotYAbB1.jpg', '', '', '', 6.484, 0, 0),
(2077, 'Love Hurts', 'Jonathan Eusebio', 'Action, Comedy, Romance', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A realtor is pulled back into the life he left behind after his former partner-in-crime resurfaces with an ominous message. With his crime-lord brother also on his trail, he must confront his past and the history he never fully buried.', 83, 'Ke Huy Quan, Ariana DeBose, Daniel Wu, Mustafa Shakir, Lio Tipton', '2025-02-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/skPPVeHoTTVVSJlb0Ib5vrqiuA4.jpg', 'Israeli Television Academy Awards', '', '', 5.906, 0, 0),
(2078, 'Mientras Cupido no está', 'Alejandro Aimetta', 'Comedy', 'Spain, Mexico', 'es', 'Mirtha Del Cañon is the owner of a million-dollar company. Her only son, Bartolo, is a mess, and to straighten him out, she decides to look for a woman for him, to achieve that, she organizes a casting to find the perfect daughter-in-law.', 0, 'Dolores Heredia, Vadhir Derbez, Antonia San Juan, Manuel Vega, Ana Lucía Domínguez', '2025-04-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/figjQxoiVMNuDJe5wl4nrgAJTDD.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2079, 'Dear David', 'Lucky Kuswandi', 'Drama, Romance, Fantasy', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'A secret fantasy blog might jeopardize the promising future of Laras, a talented student, when the blog is revealed to her entire school.', 118, 'Shenina Cinnamon, Emir Mahira, Caitlin North Lewis, Palestina Irtiza, Michael Olindo', '2023-02-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Ab1OedAN42deqjIkOu7X94nJwkG.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
(2080, 'Apocalypse Z: The Beginning of the End', 'Carles Torrens', 'Drama, Action, Horror', 'Spain', 'es', 'When a kind of rabies that transforms people into aggressive creatures spreads across the planet, Manel isolates himself at home with his cat, relying on his wits to survive; but soon they must go out in search of food, by land and by sea, dodging many dangers.', 119, 'Francisco Ortiz, José María Yázpik, Berta Vázquez, Iria del Río, Marta Poveda', '2024-10-04', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wIGJnIFQlESkC2rLpfA8EDHqk4g.jpg', '', '', '', 6.719, 0, 0),
(2081, 'Elevation', 'George Nolfi', 'Action, Science Fiction, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A single father and two women venture from the safety of their homes to face monstrous creatures to save the life of a young boy.', 91, 'Anthony Mackie, Morena Baccarin, Maddie Hasson, Danny Boyd Jr., Rachel Nicks', '2024-11-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tnfc0NJ3BzhJrGJhkkEd6MHBdq5.jpg', '', '', '', 6.488, 0, 0),
(2082, 'A Love Too Captivating', 'Desconocido', 'Romance, Animation', 'Japan', 'ja', 'Misuzu was branded a delinquent when a small incident left him isolated. But one day, he sees the top student, Kitahara, get surrounded by bullies and decides to help him out. That sparked Kitahara\'s interest in the lonely boy, but Misuzu pushes Kitahara away. \"If you get involved with me, you\'ll get ostracized by everyone else too.\" But it won\'t take long for Misuzu\'s resolve to falter...', 0, 'Chiaki Kobayashi, Takeo Otsuka', '2025-04-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zESBv0bTqtb4ICJ9oYn2HFec8JV.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2083, 'Heretic', 'Scott Beck', 'Horror, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Two young missionaries are forced to prove their faith when they knock on the wrong door and are greeted by a diabolical Mr. Reed, becoming ensnared in his deadly game of cat-and-mouse.', 111, 'Hugh Grant, Sophie Thatcher, Chloe East, Topher Grace, Elle Young', '2024-10-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fr96XzlzsONrQrGfdLMiwtQjott.jpg', '', '', '', 7.068, 0, 0),
(2084, 'El Vacío', 'Gustavo Graef-Marino', '', 'Chile', 'es', 'He, a famous filmmaker living off his past, decides to give romance a chance when he meets Her.What starts as a perfect love story is threatened by routine, unfulfilled expectations and the eternal desire to fill the void inside both of them.', 97, 'Francisco Reyes, Javiera Díaz de Valdés, Aída Caballero', '2023-06-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/woXQUmCl2VTQ2VdFdFx2vnFZVqn.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2085, 'The Assessment', 'Fleur Fortuné', 'Science Fiction, Drama, Thriller', 'Germany, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'In a climate change-ravaged world, a utopian society optimizes life, including parenthood assessments. A successful couple faces scrutiny by an evaluator over seven days to determine their fitness for childbearing.', 114, 'Elizabeth Olsen, Himesh Patel, Alicia Vikander, Minnie Driver, Indira Varma', '2025-03-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fTWki5Cl8OU3UjQiMcPIynR9QEV.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(2086, 'Ellie and the Monster Team', 'Jesper Møller', 'Animation, Family, Comedy', 'Canada, Germany', 'de', 'When a homeless little ghost knocks on the door to the eccentric residents of a Ghost Train on the lookout for a place to belong, she accidentally attracts the attention from the outside world and must team up with the motley crew of monsters on a crazy quest to save not only the future of the Ghost Train but also her only chance to finally have a family of her own.', 82, '', '2024-06-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xyNtoI1r9ydJRKFGS1SCbT9ying.jpg', '', '', '', 5.8, 0, 0),
(2087, 'Rabia', 'Mareike Engelhardt', 'Drama, Thriller', 'Germany, Belgium, France', 'fr', 'Driven by the promise of a new life, Jessica (19) and her best friend Laila left for Syria to join DAECH. But when they arrive, they find themselves locked up in a women’s house run by the authoritarian and charismatic Madame. When Jessica rebels, a game of domination and submission begins between her and the director. Between fascination and fear, Jessica will have to give up her humanity to survive within this system.', 95, 'Megan Northam, Lubna Azabal, Natacha Krief, Lena Lauzemis, Klara Wöedermann', '2024-11-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/h05EsRVWWrmLDlEsXhRIUWUSogH.jpg', '', '', '', 6.8, 0, 0),
(2088, 'The Last Supper', 'Mauro Borrelli', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In the days leading to betrayal, a gathering of disciples unravels into a web of secrets and hidden motives. As tensions simmer beneath the surface, trust is tested, and loyalty is questioned. The Last Supper becomes a night where nothing is as it seems, and every glance hides a deeper truth.', 114, 'Jamie Ward, James Oliver Wheatley, Charlie MacGechan, Nathalie Rapti Gomez, James Faulkner', '2025-03-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fulEdvN5u6mIpwig7HcBnYpkJEQ.jpg', 'Teddy Award', '', '', 7.2, 0, 0),
(2089, 'Fast X', 'Louis Leterrier', 'Action, Crime, Thriller, Adventure, Mystery', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they\'ve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who\'s fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything—and everyone—that Dom loves, forever.', 142, 'Vin Diesel, Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Ludacris, John Cena', '2023-05-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fiVW06jE7z9YnO4trhaMEdclSiC.jpg', '', '', '', 7.047, 0, 0),
(2090, 'Drop', 'Christopher Landon', 'Mystery, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Violet, a widowed mother on her first date in years, arrives at an upscale restaurant where she is relieved that her date, Henry, is more charming and handsome than she expected. But their chemistry begins to curdle as Violet begins being irritated and then terrorized by a series of anonymous drops to her phone.', 95, 'Meghann Fahy, Brandon Sklenar, Violett Beane, Jacob Robinson, Reed Diamond', '2025-04-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oK4FFNfFHQRyGc2pmo88zpiu5Gc.jpg', '', '', '', 7.262, 0, 0),
(2091, 'Jaat', 'Gopichand Malineni', 'Action, Drama', 'India', 'hi', 'After a ruffian accidentally ruins his meal, a traveler retorts violently and demands an apology, unintentionally finding himself in a web of violence, crime and corruption spun by a feared criminal.', 153, 'Sunny Deol, Randeep Hooda, Saiyami Kher, Regina Cassandra, Vineet Kumar Singh', '2025-04-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/guTflsCTgLNqTbpHTi9gJANk1Rf.jpg', '', '', '', 5, 0, 0),
(2092, 'Alien: Romulus', 'Fede Álvarez', 'Horror, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'While scavenging the deep ends of a derelict space station, a group of young space colonizers come face to face with the most terrifying life form in the universe.', 119, 'Cailee Spaeny, David Jonsson, Archie Renaux, Isabela Merced, Spike Fearn', '2024-08-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b33nnKl1GSFbao4l3fZDDqsMx0F.jpg', '', '', '', 7.2, 0, 0),
(2093, 'Opus', 'Mark Anthony Green', 'Horror, Mystery, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A young writer is invited to the remote compound of a legendary pop star who mysteriously disappeared thirty years ago. Surrounded by the star\'s cult of sycophants and intoxicated journalists, she finds herself in the middle of his twisted plan.', 104, 'Ayo Edebiri, John Malkovich, Juliette Lewis, Murray Bartlett, Melissa Chambers', '2025-03-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m0du9dsiOVeb0SgfqR8ZAEPRxww.jpg', 'Amadeus Austrian Music Awards, Grammy Award for Best Tropical Latin Album', '', '', 5.4, 0, 0),
(2094, 'Bad Boys: Ride or Die', 'Adil El Arbi', 'Action, Comedy, Crime, Thriller, Adventure', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After their late former Captain is framed, Lowrey and Burnett try to clear his name, only to end up on the run themselves.', 115, 'Will Smith, Martin Lawrence, Vanessa Hudgens, Alexander Ludwig, Paola Nuñez', '2024-06-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oGythE98MYleE6mZlGs5oBGkux1.jpg', '', '', '', 7.382, 0, 0),
(2095, 'The Travelling Dog', 'Magdalena Nieć', 'Family, Adventure', 'Poland', 'pl', 'The life of Zuzia, whose dad works on the railway, changes mas-sively when Lampo, an extraordinary travelling dog, joins the family. The remarkable shepherd dog, whose train trips are an internet sensation, immediately becomes the best friend of the girl suffering from a heart condition.', 95, 'Liliana Zajbert, Mateusz Damięcki, Monika Pikuła, Adam Woronowicz, Maksymilian Zieliński', '2023-08-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bC9K8ZWqSIG7sfe2XHzw73Sc8MC.jpg', '', '', '', 6.6, 0, 0),
(2096, 'The Electric State', 'Joe Russo', 'Science Fiction, Adventure, Action', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An orphaned teen hits the road with a mysterious robot to find her long-lost brother, teaming up with a smuggler and his wisecracking sidekick.', 125, 'Millie Bobby Brown, Chris Pratt, Ke Huy Quan, Jason Alexander, Woody Norman', '2025-03-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sI2NiMU8o65hmIMY0JI9CjJ0p7f.jpg', '', '', '', 6.58, 0, 0),
(2097, 'Devara : Part 1', 'Koratala Siva', 'Action, Drama', 'India', 'te', 'Devara, a fearless man from a coastal region, embarks on a perilous journey into the treacherous world of the sea to safeguard the lives of his people. Unbeknownst to him, his brother Bhaira is plotting a conspiracy against him. As events unfold, Devara passes on his legacy to his mild-mannered and timid son, Varada.', 175, 'N.T. Rama Rao Jr., Saif Ali Khan, Prakash Raj, Srikanth, Kalaiyarasan', '2024-09-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hdpYUidbB83AfemP369W7guOIlr.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(2098, 'Back in Action', 'Seth Gordon', 'Action, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Fifteen years after vanishing from the CIA to start a family, elite spies Matt and Emily jump back into the world of espionage when their cover is blown.', 114, 'Jamie Foxx, Cameron Diaz, McKenna Roberts, Rylan Jackson, Kyle Chandler', '2025-01-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3L3l6LsiLGHkTG4RFB2aBA6BttB.jpg', '', '', '', 6.46, 0, 0),
(2099, 'Presence', 'Steven Soderbergh', 'Horror, Drama, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A couple, Rebekah and Chris, and their children, Tyler and Chloe, move into a seemingly normal suburban home. When strange occurrences occur, they begin to believe that there is something else in the house with them. The presence is about to disrupt their lives in unimaginable ways.', 84, 'Callina Liang, Lucy Liu, Chris Sullivan, Eddy Maday, Julia Fox', '2025-01-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hZ8dTeBzigV5SVgwG1ikSROAFiS.jpg', '', 'Hugo Award for Best Novelette, Locus Award for Best Novelette', '', 5.974, 0, 0),
(2100, 'Terrifier 3', 'Damien Leone', 'Horror, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Five years after surviving Art the Clown\'s Halloween massacre, Sienna and Jonathan are still struggling to rebuild their shattered lives. As the holiday season approaches, they try to embrace the Christmas spirit and leave the horrors of the past behind. But just when they think they\'re safe, Art returns, determined to turn their holiday cheer into a new nightmare. The festive season quickly unravels as Art unleashes his twisted brand of terror, proving that no holiday is safe.', 125, 'Lauren LaVera, David Howard Thornton, Samantha Scaffidi, Elliott Fullam, Margaret Anne Florence', '2024-10-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ju10W5gl3PPK3b7TjEmVOZap51I.jpg', '', '', '', 6.857, 0, 0),
(2101, 'Ne Zha 2', 'Yang Yu', 'Animation, Fantasy, Adventure', 'China', 'zh', 'Following the Tribulation, although the souls of Ne Zha and Ao Bing were preserved, their physical bodies will soon be destroyed. Tai Yi Zhen Ren plans to use the Seven Colored Lotus to reshape their physical forms, but encounters numerous difficulties. What will become of Ne Zha and Ao Bing?', 144, 'Lu Yanting, Joseph, Han Mo, Chen Hao, Lu Qi', '2025-01-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5lUmWTGkEcYnXujixXn31o9q2T0.jpg', '', '', '', 7.81, 0, 0),
(2102, 'Escape', 'Lee Jong-pil', 'Action, Drama', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'After completing his required decade of military service and being honored as a hero, a North Korean sergeant makes a sudden shocking attempt to defect to the South, risking life and limb for the chance to finally determine his own destiny.', 96, 'Lee Je-hoon, Koo Kyo-hwan, Hong Xa-bin, Seo Hyun-woo, Lee Sung-wook', '2024-07-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qiYaXpjoPASnLwyts0ZOLBjZO0u.jpg', 'Yoshikawa Eiji Prize for Literature', '', '', 7.3, 0, 0),
(2103, 'Chhaava', 'Laxman Utekar', 'History, Action, Drama', 'India', 'hi', 'Shivaji\'s death sparks the Maratha-Mughal conflict. His son Sambhaji leads resistance against Aurangzeb\'s forces. Amid battles and intrigue, both sides face challenges in a struggle for power.', 161, 'Vicky Kaushal, Rashmika Mandanna, Akshaye Khanna, Ashutosh Rana, Divya Dutta', '2025-02-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ubRsrzb6NRW8YhVTJ6jG1kpNvCi.jpg', '', '', '', 7.2, 0, 0),
(2104, 'The Lord of the Rings: The War of the Rohirrim', 'Kenji Kamiyama', 'Animation, Fantasy, Adventure, Action', 'Japan, New Zealand, United States of America', 'en', 'A sudden attack by Wulf, a clever and traitorous lord of Rohan seeking vengeance for the death of his father, forces Helm Hammerhand, the King of Rohan, and his people to make a daring last stand in the ancient stronghold of the Hornburg.', 134, 'Brian Cox, Gaia Wise, Luke Pasqualino, Laurence Ubong Williams, Lorraine Ashbourne', '2024-12-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cXzCOx1hUuU9CfmiEv6rXjb6EqU.jpg', '', '', '', 6.667, 0, 0),
(2105, 'The Super Mario Bros. Movie', 'Michael Jelenic', 'Family, Comedy, Adventure, Animation', 'Japan, United States of America', 'en', 'While working underground to fix a water main, Brooklyn plumbers—and brothers—Mario and Luigi are transported down a mysterious pipe and wander into a magical new world. But when the brothers are separated, Mario embarks on an epic quest to find Luigi.', 93, 'Chris Pratt, Anya Taylor-Joy, Charlie Day, Jack Black, Keegan-Michael Key', '2023-04-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qNBAXBIQlnOThrVvA6mA2B5ggV6.jpg', '', 'The Game Awards − Best Adaptation', '', 7.624, 0, 0),
(2106, 'Smile 2', 'Parker Finn', 'Horror, Mystery', 'United States of America', 'en', 'About to embark on a new world tour, global pop sensation Skye Riley begins experiencing increasingly terrifying and inexplicable events. Overwhelmed by the escalating horrors and the pressures of fame, Skye is forced to face her dark past to regain control of her life before it spirals out of control.', 127, 'Naomi Scott, Rosemarie DeWitt, Lukas Gage, Miles Gutierrez-Riley, Peter Jacobson', '2024-10-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ht8Uv9QPv9y7K0RvUyJIaXOZTfd.jpg', '', '', '', 6.598, 0, 0),
(2107, 'Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning', 'Christopher McQuarrie', 'Action, Adventure, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After escaping a calamitous train crash, Ethan realizes The Entity is stashed aboard an old Russian submarine, but a foe from his past named Gabriel is also on the trail.', 0, 'Tom Cruise, Hayley Atwell, Ving Rhames, Simon Pegg, Esai Morales', '2025-05-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/z53D72EAOxGRqdr7KXXWp9dJiDe.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2108, 'Wicked', 'Jon M. Chu', 'Drama, Romance, Fantasy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In the land of Oz, ostracized and misunderstood green-skinned Elphaba is forced to share a room with the popular aristocrat Glinda at Shiz University, and the two\'s unlikely friendship is tested as they begin to fulfill their respective destinies as Glinda the Good and the Wicked Witch of the West.', 162, 'Cynthia Erivo, Ariana Grande, Jeff Goldblum, Michelle Yeoh, Jonathan Bailey', '2024-11-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xDGbZ0JJ3mYaGKy4Nzd9Kph6M9L.jpg', 'Laurence Olivier Awards, NPR Top 100 Science Fiction and Fantasy Books, Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Musical, Drama League Award, Outer Critics Circle Award, Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Book of a Musical, Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Lyrics', '', '', 6.9, 0, 0),
(2109, 'Magazine Dreams', 'Elijah Bynum', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Aspiring bodybuilder Killian Maddox struggles to find human connection in this exploration of celebrity and violence. Nothing deters him from his fiercely protected dream of superstardom, not even the doctors who warn him of the permanent damage he causes to himself with his quest.', 124, 'Jonathan Majors, Haley Bennett, Taylour Paige, Harrison Page, Harriet Sansom Harris', '2025-03-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vSidx9NHKuQIPEQ4yI9b9zkTeh3.jpg', 'Sundance Special Jury Prize for Distinctive Vision in Filmmaking', '', '', 6.5, 0, 0),
(2110, 'Barbie', 'Greta Gerwig', 'Comedy, Adventure', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.', 114, 'Margot Robbie, Ryan Gosling, America Ferrera, Ariana Greenblatt, Issa Rae', '2023-07-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iuFNMS8U5cb6xfzi51Dbkovj7vM.jpg', '', 'Academy Award for Best Picture', '', 6.978, 0, 0),
(2111, 'Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse', 'Justin K. Thompson', 'Animation, Action, Adventure, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After reuniting with Gwen Stacy, Brooklyn’s full-time, friendly neighborhood Spider-Man is catapulted across the Multiverse, where he encounters the Spider Society, a team of Spider-People charged with protecting the Multiverse’s very existence. But when the heroes clash on how to handle a new threat, Miles finds himself pitted against the other Spiders and must set out on his own to save those he loves most.', 140, 'Shameik Moore, Hailee Steinfeld, Brian Tyree Henry, Luna Lauren Velez, Jake Johnson', '2023-05-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8Vt6mWEReuy4Of61Lnj5Xj704m8.jpg', '', '', '', 8.344, 0, 0),
(2112, 'Werewolves', 'Steven C. Miller', 'Action, Horror, Thriller', 'United States of America, Puerto Rico', 'en', 'A year after a supermoon’s light activated a dormant gene, transforming humans into bloodthirsty werewolves and causing nearly a billion deaths, the nightmare resurfaces as the supermoon rises again. Two scientists attempt to stop the mutation but fail and must now struggle to reach one of their family homes.', 94, 'Frank Grillo, Katrina Law, Ilfenesh Hadera, Jimmy Cummings, Lou Diamond Phillips', '2024-12-04', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/otXBlMPbFBRs6o2Xt6KX59Qw6dL.jpg', '', '', '', 6.192, 0, 0),
(2113, 'Kung Fu Panda 4', 'Mike Mitchell', 'Animation, Family, Action, Comedy, Adventure, Fantasy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Po is gearing up to become the spiritual leader of his Valley of Peace, but also needs someone to take his place as Dragon Warrior. As such, he will train a new kung fu practitioner for the spot and will encounter a villain called the Chameleon who conjures villains from the past.', 94, 'Jack Black, Awkwafina, Viola Davis, Dustin Hoffman, Bryan Cranston', '2024-03-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nqXsAaQsKw2gKpkfhIgjXNDRqg7.jpg', '', '', '', 7.073, 0, 0),
