(2121, 'Absolution', 'Hans Petter Moland', 'Action, Crime, Thriller, Mystery, Family', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An aging ex-boxer gangster working as muscle for a Boston crime boss receives an upsetting diagnosis.  Despite a faltering memory, he attempts to rectify the sins of his past and reconnect with his estranged children. He is determined to leave a positive legacy for his grandson, but the criminal underworld isn’t done with him and won’t loosen their grip willingly.', 112, 'Liam Neeson, Ron Perlman, Yolonda Ross, Frankie Shaw, Daniel Diemer', '2024-10-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gt70JOD9xsPlpJnuBJAWdOT4yRg.jpg', '', '', '', 5.9, 0, 0),
