(2160, 'Banger', 'So-Me', 'Comedy, Music', 'France', 'fr', 'When cops recruit a has-been DJ to bust a quirky criminal gang with ties to his rival, he spots a chance to mix his way back to the top with a banger.', 90, 'Vincent Cassel, Yvick Letexier, Laura Felpin, Alexis Manenti, Nina Zem', '2025-04-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2QAgOQWcdQLnbki5V2Sjn1tcnHS.jpg', '', '', '', 4.5, 0, 0),
(2161, 'Desmontando a Lucía', 'Alberto Utrera', 'Comedy, Drama', 'Spain', 'es', 'Lucía is arrested while driving her boyfriend Héctor\'s car at 200 km/h, dazed and bloody. She was sharing a weekend at the beach with him and Elena, her best friend. Now they are both missing and Lucía only remembers a “little” argument that ended with a bottle broken on Héctor’s head, but that’s all. This complicates Simon’s life. A private investigator? No. , thank you. Simon prefers to consider himself a simple “judicial expert”. When his partner Oliver, a lawyer with financial problems due to gambling, asks him to investigate Lucía and the disappearances, Simon does not know that he is about to take the Expertise on another level. Obsessed with Bogart\'s film noir, Simón will go beyond all limits when he falls in love with Lucía, the amnesiac suspect in the murder he is investigating.', 103, 'Susana Abaitua, Hugo Silva, Julián Villagrán, Rodrigo Poisón, Angelo Olivier', '2024-11-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3zWj356Tr4SyWdgnZ0qGYc6m5v7.jpg', '', '', '', 5.333, 0, 0),
(2162, 'Rita', 'Desconocido', 'Drama', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Rita, who finds herself alone when husband Ariel works abroad. They both find solace and sexual satisfaction in other people. When Ariel comes back, they both act like nothing happened. But will this keep their marriage from falling apart?', 113, 'Christine Bermas, Gold Aceron, VR Relosa, Josh Ivan Morales, Sahil Khan', '2024-03-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pXENxAzOBrTSDJGxDcUnlNTNmWr.jpg', 'Q111851454', '', 'Eurovision Song Contest 1990', 6.7, 0, 0),
(2163, 'One of Them Days', 'Lawrence Lamont', 'Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Best friends and roommates Dreux and Alyssa are about to have One of Them Days. When they discover Alyssa’s boyfriend has blown their rent money, the duo finds themselves going to extremes in a comical race against the clock to avoid eviction and keep their friendship intact.', 97, 'Keke Palmer, SZA, Joshua David Neal, Aziza Scott, Patrick Cage', '2025-01-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ccn6bFUA5DECjA3Lo0CuJqGNQCv.jpg', '', '', '', 6.951, 0, 0),
(2164, 'Control Freak', 'Shal Ngo', 'Horror', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A motivational speaker, plagued by an uncontrollable itch on her head, becomes infected with a parasitic demon from her homeland.', 104, 'Kelly Marie Tran, Miles Robbins, Kieu Chinh, Toan Le, Callie Johnson', '2025-03-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qcOksMzsmPPA41c3DkCD47sElDU.jpg', '', '', '', 5.5, 0, 0),
(2165, 'Subservience', 'SK Dale', 'Horror, Science Fiction, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'With his wife out sick, a struggling father brings home a lifelike AI, only to have his self-aware new help want everything her new family has to offer... Like the affection of her owner and she\'ll kill to get it.', 105, 'Megan Fox, Michele Morrone, Madeline Zima, Matilda Firth, Andrew Whipp', '2024-08-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gBenxR01Uy0Ev9RTIw6dVBPoyQU.jpg', '', '', '', 6.703, 0, 0),
(2166, 'Victoria', 'Sivaranjini', 'Drama', '', 'ml', 'Victoria, a young beautician in a suburban beauty parlour, decides to elope with her Hindu boyfriend after a fierce clash with her conservative Catholic parents. Amidst the turmoil, a neighbour asks her to temporarily house an offering rooster destined for a festival at St. George church inside the parlour. Juggling the rooster\'s antics, unexpected clients, and her boyfriend\'s uncertainty, Victoria grapples with conflicting emotions leading to a day of intense personal and spiritual revelations.', 84, 'Meenakshi Jayan, Sreeshma Chandran, Jolly Chirayath, Darsana Vikas, Steeja Mary', '2024-12-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hw09PdM2o7pF1zxn1pM8NTMPzno.jpg', 'Order of Saint John, Order of Queen Maria Luisa, Order of Prince Danilo I, Order of the Cross of Takovo, Decoration of the Royal Red Cross, Order of Christ, Albert Medal, Royal Order of Kamehameha I, Order of the Crown of India, Royal Family Order of King George IV, Order of Louise, Order of the Indian Empire, Order of the Bath, Order of St Patrick, Order of the Star of India, Order of St. Sava, Order of the Thistle, Order of the Royal House of Chakri, Order of Saint Isabel, Order of the White Eagle, Order of the Garter, Order of Aftab, Order of Pedro I, Order of Saint Catherine, Grand Cross of the Legion of Honour, Order of Charles III, Order of Saint Michael and Saint George, Order of Solomon, Royal Order of Victoria and Albert, Order of the White Elephant, Order of the Immaculate Conception of Vila Viçosa, Order of Merit, Order of the Black Eagle, Royal Victorian Order, Distinguished Service Order', 'European Film Award for Best Actress, European Film Award for Best Director, European Film Award – People\'s Choice Award for Best European Film, European Film Award for Best Film', '28th European Film Awards, Brest 2016', 0, 0, 0),
(2167, 'Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga', 'George Miller', 'Action, Science Fiction, Adventure', 'Australia, United States of America', 'en', 'As the world falls, young Furiosa is snatched from the Green Place of Many Mothers into the hands of a great biker horde led by the warlord Dementus. Sweeping through the wasteland, they encounter the citadel presided over by Immortan Joe. The two tyrants wage war for dominance, and Furiosa must survive many trials as she puts together the means to find her way home.', 149, 'Anya Taylor-Joy, Chris Hemsworth, Tom Burke, Alyla Browne, George Shevtsov', '2024-05-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iADOJ8Zymht2JPMoy3R7xceZprc.jpg', '', '', '', 7.487, 0, 0),
(2168, 'Civil War', 'Alex Garland', 'War, Action, Drama', 'Finland, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'In the near future, a group of war journalists attempt to survive while reporting the truth as the United States stands on the brink of civil war.', 109, 'Kirsten Dunst, Wagner Moura, Cailee Spaeny, Stephen McKinley Henderson, Nelson Lee', '2024-04-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sh7Rg8Er3tFcN9BpKIPOMvALgZd.jpg', '', '', '', 6.872, 0, 0),
(2169, 'A Whole Life', 'Hans Steinbichler', 'Drama, History', 'Austria, Germany', 'de', 'When Andreas arrives in the remote valley in the Austrian Alps, he is only about four years old - nobody knows for sure. He grows up to become a skilled farmhand and, as a young man, joins a work crew that builds one of the first mountain railroads, bringing light and noise to the valley along with electricity. He also finds the love of his life in Marie, but their happiness is short-lived. Only many years later, when Andreas embarks on his final journey, she is with him once again. And in amazement Andreas looks back at all the years that lie behind him.', 116, 'Stefan Górski, August Zirner, Andreas Lust, Julia Franz Richter, Robert Stadlober', '2023-11-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/podcOble2lPYMQoBIwBPYaHtGhy.jpg', '', 'International Booker Prize', '', 7.185, 0, 0),
(2170, 'The Pursuit of Lust 3', 'Batdelger Byambasvren', 'Thriller', 'Mongolia', 'mn', 'This intense erotic thriller follows a disheartened woman who goes on a drinking binge after a guy she met online never showed up for their first date. Unfortunately, her drunken state would make her fall victim to a strange taxi driver’s deranged fetishes.', 36, 'G.LKHAGVADORJ, E.BAYRKHUU, Batdelger Bymbasvren', '2025-02-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uvGOLs5wX6YFq2EJqTljzykO3d1.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(2171, 'Five Nights at Freddy\'s', 'Emma Tammi', 'Horror, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Recently fired and desperate for work, a troubled young man named Mike agrees to take a position as a night security guard at an abandoned theme restaurant: Freddy Fazbear\'s Pizzeria. But he soon discovers that nothing at Freddy\'s is what it seems.', 110, 'Josh Hutcherson, Piper Rubio, Elizabeth Lail, Matthew Lillard, Mary Stuart Masterson', '2023-10-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4dKRTUylqwXQ4VJz0BS84fqW2wa.jpg', '', '', '', 7.5, 0, 0),
(2172, 'Migration', 'Benjamin Renner', 'Animation, Adventure, Comedy, Family', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After a migrating duck family alights on their pond with thrilling tales of far-flung places, the Mallard family embarks on a family road trip, from New England, to New York City, to tropical Jamaica.', 83, 'Kumail Nanjiani, Elizabeth Banks, Caspar Jennings, Tresi Gazal, Awkwafina', '2023-12-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dpXxBDi0ut5svjh5fbAqLoaJSq8.jpg', '', '', '', 7.402, 0, 0),
(2173, 'Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes', 'Wes Ball', 'Science Fiction, Adventure, Action, Drama, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Several generations following Caesar\'s reign, apes – now the dominant species – live harmoniously while humans have been reduced to living in the shadows. As a new tyrannical ape leader builds his empire, one young ape undertakes a harrowing journey that will cause him to question all he\'s known about the past and to make choices that will define a future for apes and humans alike.', 145, 'Owen Teague, Freya Allan, Kevin Durand, Peter Macon, William H. Macy', '2024-05-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gKkl37BQuKTanygYQG1pyYgLVgf.jpg', '', '', '', 7.08, 0, 0),
(2174, 'Making of The Last of Us', 'Paul C. Rosen', 'Documentary', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Featuring extensive interviews with the cast and crew, this all-access documentary gives a rare glimpse into the daunting behind-the-scenes efforts that went into the production of the HBO Original smash hit series The Last of Us.', 31, 'Pedro Pascal, Bella Ramsey, Neil Druckmann, Craig Mazin, Anna Torv', '2023-03-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nter1KTaQjmkGCjvSu5u01FoecP.jpg', '', '', '', 6.9, 0, 0),
(2175, 'Dhoom Dhaam', 'Rishab Seth', 'Comedy, Romance, Action', 'India', 'hi', 'On their wedding night, an oddball couple is thrust into a chaotic chase, dodging goons and cops in a frenzied hunt for the mysterious \"Charlie.\"', 109, 'Yami Gautam, Pratik Gandhi, Eijaz Khan, Mukul Chadda, Pavitra Sarkar', '2025-02-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2E7me3rPi8HqaeheuD86YlpNX6k.jpg', '', '', '', 6.671, 0, 0),
(2176, 'The Count of Monte Cristo', 'Alexandre de La Patellière', 'Action, Adventure, Drama', 'France', 'fr', 'Edmond Dantes becomes the target of a sinister plot and is arrested on his wedding day for a crime he did not commit. After 14 years in the island prison of Château d’If, he manages a daring escape. Now rich beyond his dreams, he assumes the identity of the Count of Monte-Cristo and exacts his revenge on the three men who betrayed him.', 178, 'Pierre Niney, Bastien Bouillon, Anaïs Demoustier, Laurent Lafitte, Pierfrancesco Favino', '2024-06-28', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sAT1P3FGhtJ68anUyJScnMu8t1l.jpg', 'National Board of Review: Top Ten Films', '', '', 8.018, 0, 0),
(2177, 'Monster', 'Hirokazu Kore-eda', 'Mystery, Thriller, Drama', 'Japan', 'ja', 'When a young boy begins behaving strangely, shocking truths emerge as the story unfolds through the eyes of his single mother, a teacher who is believed to be responsible, and the child himself.', 125, 'Soya Kurokawa, Hinata Hiiragi, Sakura Ando, Eita Nagayama, Yuko Tanaka', '2023-06-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kvUJUyUGOhEoiWWNH04IXoExPE2.jpg', 'Academy Award for Best Actress, Queer Palm, Best Screenplay Award (Cannes Film Festival), Michael L. Printz Award', 'Hugo Award for Best Novelette, Locus Award for Best Short Story, Academy Award for Best Actress, Asia Pacific Screen Award for Best Youth Feature Film', '', 7.968, 0, 0),
(2178, 'The Brutalist', 'Brady Corbet', 'Drama', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'When a visionary architect and his wife flee post-war Europe in 1947 to rebuild their legacy and witness the birth of modern United States, their lives are changed forever by a mysterious, wealthy client.', 215, 'Adrien Brody, Felicity Jones, Guy Pearce, Joe Alwyn, Raffey Cassidy', '2024-12-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vP7Yd6couiAaw9jgMd5cjMRj3hQ.jpg', 'Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture – Drama', 'Academy Award for Best Picture', '', 7.1, 0, 0),
(2179, 'Mesa de regalos', 'Noé Santillán-López', 'Comedy', 'Mexico', 'es', 'Nicolás and Antonia are two inseparable friends who are far from the emotional and professional stability that all their acquaintances have achieved. After attending countless weddings, they come up with a plan as bold as it is ingenious: to fund their dreams by organizing their own fake wedding! They announce their \"secret love,\" plan a big celebration, and at the crucial moment, Antonia is to leave Nicolás standing at the altar. Confident that the scandal will discourage guests from claiming their gifts, they plan to split the loot. However, unexpected feelings begin to arise, which could complicate their brilliant plan.', 89, 'José Eduardo Derbez, Cassandra Sánchez Navarro, Verónica Bravo, Irán Castillo, José Antonio Toledano', '2025-01-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vtabAKvDiJFgsRFskSkX2dOKYr0.jpg', '', '', '', 8.648, 0, 0),
(2180, 'Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3', 'James Gunn', 'Science Fiction, Adventure, Action, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Peter Quill, still reeling from the loss of Gamora, must rally his team around him to defend the universe along with protecting one of their own. A mission that, if not completed successfully, could quite possibly lead to the end of the Guardians as we know them.', 150, 'Chris Pratt, Zoe Saldaña, Dave Bautista, Karen Gillan, Pom Klementieff', '2023-05-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r2J02Z2OpNTctfOSN1Ydgii51I3.jpg', '', 'Academy Award for Best Visual Effects', '', 7.949, 0, 0),
(2181, 'Lilo & Stitch', 'Dean Fleischer Camp', 'Family, Comedy, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'The wildly funny and touching story of a lonely Hawaiian girl and the fugitive alien who helps to mend her broken family.', 108, 'Maia Kealoha, Chris Sanders, Sydney Agudong, Billy Magnussen, Tia Carrere', '2025-05-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3bN675X0K2E5QiAZVChzB5wq90B.jpg', 'Annie Award', 'Academy Award for Best Animated Feature', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2182, 'Exhibiting Forgiveness', 'Titus Kaphar', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Utilizing his paintings to find freedom from his past, a Black artist on the path to success is derailed by an unexpected visit from his estranged father, a recovering addict desperate to reconcile. Together, they learn that forgetting might be a greater challenge than forgiving.', 117, 'André Holland, Andra Day, John Earl Jelks, Aunjanue Ellis-Taylor, Daniel Michael Barriere', '2024-09-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gGlvpqgmyJovSA0Ny0D0gvUZFV6.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0),
(2183, 'Abigail', 'Matt Bettinelli-Olpin', 'Horror, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A group of criminals kidnap a teenage ballet dancer, the daughter of a notorious gang leader, in order to obtain a ransom of $50 million, but over time, they discover that she is not just an ordinary girl. After the kidnappers begin to diminish, one by one, they discover, to their increasing horror, that they are locked inside with no normal little girl.', 109, 'Melissa Barrera, Dan Stevens, Alisha Weir, William Catlett, Kathryn Newton', '2024-04-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5gKKSoD3iezjoL7YqZONjmyAiRA.jpg', '', '', '', 6.758, 0, 0),
(2184, 'Elyas', 'Florent-Emilio Siri', 'Action, Thriller', 'France', 'fr', 'Elyas, a former Special Forces soldier who has become paranoid since a mission in Afghanistan, is recruited to ensure the safety of Amina and her daughter Nour, 13 years old, both of whom came from the Middle East for the holidays. As he takes office, Elyas senses something is up.', 99, 'Roschdy Zem, Laëtitia Eïdo, Nabil Elouahabi, Sherwan Haji, Dimitri Storoge', '2024-07-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5q7CPIjfaBAuItjRgXVWVoafQEs.jpg', '', '', '', 6.216, 0, 0),
(2185, 'The Chosen: Last Supper', 'Dallas Jenkins', 'Drama, History, Adventure', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Jesus rides into the holy city as king, but finds His Father’s house has been turned from a place of prayer into a corrupt market. As the Jewish High Priest schemes against the would-be Messiah, Jesus strikes first—turning the tables on religious corruption.', 0, 'Jonathan Roumie, Elizabeth Tabish, Shahar Isaac, Paras Patel, Noah James', '2025-03-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aRO7Oy3o6MAZbIiSFw4eYLY5qMp.jpg', '', '', '', 8.7, 0, 0),
(2186, 'The Accountant 2', 'Gavin O\'Connor', 'Crime, Thriller, Action', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When an old acquaintance is murdered, Wolff is compelled to solve the case. Realizing more extreme measures are necessary, Wolff recruits his estranged and highly lethal brother, Brax, to help. In partnership with Marybeth Medina, they uncover a deadly conspiracy, becoming targets of a ruthless network of killers who will stop at nothing to keep their secrets buried.', 124, 'Ben Affleck, Jon Bernthal, Cynthia Addai-Robinson, J.K. Simmons, Daniella Pineda', '2025-04-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/AvAjlqg8gOSSfKnrSFE0yxlyZD4.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(2187, 'Den of Thieves 2: Pantera', 'Christian Gudegast', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'Big Nick is back on the hunt in Europe and closing in on Donnie, who is embroiled in the treacherous and unpredictable world of diamond thieves and the infamous Panther mafia, as they plot a massive heist of the world\'s largest diamond exchange.', 144, 'Gerard Butler, O\'Shea Jackson Jr., Evin Ahmad, Salvatore Esposito, Meadow Williams', '2025-01-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rxcyxxarD17xMliStDEhM6y2AYQ.jpg', '', '', '', 6.795, 0, 0),
(2188, 'Godzilla Minus One', 'Takashi Yamazaki', 'Science Fiction, Horror, Action', 'Japan', 'ja', 'In postwar Japan, Godzilla brings new devastation to an already scorched landscape. With no military intervention or government help in sight, the survivors must join together in the face of despair and fight back against an unrelenting horror.', 124, 'Ryunosuke Kamiki, Minami Hamabe, Yuki Yamada, Munetaka Aoki, Hidetaka Yoshioka', '2023-11-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hkxxMIGaiCTmrEArK7J56JTKUlB.jpg', 'Academy Award for Best Visual Effects', '', '', 7.572, 0, 0),
(2189, 'Death of a Unicorn', 'Alex Scharfman', 'Comedy, Fantasy, Horror', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A father and daughter accidentally hit and kill a unicorn while en route to a weekend retreat, where his billionaire boss seeks to exploit the creature’s miraculous curative properties.', 107, 'Paul Rudd, Jenna Ortega, Will Poulter, Richard E. Grant, Téa Leoni', '2025-03-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lXR32JepFwD1UHkplWqtBP1K79z.jpg', '', '', '', 6.3, 0, 0),
(2190, 'María, ¡Me muero!', 'Gabriela Sobarzo', 'Comedy', 'Mexico', 'es', '“Maria, I\'m dying!” is a comedy about a hypochondriac man, the only being in the world capable of even terminal colds, and his wife who has to put up with it until he decides to do something about it. The fear of death has never been so fun.', 96, 'Natalia Téllez, Ricardo Fastlicht, José Sefami, Paz Bascuñan, Minnie West', '2024-10-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/u0rr4qLKx0WuKVOwV6mXBsi8l56.jpg', '', '', '', 6.368, 0, 0),
(2191, 'IF', 'John Krasinski', 'Comedy, Fantasy, Family', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After discovering she can see everyone\'s imaginary friends, a girl embarks on a magical adventure to reconnect forgotten imaginary friends with their kids.', 104, 'Cailey Fleming, Ryan Reynolds, John Krasinski, Fiona Shaw, Steve Carell', '2024-05-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xbKFv4KF3sVYuWKllLlwWDmuZP7.jpg', '', '', '', 7.082, 0, 0),
(2192, 'The Dad Quest', 'Salvador Espinosa', 'Comedy, Drama', '', 'es', 'When a father-son duo learns that they may not be biologically related, the two embark on a wild adventure through Mexico to find the truth.', 83, 'Michel Brown, Martino Leonardi, Mayra Hermosillo, Fernanda Castillo, Julieta Egurrola', '2025-04-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5YxF7mW7vp6ETRYznnlkWIsauem.jpg', '', '', '', 6.313, 0, 0),
