(2243, 'The Boy and the Heron', 'Hayao Miyazaki', 'Animation, Adventure, Fantasy, Family, Drama', 'Japan', 'ja', 'While the Second World War rages, the teenage Mahito, haunted by his mother\'s tragic death, is relocated from Tokyo to the serene rural home of his new stepmother Natsuko, a woman who bears a striking resemblance to the boy\'s mother. As he tries to adjust, this strange new world grows even stranger following the appearance of a persistent gray heron, who perplexes and bedevils Mahito, dubbing him the \"long-awaited one.\"', 124, 'Soma Santoki, Masaki Suda, Ko Shibasaki, Aimyon, Yoshino Kimura', '2023-07-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/f4oZTcfGrVTXKTWg157AwikXqmP.jpg', 'Golden Globe Award for Best Animated Feature Film, New York Film Critics Circle Award for Best Animated Film, Los Angeles Film Critics Association Award for Best Animated Film, Chicago Film Critics Association Award for Best Animated Film, Dallas-Fort Worth Film Critics Association Award for Best Animated Film, Florida Film Critics Circle Award for Best Animated Film, San Francisco Film Critics Circle Award for Best Animated Feature, Ōfuji Noburō Award, BAFTA Award for Best Animated Film, Academy Award for Best Animated Feature', '', '', 7.458, 0, 0),
(2244, 'Revelations', 'Yeon Sang-ho', 'Thriller, Crime, Mystery', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'A pastor who believes in divine revelation and a detective haunted by visions pursue a missing person case — exposing their own demons in the process.', 122, 'Ryu Jun-yeol, Shin Hyun-been, Shin Min-jae, Han Ji-hyun, Kim Bo-min', '2025-03-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ak0HlRVsVzh8mvwIUZpZr0z6uqW.jpg', '', '', '', 6.356, 0, 0),
(2245, 'The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds & Snakes', 'Francis Lawrence', 'Drama, Science Fiction, Adventure', 'Germany, United States of America', 'en', '64 years before he becomes the tyrannical president of Panem, Coriolanus Snow sees a chance for a change in fortunes when he mentors Lucy Gray Baird, the female tribute from District 12.', 157, 'Tom Blyth, Rachel Zegler, Peter Dinklage, Jason Schwartzman, Hunter Schafer', '2023-11-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lrkOYL5GBTFW9cgs9RlojxAcZZF.jpg', '', '', '', 7.025, 0, 0),
(2246, 'A Quiet Place: Day One', 'Michael Sarnoski', 'Horror, Science Fiction, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'As New York City is invaded by alien creatures who hunt by sound, a woman named Sam fights to survive with her cat.', 99, 'Lupita Nyong\'o, Joseph Quinn, Alex Wolff, Djimon Hounsou, Eliane Umuhire', '2024-06-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hU42CRk14JuPEdqZG3AWmagiPAP.jpg', '', '', '', 6.731, 0, 0),
(2247, 'The Equalizer 3', 'Antoine Fuqua', 'Action, Thriller, Crime', 'Italy, United States of America', 'en', 'Robert McCall finds himself at home in Southern Italy but he discovers his friends are under the control of local crime bosses. As events turn deadly, McCall knows what he has to do: become his friends\' protector by taking on the mafia.', 109, 'Denzel Washington, Dakota Fanning, Eugenio Mastrandrea, David Denman, Gaia Scodellaro', '2023-08-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b0Ej6fnXAP8fK75hlyi2jKqdhHz.jpg', '', '', '', 7.315, 0, 0),
(2248, 'Watchmen: Chapter II', 'Brandon Vietti', 'Animation, Mystery, Science Fiction, Action, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Suspicious of the events ensnaring their former colleagues, Nite Owl and Silk Spectre are spurred out of retirement to investigate. As they grapple with personal ethics, inner demons and a society turned against them, they race the clock to uncover a deepening plot that might trigger global nuclear war.', 89, 'Troy Baker, Adrienne Barbeau, Michael Cerveris, Zehra Fazal, Phil Fondacaro', '2024-11-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4rBObJFpiWJOG7aIlRrOUniAkBs.jpg', '', '', '', 7.5, 0, 0),
(2249, 'Meg 2: The Trench', 'Ben Wheatley', 'Action, Science Fiction, Horror', 'China, United States of America', 'en', 'An exploratory dive into the deepest depths of the ocean of a daring research team spirals into chaos when a malevolent mining operation threatens their mission and forces them into a high-stakes battle for survival.', 116, 'Jason Statham, Wu Jing, Shuya Sophia Cai, Page Kennedy, Sergio Peris-Mencheta', '2023-08-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4m1Au3YkjqsxF8iwQy0fPYSxE0h.jpg', '', '', '', 6.449, 0, 0),
(2250, 'Oddity', 'Damian Mc Carthy', 'Horror, Mystery', 'Ireland, United States of America', 'en', 'After the brutal murder of her twin sister, Darcy goes after those responsible by using haunted items as her tools for revenge.', 98, 'Carolyn Bracken, Gwilym Lee, Steve Wall, Joe Rooney, Tadhg Murphy', '2024-07-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3Z9c1tbUhP0QruRjczPHnbx3U2D.jpg', '', 'Q110864452', '', 6.686, 0, 0),
(2251, 'Zak & Wowo: The Legend of Lendarys', 'Philippe Duchene', 'Animation, Adventure, Fantasy', 'Canada, France', 'fr', 'At the heart of an imaginary world populated by fantastical creatures and dangerous monsters, the 13 year-old Zak goes in search of his twin brother Kyle, who has disappeared mysteriously. Equipped with a magical jade stone whose superpowers he doesn\'t yet know how to control, he is joined by his grandmother NaïNaï and Indiana, a beautiful outlaw who can communicate with the world\'s fantastical creatures. But he is also flanked by Wowo, formerly a 3 meter-tall furry pachyderm, now turned into a tiny, cute and wacky furball by the magical jade stone.', 85, 'Jérôme Niel, Manu Payet, Clara Luciani, Kyan Khojandi, Akil Wingate', '2024-04-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tgOq45Aijeup6mqEmOWGzYabaVQ.jpg', '', '', '', 5.5, 0, 0),
(2252, 'Kalikot', 'Artemio Abad', 'Drama', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Sal, a hot single professor, moves across an auto service shop and rocks the world of young repairman Arnel. Ever since Sal came over to get her car fixed, Arnel\'s skilled hands have always been busy. But can he still fix the problems that come with it?', 49, 'Van Allen Ong, Sheila Snow, Arah Alonzo, Raul Montesa, Unique Valdez Cajeda', '2024-03-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bnOz6hfBTOIDYyrj8P3Pcj4uVzE.jpg', '', '', '', 6.8, 0, 0),
(2253, 'OVERLORD: The Sacred Kingdom', 'Naoyuki Ito', 'Action, Adventure, Animation, Fantasy', 'Japan', 'ja', 'After twelve years of playing his favorite MMORPG game, Momonga logs in for the last time only to find himself transported into its world playing it indefinitely. Throughout his adventures, his avatar ascends to the title of Sorcerer King Ains Ooal Gown. Once prosperous but now on the brink of ruin, The Sacred Kingdom enjoyed years of peace after construction of an enormous wall protecting them from neighboring invasions. But, one day this comes to an end when the Demon Emperor Jaldabaoth arrives with an army of villainous demi-humans. Fearing invasion of their own lands, the neighboring territory of the Slane Theocracy is forced to beg their enemies at the Sorcerer Kingdom for help. Heeding the call, Momonga, now known as the Sorcerer King Ains Ooal Gown, rallies the Sorcerer Kingdom and its undead army to join the fight alongside the Sacred Kingdom and the Slane Theocracy in hopes to defeat the Demon Emperor.', 134, 'Satoshi Hino, Yoshino Aoyama, Hitomi Nabatame, Saori Hayami, Haruka Tomatsu', '2024-09-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jEvytxNa5mfW7VAUmDWsZtIdATc.jpg', '', '', '', 7.194, 0, 0),
(2254, 'Twisters', 'Lee Isaac Chung', 'Action, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'As storm season intensifies, the paths of former storm chaser Kate Carter and reckless social-media superstar Tyler Owens collide when terrifying phenomena never seen before are unleashed. The pair and their competing teams find themselves squarely in the paths of multiple storm systems converging over central Oklahoma in the fight of their lives.', 123, 'Daisy Edgar-Jones, Glen Powell, Anthony Ramos, Brandon Perea, Maura Tierney', '2024-07-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pjnD08FlMAIXsfOLKQbvmO0f0MD.jpg', '', '', '', 6.844, 0, 0),
(2255, 'When Fall Is Coming', 'François Ozon', 'Drama, Thriller, Comedy', 'France', 'fr', 'Michelle is enjoying a peaceful retirement in a Burgundy village, close to her longtime friend Marie-Claude. When her Parisian daughter Valérie drops off her son Lucas to spend school vacation with his grandma, Michelle, stressed out by her daughter, serves her toxic mushrooms for lunch. Valérie quickly recovers, but forbids her mother from seeing her grandson anymore. Feeling lonely and guilty, Michelle falls into a depression... until Marie-Claude\'s son gets out of prison.', 104, 'Hélène Vincent, Josiane Balasko, Ludivine Sagnier, Pierre Lottin, Vincent Colombe', '2024-10-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6i7cM8UQcfGMp0nYvqo1AcIHGuR.jpg', '', '', '', 6.455, 0, 0),
(2256, 'Emilia Pérez', 'Jacques Audiard', 'Drama, Thriller', 'Belgium, France, United States of America, Mexico', 'fr', 'Rita, an underrated lawyer working for a large law firm more interested in getting criminals out of jail than bringing them to justice, is hired by the leader of a criminal organization.', 132, 'Karla Sofía Gascón, Zoe Saldaña, Selena Gomez, Adriana Paz, Edgar Ramírez', '2024-08-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fko8fTfL6BcAqOUh6BZYUjt4SQP.jpg', 'Cannes Film Festival Award for Best Actress, European Film Award for Best Film, European Film Award for Best Director', 'European Film Award for Best Film, Academy Award for Best Picture, Academy Award for Best International Feature Film, Academy Award for Best Makeup and Hairstyling', '', 6.687, 0, 0),
(2257, 'Levels', 'Adam Stern', 'Action, Science Fiction, Thriller', 'Canada', 'en', 'After witnessing his girlfriend\'s murder, a man risks everything - including reality itself - to discover the truth.', 92, 'Cara Gee, Peter Mooney, Aaron Abrams, David Hewlett, Amanda Tapping', '2024-11-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/y1xm0jMIlx9Oo2a3jWNyLGm43sJ.jpg', '', '', '', 5.733, 0, 0),
(2258, 'SpongeBob Squarepants: Kreepaway Kamp', 'Ian Vasquez', 'TV Movie, Family, Comedy, Horror, Animation', 'United States of America', 'en', 'While at Kamp Koral for a reunion, SpongeBob and the gang are stalked by a mysterious figure lurking in the shadows as campers start disappearing one by one!', 45, 'Tom Kenny, Bill Fagerbakke, Rodger Bumpass, Clancy Brown, Carolyn Lawrence', '2024-10-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aUOCmqkbCX94znDJNtSy1402Sie.jpg', '', '', '', 7.1, 0, 0),
(2259, 'Jurassic World Rebirth', 'Gareth Edwards', 'Science Fiction, Adventure, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Five years after the events of Jurassic World Dominion, covert operations expert Zora Bennett is contracted to lead a skilled team on a top-secret mission to secure genetic material from the world\'s three most massive dinosaurs. When Zora\'s operation intersects with a civilian family whose boating expedition was capsized, they all find themselves stranded on an island where they come face-to-face with a sinister, shocking discovery that\'s been hidden from the world for decades.', 0, 'Scarlett Johansson, Jonathan Bailey, Mahershala Ali, Rupert Friend, Manuel Garcia-Rulfo', '2025-07-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8BZ6oGDE336qFshFC44WxZtosBX.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2260, 'The Forge', 'Alex Kendrick', 'Drama, Family', 'United States of America', 'en', '19 year old Isaiah Wright lives for basketball and video games. A year out of high school, he has no job, no plans, and no idea how to be a man. At odds with his single mother Cynthia, Isaiah is given an ultimatum – to step up or move out. Feeling the pull from his friends and the push from his mom, Isaiah is hired by Moore Fitness, unaware of how the owner will personally impact his life. With the prayers of his mother and unexpected guidance from his new mentor, Isaiah is forced to deal with his past, sacrifice his selfishness and discover how God might have a greater purpose for his life.', 123, 'Aspen Kennedy Wilson, Priscilla C. Shirer, Cameron Arnett, Karen Abercrombie, T.C. Stallings', '2024-08-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oranxontIQRmhuyQlkoAwxpeBYz.jpg', '', '', '', 8.326, 0, 0),
(2261, 'Wish', 'Chris Buck', 'Animation, Family, Fantasy, Adventure', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Asha, a sharp-witted idealist, makes a wish so powerful that it is answered by a cosmic force – a little ball of boundless energy called Star. Together, Asha and Star confront a most formidable foe - the ruler of Rosas, King Magnifico - to save her community and prove that when the will of one courageous human connects with the magic of the stars, wondrous things can happen.', 95, 'Ariana DeBose, Chris Pine, Alan Tudyk, Angelique Cabral, Victor Garber', '2023-11-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m9ckCVKU9vW3Dxc8hbodx7mjJbe.jpg', '', '', '', 6.317, 0, 0),
(2262, 'Mob Land', 'Nicholas Maggio', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'A sheriff tries to keep the peace when a desperate family man violently robs a pill mill with his brother-in-law, alerting an enforcer for the New Orleans mafia.', 111, 'John Travolta, Shiloh Fernandez, Stephen Dorff, Ashley Benson, Kevin Dillon', '2023-08-04', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mcz8oi9oCgq1wkA3Wz2kluE94pE.jpg', '', '', '', 5.48, 0, 0),
(2263, 'Road House', 'Doug Liman', 'Action, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Ex-UFC fighter Dalton takes a job as a bouncer at a Florida Keys roadhouse, only to discover that this paradise is not all it seems.', 121, 'Jake Gyllenhaal, Billy Magnussen, Daniela Melchior, Jessica Williams, Conor McGregor', '2024-03-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fDEdtS4P0gJsxHDIt8dG8TR5dx1.jpg', '', 'Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Screenplay, Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Supporting Actor, Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Actor, Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Picture, Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Director', '', 6.945, 0, 0),
(2264, 'Borderlands', 'Eli Roth', 'Action, Science Fiction, Comedy', 'United States of America, Luxembourg', 'en', 'Returning to her home planet, an infamous bounty hunter forms an unexpected alliance with a team of unlikely heroes. Together, they battle monsters and dangerous bandits to protect a young girl who holds the key to unimaginable power.', 101, 'Cate Blanchett, Kevin Hart, Edgar Ramírez, Jamie Lee Curtis, Ariana Greenblatt', '2024-08-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p0FUR86fX7NeJEvCEVUkn2ib2me.jpg', '', '', '', 5.71, 0, 0),
(2265, 'I\'m Still Here', 'Walter Salles', 'Drama, History', 'Brazil, France', 'pt', 'In 1971, military dictatorship in Brazil reaches its height. The Paiva family — Rubens, Eunice, and their five children — live in a beachside house in Rio, open to all their friends. One day, Rubens is taken for questioning and does not return.', 138, 'Fernanda Torres, Selton Mello, Valentina Herszage, Bárbara Luz, Guilherme Silveira', '2024-09-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gZnsMbhCvhzAQlKaVpeFRHYjGyb.jpg', 'Reese\'s Book Club, Golden Globe Award for Best Actress – Motion Picture Drama, Best Screenplay Award (Venice Film Festival), Satellite Award for Best Actress – Motion Picture, Academy Award for Best International Feature Film', 'Academy Award for Best Picture, Academy Award for Best International Feature Film', '', 8, 0, 0),
(2266, 'Alone In The Night', 'Guillermo Rojas', 'Action, Comedy, Drama', 'Spain', 'es', 'A group of labour lawyers hide in a house when the coup d\'état of 23F takes place in Spain. Unsure of what to do, they debate between fleeing the country, staying in hiding or trying to do something to defend Spain\'s young democracy.', 86, 'Pablo Gómez-Pando, Andrea Carballo, Alfonso Sánchez, Félix Gómez, Paula Usero', '2024-09-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fIR4praOsKJaRA3qUC2mbzDojan.jpg', '', '', '', 5.8, 0, 0),
(2267, 'The Flash', 'Andy Muschietti', 'Adventure, Action, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When his attempt to save his family inadvertently alters the future, Barry Allen becomes trapped in a reality in which General Zod has returned and there are no Super Heroes to turn to. In order to save the world that he is in and return to the future that he knows, Barry\'s only hope is to race for his life. But will making the ultimate sacrifice be enough to reset the universe?', 144, 'Ezra Miller, Sasha Calle, Michael Keaton, Michael Shannon, Ron Livingston', '2023-06-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rktDFPbfHfUbArZ6OOOKsXcv0Bm.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0),
(2268, 'Weekend in Taipei', 'George Huang', 'Action, Adventure, Thriller', 'France, United States of America', 'en', 'A former DEA agent and a former undercover operative revisit their romance during a fateful weekend in Taipei, unaware of the dangerous consequences of their past.', 101, 'Luke Evans, Gwei Lun-Mei, Sung Kang, Wyatt Yang, Pernell Walker', '2024-09-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qSc0AUvs8mRy00R9y8QYEHWIAQ9.jpg', '', '', '', 6.224, 0, 0),
(2269, 'I Am Nezha 2', 'Desconocido', 'Animation, Fantasy, Drama', 'China', 'zh', '', 107, '', '2023-09-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vHf7HD3DU7Zz5ZiW5NfxagFHmfg.jpg', '', '', '', 9, 0, 0),
(2270, 'Jugaremos en el bosque', 'Alejandra Cárdenas', 'Horror', 'Mexico', 'es', 'After the death of his son, Javier hopes that restoring his family\'s abandoned ranch will allow him and his wife Mariana, who attempted suicide, a new beginning, but his grandmother refuses.', 0, 'Lucía Gómez-Robledo, Alejandro Cuétara, Julieta Egurrola, Arturo Ripstein, Lucía Uribe', '2024-05-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eBSl9nGymidAyEBdJGADnnm7JKt.jpg', '', '', '', 7.024, 0, 0),
(2271, 'Project Silence', 'Kim Tae-gon', 'Thriller, Action, Horror, Science Fiction, Adventure', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Due to sudden deteriorating weather conditions, visibility on the Airport Bridge is severely impaired, leaving people stranded and at risk of the bridge collapsing due to a series of chain collisions and explosions. Amidst the chaos, the canine subjects \"Echo\" from the military experiment \"Project Silence,\" who were being transported in secret, break free, and all human survivors become targets of relentless attacks.', 96, 'Lee Sun-kyun, Ju Ji-hoon, Kim Hee-won, Moon Sung-keun, Ye Su-jeong', '2024-07-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lZT5Cq4wkz7IeJEnz94U94xuEWD.jpg', '', '', '', 6.996, 0, 0),
(2272, 'Gran Turismo', 'Neill Blomkamp', 'Adventure, Action, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'The ultimate wish-fulfillment tale of a teenage Gran Turismo player whose gaming skills won him a series of Nissan competitions to become an actual professional racecar driver.', 135, 'Archie Madekwe, David Harbour, Orlando Bloom, Djimon Hounsou, Darren Barnet', '2023-08-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/51tqzRtKMMZEYUpSYkrUE7v9ehm.jpg', '', 'The Game Awards − Best Adaptation', '', 7.764, 0, 0),
(2273, 'The Creator', 'Gareth Edwards', 'Science Fiction, Action, Adventure', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'Amid a future war between the human race and the forces of artificial intelligence, a hardened ex-special forces agent grieving the disappearance of his wife, is recruited to hunt down and kill the Creator, the elusive architect of advanced AI who has developed a mysterious weapon with the power to end the war—and mankind itself.', 134, 'John David Washington, Madeleine Yuna Voyles, Gemma Chan, Allison Janney, Ken Watanabe', '2023-09-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3dSivDtOuyxLDxPH4v2tcNG1fP7.jpg', '', 'Academy Award for Best Sound, Academy Award for Best Visual Effects', '', 7.1, 0, 0),
(2274, 'Dragonkeeper', 'Jian-Ping Li', 'Animation, Family, Action, Adventure, Fantasy', 'China, Spain', 'zh', 'Set in Han Imperial China, the plot follows the adventures of enslaved girl Ping with ancient dragon Long Danzi. Dragons had been banished from the kingdom. Ping, an orphan, finds one of the last remaining dragon eggs. Palace guards force Ping to run away in order to return the dragon egg to the ocean and save all dragons from extinction. Ping discovers that she is a true Dragonkeeper.', 99, 'Lucía Pérez, Mario Gas, Fernando Castro, Carlos de Luna, José Gómez Adán', '2024-04-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ggZGnJLzO3BTu7ysuuIzou3Oex5.jpg', '', '', '', 7.664, 0, 0),
(2275, 'A Real Pain', 'Jesse Eisenberg', 'Comedy, Drama', 'Poland, United States of America', 'en', 'Mismatched cousins David and Benji reunite for a tour through Poland to honor their beloved grandmother. The adventure takes a turn when the pair\'s old tensions resurface against the backdrop of their family history.', 90, 'Jesse Eisenberg, Kieran Culkin, Will Sharpe, Jennifer Grey, Kurt Egyiawan', '2024-11-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/67xRIXm5TxXRT4nV2V4AEJ9yq2d.jpg', '', '', '', 6.8, 0, 0),
