(2485, 'El Apocalipsis de san Juan', 'Simón Delacre', 'Documentary, History', 'Argentina', 'es', 'Embark on an epic journey through time and faith with \'The Apocalypse of Saint John.\' Join the Apostle John in a stunning visual narrative that unravels the visions of the End Times. Experience each vision like never before, with striking visual effects and epic scenes that immerse you in the apocalyptic narrative.', 110, 'Ricardo Castro, Miguel Angel Marchessi, Héctor Hugo Larriera, Carlos Secilio', '2024-10-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zzXU586n4uDBgMtVMPPQW7UJwu8.jpg', '', '', '', 7.556, 0, 0),
(2486, 'The Girl with the Needle', 'Magnus von Horn', 'Drama, History', 'Denmark, Poland, Sweden', 'da', 'Struggling to survive in post-WWI Copenhagen, a newly unemployed and pregnant young woman is taken in by a charismatic elder to help run an underground adoption agency. The two form an unexpected bond, until a sudden discovery changes everything.', 123, 'Vic Carmen Sonne, Trine Dyrholm, Besir Zeciri, Joachim Fjelstrup, Tessa Hoder', '2024-09-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2xkyx8v9G3ePxe1IcFugFQkXHzQ.jpg', '', 'Academy Award for Best International Feature Film', '', 7.607, 0, 0),
(2487, 'The Naked Gun', 'Akiva Schaffer', 'Comedy, Crime', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Only one man has the particular set of skills... to lead Police Squad and save the world: Lt. Frank Drebin Jr.', 0, 'Liam Neeson, Pamela Anderson, Paul Walter Hauser, Kevin Durand, Danny Huston', '2025-07-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aq0JMbmSfPwG8JvAzExJPrBHqmG.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2488, 'Autumn and the Black Jaguar', 'Gilles de Maistre', 'Adventure, Family', 'France', 'fr', 'Growing up in the Amazon rainforest gave Autumn the rarest of friendships – a lost jaguar cub she named Hope. When a tragic event forces her to leave Hope for New York City, she dreams of going back to the rainforest and her friend. That opportunity soon comes when Autumn decides to return to the Amazon to save her beloved jaguar from animal traffickers who threaten her childhood village.', 100, 'Lumi Pollack, Emily Bett Rickards, Wayne Charles Baker, Paul Greene, Kelly Hope Taylor', '2024-02-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/krLaIUZezfBDBSdQA2ChVTg9t3Z.jpg', '', '', '', 6.664, 0, 0),
(2489, 'Norma: Antara Mertua dan Menantu', 'Guntur Soeharjanto', 'Drama, Romance', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'Newly married Norma hopes for a happy marriage, unaware that her husband is secretly having an affair with her mother.', 134, 'Tissa Biani, Wulan Guritno, Yusuf Mahardika, Rukman Rosadi, Nunung', '2025-03-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vWfe6onIjMwJNrb1ZVtQFDI3rMa.jpg', '', '', '', 5.8, 0, 0),
(2490, 'Shazam! Fury of the Gods', 'David F. Sandberg', 'Comedy, Action, Fantasy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Billy Batson and his foster siblings, who transform into superheroes by saying \"Shazam!\", are forced to get back into action and fight the Daughters of Atlas, who they must stop from using a weapon that could destroy the world.', 130, 'Zachary Levi, Asher Angel, Jack Dylan Grazer, Rachel Zegler, Adam Brody', '2023-03-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A3ZbZsmsvNGdprRi2lKgGEeVLEH.jpg', '', '', '', 6.484, 0, 0),
(2491, 'Atlas', 'Brad Peyton', 'Science Fiction, Action', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A brilliant counterterrorism analyst with a deep distrust of AI discovers it might be her only hope when a mission to capture a renegade robot goes awry.', 120, 'Jennifer Lopez, Simu Liu, Sterling K. Brown, Gregory James Cohan, Abraham Popoola', '2024-05-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bcM2Tl5HlsvPBnL8DKP9Ie6vU4r.jpg', '', 'Swiss Film Award for Best Fiction Film, Swiss Film Award for Best Cinematography', '', 6.755, 0, 0),
(2492, 'El hilo rojo', 'Celso R. García', 'Drama, Romance', '', 'es', 'Abril, a rebellious and daring stewardess, and Manuel, a shy and traditional businessman, meet on a plane and instantly feel an undeniable attraction.', 99, 'Michel Brown, Mario Morán, Carolina Miranda, Maya Zapata, Pilar Santacruz', '2025-02-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mZ8Z4jCDVlBflEuCOwH3NCDyqBP.jpg', '', '', '', 8.121, 0, 0),
(2493, 'Picture This', 'Prarthana Mohan', 'Romance, Comedy', 'United Kingdom', 'en', 'Single and without a man on the horizon, Pia runs a failing photography studio in London with her best friend Jay. As her sister Sonal prepares for marriage and her mother Laxmi urges her to partner up, a spiritual guru predicts Pia will meet the love of her life among her next five dates. With her family intervening, Pia embarks on a hilarious yet heartfelt quest for love.', 101, 'Simone Ashley, Hero Fiennes Tiffin, Sindhu Vee, Luke Fetherston, Nikesh Patel', '2025-03-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r8mUV5bJlUQrco0XWYHUiSVzgdh.jpg', '', '', '', 6.024, 0, 0),
(2494, 'Bird', 'Andrea Arnold', 'Drama, Fantasy', 'France, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', '12-year-old Bailey lives with her single dad Bug and brother Hunter in a squat in North Kent. Bug doesn’t have much time for his kids, and Bailey, who is approaching puberty, seeks attention and adventure elsewhere.', 119, 'Nykiya Adams, Franz Rogowski, Barry Keoghan, Jason Buda, Jasmine Jobson', '2024-11-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/96LljvrTGesFPzRiytTrBgPV8W9.jpg', 'Academy Award for Best Sound', 'Academy Award for Best Sound', '2024 Cannes Film Festival', 7.2, 0, 0),
(2495, 'The Union', 'Julian Farino', 'Action, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A New Jersey construction worker goes from regular guy to aspiring spy when his long-lost high school sweetheart recruits him for an espionage mission.', 109, 'Mark Wahlberg, Halle Berry, J.K. Simmons, Mike Colter, Adewale Akinnuoye-Agbaje', '2024-08-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/d9CTnTHip1RbVi2OQbA2LJJQAGI.jpg', '', '', '', 6.152, 0, 0),
(2496, 'Anatomy of a Fall', 'Justine Triet', 'Thriller, Mystery, Crime', 'France', 'fr', 'A woman is suspected of her husband\'s murder, and their blind son faces a moral dilemma as the sole witness.', 151, 'Sandra Hüller, Swann Arlaud, Milo Machado-Graner, Antoine Reinartz, Samuel Theis', '2023-08-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kQs6keheMwCxJxrzV83VUwFtHkB.jpg', 'Palme d\'Or, European Film Award for Best Film, European University Film Award, Golden Globe Award for Best English-Language Foreign Film, César Award for Best Film', 'European Film Award for Best Film, Academy Award for Best Picture, Academy Award for Best Director, Academy Award for Best Actress, Academy Award for Best Writing, Original Screenplay, Academy Award for Best Film Editing', '2023 Cannes Film Festival', 7.5, 0, 0),
(2497, 'The Girls at the Station', 'Juana Macías', 'Drama', 'Spain', 'es', 'Jara, Alex and Miranda are three girls coming of age who grew up in a juvenile detention centre, with no knowledge of unconditional love. Jara’s birthday is coming up and the three of them want to celebrate by going to the concert of their favourite performer, but they can’t afford the tickets.  So, they meet up with an older girl and former resident of the centre who offers them an indecent proposal. But before they know it, they find themselves sliding deeper into the underbelly of Mallorca.', 116, 'Julieta Tobio, Salua Hadra, María Steelman, Xóan Fórneas, Carla Gris', '2024-11-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kKUJ6rl3NdESf5qKjpsk7BM6YyT.jpg', '', '', '', 6.4, 0, 0),
(2498, 'The Roundup: No Way Out', 'Lee Sang-yong', 'Action, Crime, Comedy, Thriller, Drama', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Detective Ma Seok-do changes his affiliation from the Geumcheon Police Station to the Metropolitan Investigation Team, in order to eradicate Japanese gangsters who enter Korea to commit heinous crimes.', 105, 'Don Lee, Lee Jun-hyuk, Munetaka Aoki, Lee Beom-soo, Kim Min-jae', '2023-05-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lW6IHrtaATxDKYVYoQGU5sh0OVm.jpg', '', '', '', 7.2, 0, 0),
(2499, 'You\'re Cordially Invited', 'Nicholas Stoller', 'Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When two weddings are accidentally booked on the same day at the same venue, each bridal party is challenged with preserving their family\'s special moment while making the most of the unanticipated tight quarters. In a hilarious battle of determination and grit, the father of the bride and sister of the other bride chaotically go head-to-head as they stop at nothing to uphold an unforgettable celebration for their loved ones.', 109, 'Will Ferrell, Reese Witherspoon, Geraldine Viswanathan, Meredith Hagner, Jimmy Tatro', '2025-01-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/muXnwAdVdEEktto0NBNMyqK3uQH.jpg', '', '', '', 5.904, 0, 0),
(2500, 'Avatar: Fire and Ash', 'James Cameron', 'Science Fiction, Adventure, Fantasy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In the wake of the devastating war against the RDA and the loss of their eldest son, Jake Sully and Neytiri face a new threat on Pandora: the Ash People, a violent and power-hungry Na\'vi tribe led by the ruthless Varang. Jake\'s family must fight for their survival and the future of Pandora in a conflict that pushes them to their emotional and physical limits.', 0, 'Sam Worthington, Zoe Saldaña, Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Kate Winslet', '2025-12-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vDdFxksDMkUJjZXd00OKJfwXKre.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2501, 'The Day the Earth Blew Up: A Looney Tunes Movie', 'Peter Browngardt', 'Family, Comedy, Adventure, Animation', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Porky and Daffy, the classic animated odd couple, turn into unlikely heroes when their antics at the local bubble gum factory uncover a secret alien mind control plot. Against all odds, the two are determined to save their town (and the world!)...that is if they don\'t drive each other crazy in the process.', 90, 'Eric Bauza, Candi Milo, Peter MacNicol, Fred Tatasciore, Laraine Newman', '2024-08-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s2lB1kaYCdGSnZX5meQCiOR6HfX.jpg', '', '', '', 7.7, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `films` (`idFilm`, `title`, `directedBy`, `genre`, `origin_country`, `original_language`, `overview`, `duration`, `castCrew`, `release_date`, `frame`, `awards`, `nominations`, `festivals`, `vote_average`, `individualRate`, `globalRate`) VALUES
(2502, 'The Holdovers', 'Alexander Payne', 'Comedy, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A curmudgeonly instructor at a New England prep school is forced to remain on campus during Christmas break to babysit the handful of students with nowhere to go. Eventually, he forms an unlikely bond with one of them — a damaged, brainy troublemaker — and with the school’s head cook, who has just lost a son in Vietnam.', 133, 'Paul Giamatti, Dominic Sessa, Da\'Vine Joy Randolph, Carrie Preston, Brady Hepner', '2023-10-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/VHSzNBTwxV8vh7wylo7O9CLdac.jpg', '', '', '', 7.679, 0, 0),
(2503, 'Blood for Dust', 'Rod Blackhurst', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Reckless Ricky makes serious money dealing illegal weapons throughout the tri-state area and loves to flaunt it. Traveling salesman Cliff, covers the same territory Ricky runs guns through. Desperate to find some financial relief for his struggling family, Cliff agrees to partner with Ricky, to commit cross-state drug and gun deliveries for a mid-level American cartel boss John. When a simple exchange turns into a bloodbath after Ricky kills everyone in a territory grab, the pair find themselves in a pressure cooker situation where unlikely drug dealer Cliff must fight as hard as he can to stay alive.', 98, 'Scoot McNairy, Kit Harington, Josh Lucas, Stephen Dorff, Nora Zehetner', '2024-04-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nvaCnkl8RilLhVAQXPFei0tqkqW.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(2504, 'The Mouse Trap', 'Jamie Bailey', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Canada', 'en', 'It\'s Alex\'s 21st Birthday, but she\'s stuck at the amusement arcade on a late shift so her friends decide to surprise her, but a masked killer dressed as Mickey Mouse decides to play a game of his own with them which she must survive.', 80, 'Simon Phillips, Sophie McIntosh, Madeline Kelman, Ben Harris, Calum Sywyk', '2024-08-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3ovFaFeojLFIl5ClqhtgYMDS8sE.jpg', '', '', '', 4.318, 0, 0),
(2505, 'The Canterville Ghost', 'Kim Burdon', 'Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy', 'Canada, United Kingdom', 'en', 'An American family moves in to the Canterville Chase, a London mansion that has been haunted by ghost Sir Simon De Canterville for 300 years.', 89, 'Stephen Fry, Hugh Laurie, Freddie Highmore, Emily Carey, Imelda Staunton', '2023-09-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dFu8oHN805ZRzpQZNOjkiLzMbep.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0),
(2506, 'Fly Me to the Moon', 'Greg Berlanti', 'Romance, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Sparks fly in all directions as marketing maven Kelly Jones, brought in to fix NASA\'s public image, wreaks havoc on Apollo 11 launch director Cole Davis\' already difficult task of putting a man on the moon. When the White House deems the mission too important to fail, Jones is directed to stage a fake moon landing as backup, and the countdown truly begins.', 132, 'Channing Tatum, Scarlett Johansson, Woody Harrelson, Ray Romano, Jim Rash', '2024-07-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gjk8YdXpItoC1in53FCrZMFIuBx.jpg', '', 'European Film Award – People\'s Choice Award for Best European Film', '', 6.844, 0, 0),
(2507, 'HAIKYU!! The Dumpster Battle', 'Susumu Mitsunaka', 'Animation, Comedy', 'Japan', 'ja', 'Shoyo Hinata joins Karasuno High\'s volleyball club to be like his idol, a former Karasuno player known as the \'Little Giant\'. But Hinata soon learns that he must team up with his middle school nemesis, Tobio Kageyama. Their clashing styles form a surprising weapon, but can their newfound teamwork defeat their rival Nekoma High in the highly anticipated \'Dumpster Battle\', the long awaited ultimate showdown between two opposing underdog teams?', 85, 'Ayumu Murase, Kaito Ishikawa, Yuki Kaji, Yuichi Nakamura, Koki Uchiyama', '2024-02-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ntRU0OA4etGGiMMmH1Yw0bnaMdW.jpg', '', '', '', 7.623, 0, 0),
(2508, 'Justice League: Crisis on Infinite Earths Part Three', 'Jeff Wamester', 'Animation, Science Fiction, Action', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Now fully revealed as the ultimate threat to existence, the Anti-Monitor wages an unrelenting attack on the surviving Earths that struggle for survival in a pocket universe. One by one, these worlds and all their inhabitants are vaporized! On the planets that remain, even time itself is shattered, and heroes from the past join the Justice League and their rag-tag allies against the epitome of evil. But as they make their last stand, will the sacrifice of the superheroes be enough to save us all?', 99, 'Jensen Ackles, Darren Criss, Corey Stoll, Gideon Adlon, Ike Amadi', '2024-07-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a3q8NkM8uTh9E23VsbUOdDSbBeN.jpg', '', '', '', 7.34, 0, 0),
(2509, 'Hurry Up Tomorrow', 'Trey Edward Shults', 'Thriller, Music', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A musician plagued by insomnia is pulled into an odyssey with a stranger who begins to unravel the very core of his existence.', 105, 'The Weeknd, Jenna Ortega, Barry Keoghan, Paul L. Davis, Gabby Barrett', '2025-05-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vjNYHZjoCya803vJXxJXUkNJQWO.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2510, 'Creation of the Gods I: Kingdom of Storms', 'Wuershan', 'Action, Fantasy, War', 'China', 'zh', 'Based on the most well-known classical fantasy novel of China, Fengshenyanyi, the trilogy is a magnificent eastern high fantasy epic that recreates the prolonged mythical wars between humans, immortals and monsters, which happened more than three thousand years ago.', 148, 'Kris Phillips, Li Xuejian, Huang Bo, Yu Shi, Chen Muchi', '2023-07-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/n3Vy8oJEGqvaFurE7e7QJbF4mGs.jpg', 'Golden Rooster Award for Best Picture', '', '', 7.088, 0, 0),
(2511, 'LEGO Marvel Avengers: Mission Demolition', 'Ken Cunningham', 'Animation, Comedy, Science Fiction', 'United States of America, Canada', 'en', 'A young, aspiring hero and superhero fan inadvertently unleashes a powerful new villain looking to rid the world of the Avengers.', 44, 'Will Friedle, Kevin Smith, John Stamos, Roger Craig Smith, Ogie Banks', '2024-10-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4KfgyzCgJeG0XJDbqNztdP730Pv.jpg', '', '', '', 6.782, 0, 0),
(2512, 'Knox Goes Away', 'Michael Keaton', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A contract killer, after being diagnosed with a fast-moving form of dementia, is presented with the opportunity to redeem himself by saving the life of his estranged adult son. But to do so, he must race against the police closing in on him as well as the ticking clock of his own rapidly deteriorating mind.', 114, 'Michael Keaton, Al Pacino, Marcia Gay Harden, James Marsden, Suzy Nakamura', '2024-03-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/w39qKYjltCix18BwtoZ1e45usdb.jpg', '', '', '', 6.9, 0, 0),
(2513, 'Eddington', 'Ari Aster', 'Western, Comedy, Thriller', 'United States of America, Finland', 'en', 'In May of 2020, a standoff between a small-town sheriff and mayor sparks a powder keg as neighbor is pitted against neighbor in Eddington, New Mexico.', 0, 'Joaquin Phoenix, Pedro Pascal, Emma Stone, Austin Butler, Deirdre O\'Connell', '2025-07-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xxXKlECD5PIrszc1i8nKbaI3jpp.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2514, 'Love Lies Bleeding', 'Rose Glass', 'Crime, Romance, Horror, Thriller, Action', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'Reclusive gym manager Lou falls hard for Jackie, an ambitious bodybuilder headed through town to Las Vegas in pursuit of her dream. But their love ignites violence, pulling them deep into the web of Lou’s criminal family.', 104, 'Kristen Stewart, Katy O\'Brian, Ed Harris, Dave Franco, Jena Malone', '2024-03-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p7jyFWiLyHPttqYBFAlLJwtYTYH.jpg', '', '', '', 6.566, 0, 0),
(2515, 'Chaos: The Manson Murders', 'Errol Morris', 'Documentary, Crime', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In August 1969, Charles Manson\'s followers killed seven people on his orders. Why? Explore a conspiracy of mind control, CIA experiments, and murder.', 96, 'Charles Manson, Stephen Kay, Tom O\'Neill, Gregg Jakobson, Bobby Beausoleil', '2025-03-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lcWOKxTVZybE8aRUhzkKokU2s0s.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
(2516, 'Snack Shack', 'Adam Rehmeier', 'Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Inseparable best friends AJ and Moose decide to run the local pool\'s snack shack after their plan to sell home-brewed beer goes down the drain. Things take a turn when they meet Brooke, an effortlessly cool lifeguard who puts their big plans, and friendship, at risk.', 112, 'Conor Sherry, Gabriel LaBelle, Mika Abdalla, Nick Robinson, David Costabile', '2024-03-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wCXd5tpUSc12LVPd2oN9OKU1EVQ.jpg', '', '', '', 7.153, 0, 0),
(2517, 'Outside', 'Carlo Ledesma', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'A family retreats to an isolated farm during a zombie outbreak, but years of painful secrets take a toll as they navigate their desolate world.', 142, 'Sid Lucero, Beauty Gonzalez, Marco Masa, Aiden Patdu, James Blanco', '2024-10-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e2YYJYZrQkodvMGfgdSUH5LBPpr.jpg', '', '', '', 6.112, 0, 0),
(2518, 'Kalki 2898-AD', 'Nag Ashwin', 'Drama, Action, Fantasy, Science Fiction', 'India', 'te', 'In the year 2898 AD, around 6000 years after Kurukshetra war, Ashwatthama gears up for his final battle of redemption at the sign of hope in a dystopian world and Bhairava, a wisecracking and self-interested bounty hunter, tired of the perilous life becomes the hurdle in the process.', 176, 'Amitabh Bachchan, Prabhas, Deepika Padukone, Kamal Haasan, Saswata Chatterjee', '2024-06-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rstcAnBeCkxNQjNp3YXrF6IP1tW.jpg', '', '', '', 6.4, 0, 0),
(2519, 'The Killer', 'John Woo', 'Action, Thriller, Crime', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'Zee is a feared contract killer known as \"the Queen of the Dead,\" but when she refuses to murder a young blind woman, she finds herself hunted both by criminal colleagues and a determined police detective.', 126, 'Nathalie Emmanuel, Omar Sy, Sam Worthington, Diana Silvers, Saïd Taghmaoui', '2024-08-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6PCnxKZZIVRanWb710pNpYVkCSw.jpg', '', '', '', 6.386, 0, 0),
(2520, 'Creation of the Gods II: Demon Force', 'Wuershan', 'Action, Fantasy, War', 'China', 'zh', 'Taishi Wen Zhong led the army of Shang Dynasty including Deng Chanyu and four generals of the Mo Family to Xiqi. With the help of Kunlun immortals such as Jiang Ziya, Ji Fa led the army and civilians of Xiqi to defend their homeland.', 145, 'Huang Bo, Yu Shi, Nashi, Chen Muchi, Kris Phillips', '2025-01-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kHII3r0PZ0nEGeSTSuhfAM2q1tI.jpg', '', '', '', 6.383, 0, 0),
(2521, 'Sound of Freedom', 'Alejandro Monteverde', 'Action, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'The story of Tim Ballard, a former US government agent, who quits his job in order to devote his life to rescuing children from global sex traffickers.', 131, 'Jim Caviezel, Mira Sorvino, Bill Camp, Gerardo Taracena, Kurt Fuller', '2023-07-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qA5kPYZA7FkVvqcEfJRoOy4kpHg.jpg', '', '', '', 7.992, 0, 0),
(2522, 'COLORFUL STAGE! The Movie: A Miku Who Can\'t Sing', 'Hiroyuki Hata', 'Animation, Music, Drama, Science Fiction', 'Japan', 'ja', 'Ichika is a high school musician who can enter a mysterious place called “SEKAI,” where she and her friends express their innermost emotions through music alongside Hatsune Miku. One day after giving a live performance, Ichika meets a new Miku that she has never seen before. No matter how hard this new Miku tries to sing, she struggles connecting with the hearts of her listeners. Miku must rely on the help of others to find a way to sing again.', 105, 'Saki Fujita, Asami Shimoda, Yuu Asakawa, Meiko Haigou, Naoto Fuga', '2025-01-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aUT9on5smRVFub54mJQsRGZURR4.jpg', '', '', '', 9, 0, 0),
(2523, 'The Wandering Earth II', 'Frant Gwo', 'Science Fiction', 'China', 'zh', 'Humans built huge engines on the surface of the earth to find a new home. But the road to the universe is perilous. In order to save earth, young people once again have to step forward to start a race against time for life and death.', 173, 'Andy Lau, Wu Jing, Yi Sha, Zhu Yanmanzi, Li Xuejian', '2023-01-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jAZzFYS36UFT0SKhKVmEY7qShal.jpg', '', '', '', 7.289, 0, 0),
(2524, 'It\'s What\'s Inside', 'Greg Jardin', 'Comedy, Mystery, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A pre-wedding reunion descends into a psychological nightmare for a group of college friends when a surprise guest arrives with a mysterious suitcase.', 105, 'James Morosini, Brittany O\'Grady, David Thompson, Alycia Debnam-Carey, Gavin Leatherwood', '2024-01-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/32Lfs4nbLehgbXI8VTeYg5jgIQt.jpg', '', '', '', 6.401, 0, 0),
(2525, 'Marinette', 'Virginie Verrier', 'Drama, History', 'France', 'fr', 'Based on the biography Ne jamais rien lâcher, the script traces the career of Marinette Pichon over three decades. Born in 1975, she was the pioneer of French women\'s football and one of the greatest stars of that sport in the world. A prodigy discovered at the age of five, she went on to become the first French player to make a career in the United States (men/women combined) and the record holder for the number of goals and selections for the French team (men/women combined). From her childhood, ravaged by an alcoholic and violent father, to the American dream (she was crowned best player and best scorer in the prestigious US league in 2002 and 2003 and \"Most Valuable Player\" in 2003), via her career with the French team, Marinette paints the portrait of a kid from a working-class background who was not destined for such an extraordinary career path...', 104, 'Garance Marillier, Émilie Dequenne, Fred Testot, Sylvie Testud, Alban Lenoir', '2023-06-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aM7o55PKT45q630Qmma1fNu99Cd.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0),
(2526, 'Elio', 'Madeline Sharafian', 'Animation, Family, Adventure, Science Fiction, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Elio, a space fanatic with an active imagination, finds himself on a cosmic misadventure where he must form new bonds with eccentric alien lifeforms, navigate a crisis of intergalactic proportions and somehow discover who he is truly meant to be.', 0, 'Yonas Kibreab, Zoe Saldaña, Jameela Jamil, Brad Garrett, Remy Edgerly', '2025-06-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/w2ARwtc1zoh0pyfwmyhpZHwuXgK.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2527, 'Carl\'s Date', 'Bob Peterson', 'Animation, Adventure, Family, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Carl Fredricksen reluctantly agrees to go on a date with a lady friend—but admittedly has no idea how dating works these days. Ever the helpful friend, Dug steps in to calm Carl\'s pre-date jitters and offer some tried-and-true tips for making friends—if you\'re a dog.', 9, 'Ed Asner, Bob Peterson', '2023-06-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wakoF2UgsEE3fGs5KpuwMWsaNr2.jpg', '', '', '', 7.5, 0, 0),
(2528, 'Megalopolis', 'Francis Ford Coppola', 'Science Fiction, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Genius artist Cesar Catilina seeks to leap the City of New Rome into a utopian, idealistic future, while his opposition, Mayor Franklyn Cicero, remains committed to a regressive status quo, perpetuating greed, special interests, and partisan warfare. Torn between them is socialite Julia Cicero, the mayor’s daughter, whose love for Cesar has divided her loyalties, forcing her to discover what she truly believes humanity deserves.', 138, 'Adam Driver, Giancarlo Esposito, Nathalie Emmanuel, Aubrey Plaza, Shia LaBeouf', '2024-09-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8Sok3HNA3r1GHnK2lCytHyBz1A.jpg', '', '', '', 5.3, 0, 0),
(2529, 'Last Sentinel', 'Tanel Toom', 'Science Fiction, Thriller', 'Estonia, Germany, United Kingdom', 'en', 'Set in the future on a war-ravaged Earth, four exhausted soldiers man Sentinel - a remote military base in a vast ocean that separates two warring continents. While their tour of duty ended three months ago, the relief crew still hasn\'t arrived and as the empty weeks turn to months, paranoia descends, testing relationships to breaking point...', 112, 'Kate Bosworth, Lucien Laviscount, Martin McCann, Thomas Kretschmann, Ben Pullen', '2023-03-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pD1o9B0ibENdNroYrBCQemG2jnr.jpg', '', '', '', 5.406, 0, 0),
(2530, 'Mavka: The Forest Song', 'Oleg Malamuzh', 'Animation, Adventure, Family, Fantasy', 'Ukraine', 'uk', 'Mavka, a Soul of the Forest, faces an impossible choice between love and her duty as Guardian of the Heart of the Forest when she falls for a human, a talented young musician named Lukas.', 99, 'Natalka Denysenko, Artem Pyvovarov, Nazar Zadniprovskyi, Oleh Skrypka, Olena Kravets', '2023-03-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eeJjd9JU2Mdj9d7nWRFLWlrcExi.jpg', '', '', '', 7.178, 0, 0),
