(2538, 'Priscilla', 'Sofia Coppola', 'Drama, Romance', 'Italy, United States of America', 'en', 'When teenage Priscilla Beaulieu meets Elvis Presley at a party, the man who is already a meteoric rock-and-roll superstar becomes someone entirely unexpected in private moments: a thrilling crush, an ally in loneliness, a vulnerable best friend.', 113, 'Cailee Spaeny, Jacob Elordi, Ari Cohen, Dagmara Dominczyk, Tim Post', '2023-10-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uDCeELWWpsNq7ErM61Yuq70WAE9.jpg', 'Volpi Cup for Best Actress', '', 'The Masked Singer Brasil 1, 80th Venice International Film Festival', 6.8, 0, 0),
(2539, 'Freedom', 'Mélanie Laurent', 'Action, Romance, Drama', 'France', 'fr', 'Inspired by the true events of one of France\'s most notorious non-violent robbers, Bruno Sulak, in the 1980s. He led multiple heists, then captured public attention for his many daring escapes from police custody...always to reunite with his beloved lover and accomplice Annie, becoming both France\'s Public Enemy #1 and an icon of Freedom.', 110, 'Lucas Bravo, Yvan Attal, Léa Luce Busato, Steve Tientcheu, David Ayala', '2024-11-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b2YL2kncIqlcDcqly78AsOPJi6r.jpg', 'award', '', 'Eurovision Song Contest 2025', 6.332, 0, 0),
(2540, '28 Years Later', 'Danny Boyle', 'Horror, Thriller, Science Fiction', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'It\'s been almost three decades since the rage virus escaped a biological weapons laboratory, and now, still in a ruthlessly enforced quarantine, some have found ways to exist amidst the infected. One such group of survivors lives on a small island connected to the mainland by a single, heavily-defended causeway. When one of the group leaves the island on a mission into the dark heart of the mainland, he discovers secrets, wonders, and horrors that have mutated not only the infected but other survivors as well.', 0, 'Jodie Comer, Aaron Taylor-Johnson, Jack O\'Connell, Alfie Williams, Ralph Fiennes', '2025-06-18', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hVKHzr4GwSw0FepqhqQ0DDiYHNY.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
