(2549, 'Black Clover: Sword of the Wizard King', 'Ayataka Tanemura', 'Animation, Fantasy, Action, Adventure', 'Japan', 'ja', 'As a lionhearted boy who can\'t wield magic strives for the title of Wizard King, four banished Wizard Kings of yore return to crush the Clover Kingdom.', 113, 'Gakuto Kajiwara, Nobunaga Shimazaki, Junichi Suwabe, Kana Yuuki, Toshihiko Seki', '2023-06-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9YEGawvjaRgnyW6QVcUhFJPFDco.jpg', '', '', '', 8.158, 0, 0),
