(2567, 'Baki Hanma VS Kengan Ashura', 'Toshiki Hirano', 'Animation, Action, Fantasy', 'Japan', 'ja', 'It\'s the ultimate showdown. The toughest fighters from \"Baki Hanma\" and \"Kengan Ashura\" clash in this unprecedented, hard-hitting martial arts crossover.', 60, 'Nobunaga Shimazaki, Tatsuhisa Suzuki', '2024-06-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/etbHJxil0wHvYOCmibzFLsMcl2C.jpg', '', '', '', 7.471, 0, 0),
(2568, 'Hounds of War', 'Isaac Florentine', 'Action, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After a mission goes wrong, only one of a group of mercenaries is left alive to avenge his fallen brothers.', 94, 'Frank Grillo, Robert Patrick, Rhona Mitra, Leeshon Alexander, Urs Rechn', '2024-08-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tLdUPi2h6LGmF5foza0a5PXtQRr.jpg', '', '', '', 6.3, 0, 0),
(2569, 'Shape of My Heart', 'Shinji Imaoka', 'Romance', 'Japan', 'ja', 'A romance about a man and a woman who, due to an unexpected event, end up switching bodies. Despite coming from completely different backgrounds and environments, the two try to overcome the various difficulties that arise from their body swap.', 91, 'Keisuke Koide, Kei Fubuki, Manami Shindo, Yohta Kawase, Kotaro Tanaka', '2024-07-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oeCzME5oxy9nauVtnHD8Eg9fJhq.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(2570, 'Exorcism in Utero', 'Erik Skybak', 'Horror', '', 'en', 'Herma finds a powerful ring that possesses her when she tries it on; as her body transforms and mind begins to deteriorate, she must find a way out to save herself and her unborn baby.', 88, 'Allegra Sweeney, Calvin Morie McCarthy, Neil Green, Sam Bangs', '2023-05-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7HKgVo8jBISdqxtn4h9CnEgFrKh.jpg', '', '', '', 5.7, 0, 0),
(2571, 'Premalu', 'Girish A. D.', 'Romance, Comedy', 'India', 'ml', 'Sachin, a carefree graduate, crosses paths with Reenu, a spirited IT professional, in Hyderabad. As their friendship deepens, unspoken feelings, career ambitions and life choices challenge their bond.', 155, 'Naslen, Mamitha Baiju, Sangeeth Prathap, Shyam Mohan, Akhila Bhargavan', '2024-02-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uPpmBjY3znUqGY8kYwI5xvOrSc0.jpg', '', '', '', 7.7, 0, 0),
(2572, 'Saint-Exupéry', 'Pablo Agüero', 'Drama, History, Adventure', 'Belgium, France', 'fr', 'The story takes us back to 1930 and centres around Antoine de Saint-Exupéry, an Airmail pilot in Argentina. When his best friend who happens to be Airmail’s best pilot Henri Guillaumet disappears in the Andes, Saint-Ex decides to set out in search of him, against all odds. This impossible quest forces him to push beyond his limits, turning his capacity to dream into his greatest strength...', 0, 'Louis Garrel, Vincent Cassel, Diane Kruger, Sergej Onopko, Blanche Redouloux', '2024-12-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1DBZpPdoLbBd0pfK7nFa6NtqzJG.jpg', '', '', '', 5.6, 0, 0),
(2573, 'Perfect Addiction', 'Castille Landon', 'Drama, Romance', 'Germany, Switzerland, United States of America', 'en', 'A female boxing trainer discovers that her champion cage-fighter boyfriend has been cheating on her with her sister and decides to seek revenge by training up his arch-rival to challenge him.', 97, 'Kiana Madeira, Ross Butler, Matthew Noszka, Bree Winslow, Nicholas Duvernay', '2023-02-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ucO3NFIvMff71cBRR5EgYXPKWMC.jpg', '', '', '', 6.778, 0, 0),
(2574, 'The Animal Kingdom', 'Thomas Cailley', 'Adventure, Drama, Science Fiction', 'Belgium, France', 'fr', 'In a world hit by a wave of mutations transforming humans into animals, François does everything he can to save his wife. As some of the creatures disappear into a nearby forest, he and their son Émile embark on a quest that will change their lives forever.', 127, 'Romain Duris, Paul Kircher, Adèle Exarchopoulos, Tom Mercier, Billie Blain', '2023-10-04', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/39AiQnXlXOjoqBSkiUpTG80rXLw.jpg', '', 'César Award for Best Film, César Award for Best Director, César Award for Best Original Screenplay, César Award for Best Male Revelation, César Award for Best Actor, César Award for Best Sound, César Award for Best Music Written for a Film, César Award for Best Cinematography, César Award for Best Editing, César Award for Best Costume Design, César Award for Best Production Design, César Award for Best Visual Effects', '', 6.996, 0, 0),
(2575, 'Monkey Man', 'Dev Patel', 'Action, Thriller, Crime', 'Canada, Singapore, United States of America', 'en', 'Kid is an anonymous young man who ekes out a meager living in an underground fight club where, night after night, wearing a gorilla mask, he is beaten bloody by more popular fighters for cash. After years of suppressed rage, Kid discovers a way to infiltrate the enclave of the city’s sinister elite. As his childhood trauma boils over, his mysteriously scarred hands unleash an explosive campaign of retribution to settle the score with the men who took everything from him.', 121, 'Dev Patel, Sikandar Kher, Makrand Deshpande, Pitobash, Vipin Sharma', '2024-04-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4lhR4L2vzzjl68P1zJyCH755Oz4.jpg', '', '', '', 6.901, 0, 0),
(2576, 'Totally Killer', 'Nahnatchka Khan', 'Horror, Comedy, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When the infamous \"Sweet Sixteen Killer\" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.', 105, 'Kiernan Shipka, Olivia Holt, Troy Leigh-Anne Johnson, Kelcey Mawema, Jonathan Potts', '2023-09-28', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/52YBwGJ3cJs54fpBzwnT1lnqgTo.jpg', '', '', '', 6.831, 0, 0),
(2577, 'The Strangers: Chapter 1', 'Renny Harlin', 'Horror, Thriller', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'After their car breaks down in an eerie small town, a young couple are forced to spend the night in a remote cabin. Panic ensues as they are terrorized by three masked strangers who strike with no mercy and seemingly no motives.', 91, 'Madelaine Petsch, Froy Gutierrez, Gabriel Basso, Ema Horvath, Richard Brake', '2024-05-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oYsCNpW4k7Pd7ac3uQfBhr2ihtW.jpg', '', '', '', 5.758, 0, 0),
(2578, 'Death Whisperer', 'Taweewat Wantha', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Thailand', 'th', 'When a remote village is plagued by a deadly curse, one brother must fight to save his family from a terrifying supernatural threat.', 121, 'Nadech Kugimiya, Kajbhunditt Jaidee, Peerakrit Phacharaboonyakiat, Denise Jelilcha Kapaun, Rattanawadee Wongtong', '2023-10-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/48TDjSJpCdJ4SBOHZX3G5IjaV02.jpg', '', '', '', 7.5, 0, 0),
(2579, 'Squid Game: Fireplace', 'Desconocido', '', 'South Korea', 'xx', 'Come share a toast in the Front Man\'s lair — but tread carefully, for you’re playing with fire.', 60, '', '2024-12-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cIIMvxLztRs1MbXH0oqaw3SGV0q.jpg', '', '', '', 6.139, 0, 0),
(2580, 'Big World', 'Yang Lina', 'Drama, Family', 'China', 'zh', 'Liu Chunhe, suffering from cerebral palsy, bravely breaks through the shackles of body and mind to realize the dream stage for his grandmother, while trying to find the coordinates of his own life. After experiencing a summer transformation, he finally embarked on a new journey.', 131, 'Jackson Yee, Diana Lin, Jiang Qinqin, Zhou Yutong, Liao Xueqiu', '2024-12-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rLj287mA1tp4hZmd69umb1rOZu8.jpg', '', '', '', 7.6, 0, 0),
(2581, 'Wake Up', 'François Simard', 'Horror, Thriller, Action', 'Canada, France', 'en', 'A group of young activists set out to make an environmental statement by vandalizing a home superstore as it closes. But their plan goes terribly wrong when they become trapped inside and must face a deranged security guard with a gruesome passion for primitive hunting. As the night fills with violence and terror, the teenagers find themselves in a desperate fight for their lives.', 80, 'Turlough Convery, Benny O. Arthur, Jacqueline Moré, Thomas Gould, Alessia Yoko Fontana', '2024-05-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/erEAU7ygq2XFjziI3FpAdMajJFZ.jpg', '', '', 'Eurovision Song Contest 2019', 7.059, 0, 0),
(2582, 'Sugar Baby', 'Christian Paolo Lat', 'Romance', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Two high school friends turned sugar babies, who sacrifice everything for each other. Until love gets in the way', 114, 'Azi Acosta, Robb Guinto, Jeffrey Hidalgo, Josef Elizalde, Ralmon Mendoza', '2023-11-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/g9MaTZCsGGXjqF87I8XiFHp8Kby.jpg', '', '', '', 4.5, 0, 0),
(2583, 'Kleks Academy', 'Maciej Kawulski', 'Fantasy, Adventure, Family', 'Poland', 'pl', 'A seemingly ordinary girl finds her way into the eponymous Academy to explore the world of fairy tales, imagination and creativity. With the help of a crazy, talented teacher, she develops her unique abilities and also stumbles upon a clue that will help her unravel the biggest secret of the family...', 130, 'Antonina Litwiniak, Tomasz Kot, Piotr Fronczewski, Sebastian Stankiewicz, Agnieszka Grochowska', '2024-01-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ymbECZscR8BTkdvXziSinMIckAz.jpg', '', '', '', 6.1, 0, 0),
(2584, 'Naughty', 'Dmitriy Suvorov', 'Drama', 'Russia', 'ru', 'Twenty-year-old Elya is a student and a future ecologist. One day, Matvey, the head of a construction company, comes to her university to talk about a development plan on the site of an old forest park. Elya does not hesitate to smash his project to smithereens. Matvey is intrigued by the girl\'s self-confidence and uses his usual methods of influence - he simply tries to \"buy\" her. But Elya doesn\'t need a sponsor. Then Matvey, surprised by her impregnability, offers Elya a bet: seven romantic days according to his rules. If after that the girl still decides to leave, he will refuse to build a skyscraper in the forest park. She agrees when Matvey really suspends the design work. Elya sees herself as something like the heroine of the film Pretty Woman, but Matvey turns out to be not at all the person she imagined.', 109, 'Anastasiya Reznik, Alexander Petrov, Semen Arzumanov, Yan Tsapnik, Anna Churina', '2023-02-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9vUEWR3LjQcPqaev2Rfm5uKvV9i.jpg', '', '', '', 6.294, 0, 0),
(2585, 'Big City Greens the Movie: Spacecation', 'Anna O\'Brian', 'Animation, Family, Comedy, Music, TV Movie', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When thrill-seeker Cricket tricks his family into taking a \"road trip\" in space, chaos in the cosmos quickly ensues. Despite growing frustrations between Cricket and his dad, Bill, the two must learn to appreciate each other\'s unique perspectives in order to prevent Big City from being destroyed by an interstellar disaster.', 82, 'Chris Houghton, Marieve Herington, Bob Joles, Artemis Pebdani, Wendi McLendon-Covey', '2024-06-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wV0nNtlL0nxgse8llRi7SypkCQI.jpg', '', '', '', 7.6, 0, 0),
(2586, 'Distant', 'Josh Gordon', 'Science Fiction, Comedy, Action', 'United States of America, India', 'en', 'After crash-landing on an alien planet, an asteroid miner must contend with the challenges of his new surroundings, while making his way across the harsh terrain to the only other survivor – a woman who is trapped in her escape pod.', 87, 'Anthony Ramos, Naomi Scott, Kristofer Hivju, Zachary Quinto, Izzy Jones', '2024-07-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/czh8HOhsbBUKoKsmRmLQMCLHUev.jpg', '', '', '', 5.922, 0, 0),
(2587, 'Kill', 'Nikhil Nagesh Bhat', 'Action, Crime, Thriller, Drama', 'India', 'hi', 'When an army commando finds out his true love is engaged against her will, he boards a New Dehli-bound train in a daring quest to derail the arranged marriage. But when a gang of knife-wielding thieves begin to terrorize innocent passengers on his train, the commando takes them on, one by one.', 105, 'Lakshya Lalwani, Raghav Juyal, Tanya Maniktala, Ashish Vidhyarthi, Abhishek Chauhan', '2024-07-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m2zXTuNPkywdYLyWlVyJZW2QOJH.jpg', '', '', '', 7.14, 0, 0),
(2588, 'Las corredoras', 'Néstor Montalbano', 'Comedy', 'Argentina', 'es', 'In 1959, in Buenos Aires, Mabel, an employee of a ministry must travel to the field to get a contract signed by the rancher Antonovich. In that solitary house, guarded by a female motorist, she will live unexpected scenarios with intriguing characters that will change forever the course of her life.', 111, 'Diego Capusotto, Carola Reyna, Alejandra Flechner, Alejandro Müller, Eduardo Calvo', '2024-05-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qmGVDQAbcs4wbMQzN6Ax2nSrCCT.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0);
