(2589, 'Crayon Shin-chan the Movie: Our Dinosaur Diary', 'Shinobu Sasaki', 'Animation, Adventure, Comedy, Family', 'Japan', 'ja', 'Follow the friendship between the Nobara family\'s pet dog Shiro and a \"small dinosaur\". Their connection helps the growth of Shinnosuke and the Kusakabe Defense Squad.', 106, 'Yumiko Kobayashi, Miki Narahashi, Toshiyuki Morikawa, Satomi Korogi, Mari Mashiba', '2024-08-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/n7YcOeqPOmvQ2PUatn4UqV5YStj.jpg', '', '', '', 5.6, 0, 0),
(2590, 'Salem\'s Lot', 'Gary Dauberman', 'Horror', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Author Ben Mears returns to his childhood home of Jerusalem\'s Lot only to discover his hometown is being preyed upon by a bloodthirsty vampire.', 113, 'Lewis Pullman, Makenzie Leigh, Jordan Preston Carter, Alfre Woodard, Bill Camp', '2024-10-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j7ncdqBVufydVzVtxmXu8Ago4ox.jpg', '', '', '', 6.171, 0, 0),
(2591, 'Zootopia 2', 'Jared Bush', 'Family, Comedy, Adventure, Animation', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Detectives Judy Hopps and Nick Wilde find themselves on the twisting trail of a mysterious reptile who arrives in Zootopia and turns the mammal metropolis upside down.', 0, 'Ginnifer Goodwin, Jason Bateman, Ke Huy Quan, Fortune Feimster, Idris Elba', '2025-11-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ieaBcDSZBZZY4imyEJmMOdSCeo3.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2592, 'Die Alone', 'Lowell Dean', 'Horror, Thriller, Science Fiction', 'Canada', 'en', 'Lost in a world reclaimed by nature and overrun by mysterious creatures, Ethan, a young man with amnesia navigates the dangerous landscape in search of his lost love Emma.  His journey takes an unexpected turn when he encounters Mae, a hardened and eccentric survivor.  Together, Ethan and Mae face threats both human and otherwise before a fateful encounter with Kai unravels a secret that lies just beyond Ethan\'s fractured memory.', 91, 'Carrie-Anne Moss, Douglas Smith, Frank Grillo, Kimberly-Sue Murray, Jonathan Cherry', '2024-09-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dQdIj2OYELhLzECWONY932wGRxA.jpg', '', '', '', 5.865, 0, 0),
(2593, 'Sweet Release', 'Desconocido', 'Drama', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Ataska and Dyessa Garcia will take you to a hot and crazy roadtrip perfect for the summer season. Two girl bestfriends and a young man take on a a journey of self-discovery. Along the way, their bond deepens as they explore their sexual desires.', 101, 'Ataska Mercado, Dyessa Garcia, Mhack Morales, Horace Mendoza, Jem Milton', '2024-04-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/blp7kKUbGSNPJyYYHalYEL4n7t1.jpg', '', '', '', 3.9, 0, 0),
(2594, 'Wicked: For Good', 'Jon M. Chu', 'Drama, Fantasy, Romance', 'United States of America', 'en', 'With the Wizard and the entirety of Oz framing her as wicked, Elphaba’s righteous crusade comes into conflict with Glinda’s struggle for power. As a mysterious cyclone brings in an unwitting young outsider, the former friends will soon discover how much their actions have changed each other, and all of Oz, for good. The second part of a two-part feature film adaptation of the Broadway musical phenomenon.', 0, 'Cynthia Erivo, Ariana Grande, Jonathan Bailey, Michelle Yeoh, Jeff Goldblum', '2025-11-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cdlwS7DF4gw9F0jadfPHptuGuCt.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2595, 'House of Ga\'a', 'Bolanle Austen-Peters', 'Action, History', 'Nigeria', 'en', 'At the height of the Oyo Empire, the ferocious Bashorun Ga\'a became more powerful than the kings he enthroned, only to be undone by his own blood.', 120, 'Femi Branch, Mike Afolarin, Funke Akindele, Femi Adebayo, Ibrahim Chatta', '2024-07-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6yK9hmS641NMwRkR1wWAALWI34t.jpg', '', '', '', 5.461, 0, 0),
(2596, 'Making Squid Game: The Challenge', 'Desconocido', 'Documentary', 'United Kingdom', 'en', 'Go behind the scenes and witness how the \"Squid Game\"-inspired reality show transformed from a scripted drama to a cutthroat, nail-biting competition.', 30, 'Nicola Brown, Rikki Finlay, Tim Harcourt, Toni Ireland, Stephen Lambert', '2023-12-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/78yTLvtsMntVN1cLfzBuZj870pe.jpg', '', '', '', 7.152, 0, 0),
(2597, 'The Thicket', 'Elliott Lester', 'Crime, Thriller, Western', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'An innocent young man, Jack, goes on an epic quest to rescue his sister Lula after she has been kidnapped by the violent killer Cut Throat Bill and her gang. To save her, Jack enlists the help of a crafty bounty hunter named Reginald Jones, a grave-digging alcoholic son of an ex-slave, and a street-smart prostitute. The gang tracks Cut Throat Bill into the deadly no-man’s land known as The Big Thicket — a place where blood and chaos reign.', 108, 'Peter Dinklage, Juliette Lewis, Levon Hawke, Leslie Grace, Gbenga Akinnagbe', '2024-09-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ukqWWQrJRgJym6dsTt1x3EwR2Kp.jpg', '', '', '', 6.423, 0, 0),
(2598, 'Kandahar', 'Ric Roman Waugh', 'Action, Thriller', 'United Arab Emirates, United States of America', 'en', 'After his mission is exposed, an undercover CIA operative stuck deep in hostile territory in Afghanistan must fight his way out, alongside his Afghan translator, to an extraction point in Kandahar, all whilst avoiding elite enemy forces and foreign spies tasked with hunting them down.', 119, 'Gerard Butler, Navid Negahban, Travis Fimmel, Ali Fazal, Bahador Foladi', '2023-05-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lCanGgsqF4xD2WA5NF8PWeT3IXd.jpg', '', 'European Film Award for Best Non-European Film', '', 6.829, 0, 0),
(2599, 'Thelma the Unicorn', 'Lynn Wang', 'Animation, Fantasy, Family', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Thelma dreams of being a glamorous unicorn. Then in a rare pink and glitter-filled moment of fate, Thelma\'s wish comes true. She rises to instant international stardom, but at an unexpected cost. After a while, Thelma realizes that she was happier as her ordinary, sparkle-free self. So she ditches her horn, scrubs off her sparkles, and returns home, where her best friend is waiting for her with a hug.', 98, 'Brittany Howard, Will Forte, Jemaine Clement, Edi Patterson, Maliaka Mitchell', '2024-05-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yutiEZ7taGDNau2jGjKIdDwQpDw.jpg', '', '', '', 7.1, 0, 0),
(2600, 'The Well', 'Federico Zampaglione', 'Horror', 'Italy', 'en', 'A young restorer travels to a small village to restore a medieval painting to its former glory. She will put her life in danger due to a curse attached to the painting.', 91, 'Lauren LaVera, Claudia Gerini, Giovanni Lombardo Radice, Linda Zampaglione, Jonathan Dylan King', '2024-08-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8QV86y9ympSjtZfuAeufAeBb9OG.jpg', 'AACTA Award for Best Adapted Screenplay, AACTA Award for Best Actress in a Leading Role, AACTA Award for Best Production Design', 'Academy Award for Best Writing, Original Screenplay, Academy Award for Best Film Editing, AACTA Award for Best Actress in a Leading Role, AACTA Award for Best Production Design, AACTA Award for Best Direction, AACTA Award for Best Film, AACTA Award for Best Editing, AACTA Award for Best Costume Design, AACTA Award for Best Adapted Screenplay, AACTA Award for Best Cinematography, AACTA Award for Best Sound, AACTA Award for Best Original Music Score, International Submission to the Academy Awards, International Submission to the Academy Awards', '1997 Cannes Film Festival', 5.7, 0, 0),
(2601, 'When Evil Lurks', 'Demián Rugna', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Argentina, United States of America', 'es', 'Residents of a small rural town discover that a demon is about to be born among them. They desperately try to escape before the evil is born, but it may be too late.', 100, 'Ezequiel Rodríguez, Demián Salomón, Silvina Sabater, Luis Ziembrowski, Marcelo Michinaux', '2023-10-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iQ7G9LhP7NRRIUM4Vlai3eOxBAc.jpg', 'Sitges Film Festival Best Feature-Length Film award, Q6359153', '', '', 7.271, 0, 0),
(2602, 'Incoming', 'Dave Chernin', 'Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Their first week of high school. The biggest party of the year. Mistakes will be made as four teenage boys navigate a night of mayhem and debauchery.', 92, 'Mason Thames, Ramon Reed, Raphael Alejandro, Isabella Ferreira, Bardia Seiri', '2024-08-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k2ySukuAiAarLns0yttKS3jg85Y.jpg', '', '', '', 6.195, 0, 0),
(2603, 'The Courier', 'Daniel Calparsoro', 'Thriller, Crime', 'Belgium, France, Spain', 'es', 'After shrewdly seizing his chance to join a money-laundering scheme, a modest valet dives into a world of fast cash, fast cars — and an inevitable crash.', 102, 'Arón Piper, María Pedraza, Luis Tosar, Laura Sépul, Nourdin Batán', '2024-01-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1IRKYqQXXleihbzaFXeDU1TdxKP.jpg', '', '', '', 6.461, 0, 0),
(2604, 'The Bad Guys 2', 'Pierre Perifel', 'Family, Comedy, Crime, Animation', 'Japan, United States of America', 'en', 'The now-reformed Bad Guys are trying (very, very hard) to be good, but instead find themselves hijacked into a high-stakes, globe-trotting heist, masterminded by a new team of criminals they never saw coming: The Bad Girls.', 0, 'Sam Rockwell, Marc Maron, Craig Robinson, Anthony Ramos, Awkwafina', '2025-07-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tBrwjBgDC2LXp7TAkn1mxqFm6aD.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2605, 'The Legend of Ochi', 'Isaiah Saxon', 'Fantasy, Adventure, Family', 'Finland, United States of America', 'en', 'In a remote village on the island of Carpathia, a shy farm girl named Yuri is raised to fear an elusive animal species known as ochi. But when Yuri discovers a wounded baby ochi has been left behind, she escapes on a quest to bring him home.', 95, 'Helena Zengel, Finn Wolfhard, Willem Dafoe, Emily Watson, Razvan Stoica', '2025-04-18', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zpc0GlWfkAiiWPXj10FwUxbkUW9.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2606, 'The Last Voyage of the Demeter', 'André Øvredal', 'Fantasy, Horror, Thriller', 'Germany, India, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'The crew of the merchant ship Demeter attempts to survive the ocean voyage from Carpathia to London as they are stalked each night by a merciless presence onboard the ship.', 119, 'Corey Hawkins, Aisling Franciosi, David Dastmalchian, Javier Botet, Liam Cunningham', '2023-08-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nrtbv6Cew7qC7k9GsYSf5uSmuKh.jpg', '', '', '', 6.775, 0, 0),
(2607, 'The Most Beautiful Girl in the World', 'Robert Ronny', 'Comedy, Drama, Romance', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'A playboy stages a dating show to earn his inheritance by granting his father\'s last wish: for his son to marry the most beautiful girl in the world.', 122, 'Reza Rahadian, Sheila Dara, Kevin Julio, Indra Birowo, Jihane Almira', '2025-02-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t8fgC2kom2ZSKP70tGLLvo3aCcD.jpg', '', '', '', 6.5, 0, 0),
