(2654, 'Alienoid: Return to the Future', 'Choi Dong-hoon', 'Action, Fantasy, Adventure', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Ean has a critical mission to return to the future to save everyone. However, she becomes trapped in the distant past while trying to prevent the escape of alien prisoners who are locked up in the bodies of humans. Meanwhile, Muruk, who helps Ean escape various predicaments, is unnerved when he begins sensing the presence of a strange being in his body. Traveling through the centuries, they are trying to prevent the explosion of the haava.', 122, 'Ryu Jun-yeol, Kim Tae-ri, Kim Woo-bin, Lee Ha-nee, Yum Jung-ah', '2024-01-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4RClncz0GTKPZzSAcAalHCw0h3g.jpg', '', '', '', 6.6, 0, 2),
(2655, 'La Dolce Villa', 'Mark Waters', 'Romance, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When his daughter decides to buy a crumbling Tuscan villa, Eric rushes to Italy to talk her out of it — and instead finds beauty, romance and new purpose.', 99, 'Scott Foley, Violante Placido, Maia Reficco, Giuseppe Futia, Simone Luglio', '2025-02-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sEma5RN8aZ5Yu2Dkefyn5ULdlc1.jpg', '', '', '', 6.237, 0, 0),
(2656, 'Lazareth', 'Alec Tibaldi', 'Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Lee is an aunt whose life mission is to protect her orphaned nieces, Imogen and Maeve, from a self-destructing world, raising them in isolation until an outsider threatens their peaceful existence.', 86, 'Ashley Judd, Sarah Pidgeon, Katie Douglas, Asher Angel, Edward Balaban', '2024-05-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/36o8ancoKDKW1sstzMi0YYkQkpU.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(2657, 'Heart of Stone', 'Tom Harper', 'Thriller, Action', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An intelligence operative for a shadowy global peacekeeping agency races to stop a hacker from stealing its most valuable — and dangerous — weapon.', 122, 'Gal Gadot, Jamie Dornan, Alia Bhatt, Sophie Okonedo, Matthias Schweighöfer', '2023-08-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vB8o2p4ETnrfiWEgVxHmHWP9yRl.jpg', '', '', '', 6.785, 0, 0),
(2658, 'Hypnotic', 'Robert Rodriguez', 'Mystery, Thriller, Science Fiction, Action', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'A detective becomes entangled in a mystery involving his missing daughter and a secret government program while investigating a string of reality-bending crimes.', 93, 'Ben Affleck, Alice Braga, William Fichtner, J. D. Pardo, Dayo Okeniyi', '2023-05-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m0mYmlN9AewOGSOl7Q1ZgZvEeUU.jpg', '', '', '', 6.226, 0, 0),
(2659, 'You Are Not Me', 'Marisa Crespo', 'Drama, Horror, Thriller', 'Spain', 'ca', 'After an absence of three years, Aitana makes a surprise return home with Gabi, her Brazilian partner, and their son. The reception from her parents is surprisingly cold. Only her wheelchair-bound brother is pleased to see her. But what affects Aitana most of all is the presence of a stranger her age sleeping in her bed, wearing her clothes, living in her house, and being treated by her parents as if she were their daughter. From that moment on, torn by jealousy, suspicion, and misunderstanding, Aitana tries to find out what is happening and who the intruder is until she discovers an unexpected and disturbing truth darker than she would ever have thought possible.', 98, 'Roser Tapias, Jorge Motos, Pilar Almería, Álvaro Báguena, Alfred Picó', '2024-12-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6bHLAzzTW9KuC4p4RoSHFTnBzox.jpg', '', '', '', 6.9, 0, 0),
(2660, 'Saptha Kandam', 'Prasanth Sasi', 'Drama, Romance', 'India', 'ml', 'In a remote resort, newlyweds Apsara and her husband, Laalu, face a dangerous bet with the wealthy moneylender, Madhavan, who seeks to claim Apsara. Over the course of seven days, Madhavan attempts to seduce her through discussions of an ancient book on lust. Meanwhile, Apsara, determined to remain faithful, battles his advances. The outcome of the bet hinges on her ability to resist his manipulation and maintain her resolve.', 95, 'Sreelakshmi Aravindakshan', '2024-12-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1i35IfvW8bdoOuBF7GWkXBDEFI4.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2661, 'The Lion King at the Hollywood Bowl', 'Paul Dugdale', 'Music', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In honor of “The Lion King\'s” 30th Anniversary, the Hollywood Bowl transforms into the Pride Lands for an immersive concert event. This music event celebrates the franchise\'s evolution, from the 1994 animated film to the Tony Award-winning musical, and the 2019 and 2024 live-action films, honoring the music and characters that made it a global phenomenon.', 68, 'Jennifer Hudson, Nathan Lane, Jeremy Irons, Ernie Sabella, Billy Eichner', '2025-02-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/q0amPqVnEC3uG9H34PSBr8IaVLP.jpg', '', '', '', 6.893, 0, 0),
(2662, 'The Seed of the Sacred Fig', 'Mohammad Rasoulof', 'Drama, Thriller, Crime', 'France, Germany, Iran', 'fr', 'Investigating judge Iman grapples with paranoia amid political unrest in Tehran. When his gun vanishes, he suspects his wife and daughters, imposing draconian measures that strain family ties as societal rules crumble.', 167, 'Misagh Zare, Soheila Golestani, Mahsa Rostami, Setareh Maleki, Niousha Akhshi', '2024-09-18', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ifOazNzv2cNJ5CQjMV7cPXG2Lmy.jpg', '', 'European Film Award for Best Film, Academy Award for Best International Feature Film', '', 7.6, 0, 0),
(2663, 'F1', 'Joseph Kosinski', 'Action, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Racing legend Sonny Hayes is coaxed out of retirement to lead a struggling Formula 1 team—and mentor a young hotshot driver—while chasing one more chance at glory.', 0, 'Brad Pitt, Damson Idris, Kerry Condon, Javier Bardem, Kim Bodnia', '2025-06-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6H6p82aWQFEKEuVUiZll6JxV8Ft.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2664, 'Flies', 'Aritz Moreno', 'Thriller', 'Argentina, Spain', 'es', 'Mr. Machi is a businessman fond of luxuries, easy money and women. A despicable person who abuses his power and position, but suddenly finds himself in an extreme situation: one morning, in broad daylight, he punctures a tire. But his surprise comes when he discovers the disfigured corpse of a stranger in his trunk.  Someone has set a trap for him. There he begins a desperate route to get rid of the body, discover his identity and know who is behind all this. One of the many enemies that he has cultivated over the years, from his own wife to co-workers, bodyguards and politicians. It could have been any of those that he has stepped on during these years to continue climbing or to consolidate his power, because for Luis Machi, people are so insignificant that from afar they look like flies.', 97, 'Ernesto Alterio, Mara Bestelli, Claudio Rissi, Tomás Pozzi, Gabriel Fernández', '2023-10-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/x9N3Ve9inJAHIF8vYHpm4hdUdBH.jpg', '', '', '', 6.5, 0, 0),
(2665, 'The Killer', 'David Fincher', 'Crime, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After a fateful miss, an assassin battles his employers, and himself, on an international manhunt he insists isn\'t personal.', 118, 'Michael Fassbender, Tilda Swinton, Charles Parnell, Arliss Howard, Kerry O\'Malley', '2023-10-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e7Jvsry47JJQruuezjU2X1Z6J77.jpg', '', '', '', 6.572, 0, 0),
(2666, 'Tayuan', 'Topel Lee', 'Drama, Romance', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Ella, an events project manager, usually takes a private transportation service. However, she is forced to take a bus, where bus conductor Rico becomes aroused when her body gets pressed into him due to the thick crowd.  This encounter deeply affects Ella, and from that night on, she starts pursuing Rico. Even after discovering that Rico already has a live-in partner and a daughter, Ella doesn’t care at all and she’ll do anything to make him want her just as much.', 101, 'Angeli Khang, Stephanie Raz, Chester Grecia, Francine Garcia, Rash Flores', '2023-06-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5eX2JxR8djmoPBQhU0327uehqBf.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(2667, '172 Days', 'Hadrah Daeng Ratu', 'Drama, Romance', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'A young woman with a troubled past turns to religion as she seeks purpose in life — and a chance at finding true love.', 103, 'Yasmin Napper, Bryan Domani, Abun Sungkar, Yoriko Angeline, Amara Sophie', '2023-11-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pbeSOr5ODJMHMzR4hbLXhnHNs1S.jpg', '', '', '', 5.655, 0, 0),
(2668, 'Santa Isn\'t Real', 'Zac Locke', 'Horror', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After suffering a brutal attack on Christmas Eve, Nikki struggles to convince her friends that the assailant was none other than Ol\' Kris Kringle. When Santa returns to terrorize the group in their remote cabin the next Christmas, Nikki and her friends must overcome disbelief as they fight to stay alive.', 76, 'Scarlett Sperduto, Kaya Coleman, Dana Millican, Cissy Ly, Michelle Damis', '2023-12-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pDRZgeTeefpled1CIRLxdXPgXcv.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0),
(2669, 'Resident Evil: Death Island', 'Eiichirō Hasumi', 'Animation, Action, Horror', 'Japan', 'ja', 'In San Francisco, Jill Valentine is dealing with a zombie outbreak and a new T-Virus, Leon Kennedy is on the trail of a kidnapped DARPA scientist, and Claire Redfield is investigating a monstrous fish that is killing whales in the bay. Joined by Chris Redfield and Rebecca Chambers, they discover the trail of clues from their separate cases all converge on the same location, Alcatraz Island, where a new evil has taken residence and awaits their arrival.', 91, 'Matthew Mercer, Nicole Tompkins, Kevin Dorman, Stephanie Panisello, Erin Cahill', '2023-06-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qayga07ICNDswm0cMJ8P3VwklFZ.jpg', '', '', '', 7.3, 0, 0),
(2670, 'Outlaw', 'João Wainer', 'Action, Crime, Drama', 'Brazil', 'pt', 'At the age of nine, Rebeca is sold by her grandmother to the bookseller who ran Rocinha. Disputed by bicheiros and drug dealers, the community is going through changes in power. Rebeca becomes the wife of the chief drug dealer and, with the death of her partner, his successor. The electrifying trajectory of crime, violence, drugs and love of a female drug kingpin in Rocinha, Rio de Janeiro in the 1980s.', 80, 'Maria Bomani, Jean Luís Amorim, Milhem Cortaz, João Vitor Nascimento, Jorge Hissa', '2024-06-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rGS8SzheANVQicNba0GCE6w1XHb.jpg', 'Robert Award for Best Short Television Series', '', '', 6.196, 0, 0),
(2671, 'The Iron Claw', 'Sean Durkin', 'History, Drama', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'The true story of the inseparable Von Erich brothers, who made history in the intensely competitive world of professional wrestling in the early 1980s. Through tragedy and triumph, under the shadow of their domineering father and coach, the brothers seek larger-than-life immortality on the biggest stage in sports.', 132, 'Zac Efron, Jeremy Allen White, Harris Dickinson, Stanley Simons, Holt McCallany', '2023-12-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lsdismtCDga4vsKnmliz0h7CaZT.jpg', '', '', '', 7.542, 0, 0),
(2672, 'Here', 'Robert Zemeckis', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An odyssey through time and memory, centered on a place in New England where—from wilderness, and then, later, from a home—love, loss, struggle, hope and legacy play out between couples and families over generations.', 105, 'Tom Hanks, Robin Wright, Paul Bettany, Kelly Reilly, Ellis Grunsell', '2024-10-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/79euHUJJtfgeGU63ef38KtNjXEn.jpg', '', '', '', 6.653, 0, 0),
(2673, 'Night Swim', 'Bryce McGuire', 'Horror', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Forced into early retirement by a degenerative illness, former baseball player Ray Waller moves into a new house with his wife and two children. He hopes that the backyard swimming pool will be fun for the kids and provide physical therapy for himself. However, a dark secret from the home\'s past soon unleashes a malevolent force that drags the family into the depths of inescapable terror.', 98, 'Wyatt Russell, Kerry Condon, Amélie Hoeferle, Gavin Warren, Nancy Lenehan', '2024-01-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gSkfBGdxdialBMM7P02V4hcI6Ij.jpg', '', '', '', 5.548, 0, 0),
(2674, 'Vikings: Battle of Heirs', 'Robin Keane', 'Action', 'United Kingdom', 'en', 'A young Viking must come to terms with the realization that he may be the King\'s son, who was switched at birth, but not before others try to take his rightful place.', 82, 'Amber Doig-Thorne, Iris Papas, Gaston Alexander, Christabel Clark, Nazeku', '2023-04-28', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/87goLbbqrJqAxqDS5cBsik1zKT.jpg', '', '', '', 5.962, 0, 0),
(2675, 'Imaginary', 'Jeff Wadlow', 'Horror, Mystery', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When Jessica moves back into her childhood home with her family, her youngest stepdaughter Alice develops an eerie attachment to a stuffed bear named Chauncey she finds in the basement. Alice starts playing games with Chauncey that begin playful and become increasingly sinister. As Alice’s behavior becomes more and more concerning, Jessica intervenes only to realize Chauncey is much more than the stuffed toy bear she believed him to be.', 104, 'DeWanda Wise, Taegen Burns, Pyper Braun, Betty Buckley, Tom Payne', '2024-03-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bPCxkrCEGJmaYfvdXj0x3mCLbGr.jpg', '', '', '', 5.979, 0, 0),
(2676, 'Winter Spring Summer or Fall', 'Tiffany Paulsen', 'Comedy, Romance, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Remi and Barnes, two very different teenagers, meet by chance in the winter of their senior year, then spend four  days together over the course of a year that will change their lives forever.', 97, 'Jenna Ortega, Percy Hynes White, Adam Rodriguez, Marisol Nichols, Elias Kacavas', '2024-12-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eqtMRn27ztlRbFRvfHI9SXHSOns.jpg', '', '', '', 9.7, 0, 0),
(2677, 'Verano en diciembre', 'Carolina África', 'Comedy', 'Spain', 'es', '', 0, 'Carmen Machi, Bárbara Lennie, Irene Escolar, Victoria Luengo, Beatriz Grimaldos', '2024-11-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xUJecKzNuaL5CCqO6MS7V4S7oBI.jpg', '', '', '', 5.909, 0, 0),
(2678, 'Smugglers', 'Ryoo Seung-wan', 'Crime, Action', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'During the 1970s, in Kunchon, there were women divers who were able to dive without equipment, including two best friends Choon-ja and Jin-sook, Jin-sook\'s brother and Hammer. They always collected seafood under water for living. But, as fewer factories started to be built near the beach, the women divers started to have trouble with what they were doing for living. Without any choice, the ship crews decided to join the smuggling business in the water to seek a way for their living. But the smuggling business in their village got too big for Jin-sook\'s family to handle and the peaceful village was gradually broken.', 129, 'Kim Hye-soo, Yum Jung-ah, Zo In-sung, Park Jeong-min, Kim Jong-soo', '2023-07-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j8Jx4vpBG258jPxd4o0kOLDwTvm.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0);
