(2740, 'The American', 'James Napier Robertson', 'Drama', 'New Zealand, Poland, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'American ballet dancer Joy Womack is accepted into Moscow\'s infamously tough Bolshoi Ballet Academy, with the dream of becoming a great ballerina.', 110, 'Talia Ryder, Diane Kruger, Oleg Ivenko, Natasha Alderslade, Natalia Osipova', '2023-11-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7dNpUdJHjCue7H22jQR1NIX1kou.jpg', '', '', '', 6.8, 0, 0),
