(2742, 'The Deliverance', 'Lee Daniels', 'Horror, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Ebony Jackson, a struggling single mother fighting her personal demons, moves her family into a new home for a fresh start. But when strange occurrences inside the home raise the suspicions of Child Protective Services and threaten to tear the family apart, Ebony soon finds herself locked in a battle for her life and the souls of her children.', 112, 'Andra Day, Glenn Close, Anthony B. Jenkins, Caleb McLaughlin, Demi Singleton', '2024-08-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/og1FteMFRInoQnlZeWqEn8XpXHh.jpg', '', '', '', 6.056, 0, 0),
(2743, 'Petak Umpet', 'Rizal Mantovani', 'Horror', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'When he can\'t find his sister after she plays hide-and-seek, an older brother must search a decrepit house cursed by a malevolent presence.', 91, 'Randy Martin, Saskia Chadwick, Alesha Fadillah, Adam Farrel, Putri Ayudya', '2024-11-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bJ2qLAEP3ZbA1NCJngPhHICJIqM.jpg', '', '', '', 4.7, 0, 0),
(2744, 'Chhorii 2', 'Vishal Furia', 'Horror, Drama', 'India', 'hi', 'Sakshi must rescue her seven year old daughter from being sacrificed by an evil cult to satisfy their resident leader, while fighting societal superstitions and the horror that continues to haunt her and young women around her.', 133, 'Nushrratt Bharuccha, Soha Ali Khan, Pallavi Patil, Saurabh Goyal, Shyam Gopal', '2025-04-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fnbJbisEy4zoCecirO4WNje6opw.jpg', '', '', '', 4, 0, 0),
(2745, 'The Flood', 'Brandon Slagle', 'Action, Mystery, Thriller, Horror', 'Thailand, United States of America', 'en', 'A horde of giant hungry alligators is unleashed on a group of in-transit prisoners and their guards after a massive hurricane floods Louisiana.', 93, 'Nicky Whelan, Casper Van Dien, Louis Mandylor, Devanny Pinn, Randy Wayne', '2023-07-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mvjqqklMpHwOxc40rn7dMhGT0Fc.jpg', '', '', '', 6.295, 0, 0),
(2746, 'Watchmen: Chapter I', 'Brandon Vietti', 'Animation, Drama, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In 1985, the murder of a government-sponsored superhero draws his outlawed colleagues out of retirement and into a mystery that threatens to upend their personal lives and the world itself.', 84, 'Troy Baker, Adrienne Barbeau, Corey Burton, Michael Cerveris, Jeffrey Combs', '2024-08-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tE2vZ6HdlmKaBh0wpsvHCf7HJKo.jpg', '', '', '', 7.6, 0, 0),
(2747, 'The Return', 'Uberto Pasolini', 'History, Drama, Adventure', 'Greece, Italy, United Kingdom, United States of America, France', 'en', 'After twenty years away, Odysseus washes up on the shores of Ithaca, haggard and unrecognizable. The king has finally returned home, but much has changed in his kingdom since he left to fight in the Trojan war.', 116, 'Ralph Fiennes, Juliette Binoche, Charlie Plummer, Marwan Kenzari, Claudio Santamaria', '2024-09-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xSj6EbdwHs3MFT2tRj9L3I7TE5j.jpg', 'PEN/Jean Stein Book Award, Golden Lion, Tromsø International Film Festival\'s audience award, European Film Award for European Discovery of the Year', 'IFFR audience award, European Film Award for European Discovery of the Year, International Submission to the Academy Awards', '', 6.536, 0, 0),
(2748, 'The Girl Who Escaped: The Kara Robinson Story', 'Simone Stock', 'Thriller, Drama, Crime, TV Movie', 'United States of America', 'en', 'The true story of how Kara Robinson was kidnapped, assaulted and held captive for 18 hours, 15-year-old Kara Robinson plots a daring escape from a serial killer\'s apartment.', 88, 'Katie Douglas, Cara Buono, Kristian Bruun, Erik Athavale, Lisa Marie DiGiacinto', '2023-02-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o9hwOE1FeOelkNxfsGtTNrlWnyq.jpg', '', '', '', 7.224, 0, 0),
(2749, 'Silent Love', 'Eiji Uchida', 'Romance, Drama', 'Japan', 'ja', 'A silent love story of a young man who wishes to make the dream come true of a young woman who lost her light.', 116, 'Arata Furuta, Minami Hamabe, Wan Marui, Ayumu Nakajima, SWAY', '2024-01-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bdV2jUZuSThWZsmjgEsZk0vp9NW.jpg', '', '', '', 7.3, 0, 0),
(2750, 'The Quest for Tom Sawyer\'s Gold', 'Kirk Harris', 'Adventure, Family', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Agatha Armstrong and her trusty sidekick Mrs. Mac were once the world’s most daring adventurers. But when her son Ant came along, everything quickly changed and her devil-may-care ways took a backseat to being over-protective and terrified of anything that posed a risk to her family.', 88, 'Stephen A. Elkins, Max Purget, Bobby Ray Thompson III, Joey Lauren Adams, Patrick Muldoon', '2023-06-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zceLrHeYOgJHw1tw6MUi15N2NUz.jpg', '', '', '', 5.239, 0, 0),
(2751, 'Game Changer', 'Shankar', 'Action, Drama', 'India', 'te', 'Ram, a newly appointed district collector, takes charge in a city in Andhra Pradesh and immediately confronts the deeply entrenched corruption and inefficiency plaguing the government. Determined to bring reforms, he initiates sweeping changes, sparking a fierce conflict with a powerful state Minister.', 164, 'Ram Charan, Anjali, Kiara Advani, S. J. Suryah, Srikanth', '2025-01-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qtOGsZoLW7QceqKmsOy5nSM6Aik.jpg', '', '', '', 4.654, 0, 0),
(2752, 'One Battle After Another', 'Paul Thomas Anderson', 'Crime, Action, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When their evil nemesis resurfaces after 16 years, a band of ex-revolutionaries reunite to rescue the daughter of one of their own.', 170, 'Leonardo DiCaprio, Sean Penn, Benicio del Toro, Regina Hall, Teyana Taylor', '2025-09-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7U8V3o2585Q9m04wU9yUOjYflQF.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2753, 'White Snake: Afloat', 'Chen Jianxi', 'Animation, Romance, Comedy, Fantasy', 'China', 'zh', 'Xiaobai finally found Xu Xian, the reincarnation of Axuan, after 500 years, the two met on the Broken Bridge. Xiaobai and sister hid in the streets and alleys, started a lively life in human world with him and his brother-in-law Li Gongfu.', 133, 'Zhang Zhe, Yang Tianxiang, Tang Xiaoxi, Zhang He, Liu Cong', '2024-07-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7tltIsVonubKCBUVpzsfaK4FaDF.jpg', '', '', '', 7.824, 0, 0),
(2754, 'The Last Showgirl', 'Gia Coppola', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When the glittering Las Vegas revue she has headlined for decades announces it will soon close, a glamorous showgirl must reconcile with the decisions she’s made and the community she has built as she plans her next act.', 89, 'Pamela Anderson, Jamie Lee Curtis, Dave Bautista, Brenda Song, Kiernan Shipka', '2024-12-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o70dV2jjGd6TmYTMOY9b34OLzDK.jpg', '', '', '', 6.557, 0, 0),
(2755, 'Flamin\' Hot', 'Eva Longoria', 'Drama, History', 'United States of America', 'en', 'The inspiring true story of Richard Montañez, the Frito Lay janitor who channeled his Mexican American heritage and upbringing to turn the iconic Flamin\' Hot Cheetos into a snack that disrupted the food industry and became a global pop culture phenomenon.', 99, 'Jesse Garcia, Annie Gonzalez, Emilio Rivera, Vanessa Martinez, Dennis Haysbert', '2023-03-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a7KyFMPXj0iY4EoLq1PIGU1WJPw.jpg', '', '', '', 7.948, 0, 0),
(2756, 'Sakra', 'Donnie Yen', 'Action', 'China, Hong Kong', 'cn', 'Qiao Feng is the respected leader of a roving band of martial artists. After he is wrongfully accused of murder and subsequently exiled, Qiao Feng goes on the run in search of answers about his own mysterious origin story—and the unknown enemies working to destroy him from the shadows.', 130, 'Donnie Yen, Yukee Chen, Liu Yase, Kara Wai Ying-Hung, Wu Yue', '2023-01-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2vA3CqwZ01LUsEaYRz2ZY6Om9xi.jpg', '', '', '', 6.423, 0, 0),
(2757, 'The Promised Land', 'Nikolaj Arcel', 'Action, Drama, History', 'Denmark, Germany, Sweden', 'da', 'Denmark, 1755. Captain Ludvig Kahlen sets out to conquer a Danish heath reputed to be uncultivable, with an impossible goal: to establish a colony in the name of the king, in exchange for a royal title. A single-minded ambition that the ruthless lord of the region will relentlessly seek to put down. Kahlen\'s fate hangs in the balance: will his endevours bring him wealth and honour, or cost him his life...?', 127, 'Mads Mikkelsen, Amanda Collin, Simon Bennebjerg, Kristine Kujath Thorp, Gustav Lindh', '2023-10-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/npQgoOWn4fnvOIIyTj4rIV80FXC.jpg', 'European Film Award for Best Cinematographer, European Film Award for Best Costume Designer, European Film Award for Best Actor, Robert Award for Best Danish Film, FIPRESCI Award Best Nordic Film, Audience Dragon Award Best Nordic Film, Bodil Award for Best Danish Film', 'Academy Award for Best International Feature Film, International Submission to the Academy Awards, International Submission to the Academy Awards', 'Q89370484', 7.749, 0, 0),
(2758, 'The Love Scam', 'Umberto Riccioni Carteni', 'Comedy, Romance', 'Italy', 'it', 'Drowning in debt, two brothers concoct a plan to scam a wealthy heiress and save their home in Naples — but unexpected love soon complicates the scheme.', 101, 'Antonio Folletto, Laura Adriani, Vincenzo Nemolato, Saverio Picozzi', '2025-01-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kWBjdB6tP71ed4WTFxuqDZnWVk5.jpg', '', '', '', 6.434, 0, 0),
(2759, 'In Youth We Trust', 'Puttipong Nakthong', 'Action, Drama, Crime', 'Thailand', 'th', 'Puek, a boy from the slums, had no choice but to endure his circumstances, feeling that he could never have the same worth as others. He remained silent, accepting the bullying of others just to survive in society.', 132, 'Nat Kitcharit, Arak Amornsupasiri, Itkron Pungkiatrussamee, Benjamin Joseph Varney, Todsapol Maisuk', '2024-11-28', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vQsWKmt2np2BRtW1niifmJVQCJX.jpg', '', '', '', 6.4, 0, 0),
(2760, 'Cobweb', 'Samuel Bodin', 'Horror', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Eight year old Peter is plagued by a mysterious, constant tapping from inside his bedroom wall—one that his parents insist is all in his imagination. As Peter\'s fear intensifies, he believes that his parents could be hiding a terrible, dangerous secret and questions their trustworthiness.', 88, 'Lizzy Caplan, Antony Starr, Cleopatra Coleman, Woody Norman, Luke Busey', '2023-07-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cGXFosYUHYjjdKrOmA0bbjvzhKz.jpg', '', '', '', 6.486, 0, 0),
(2761, 'Daddio', 'Christy Hall', 'Drama', 'United States of America, Luxembourg', 'en', 'A woman taking a cab ride from JFK airport engages in a conversation with the driver about the important relationships in their lives.', 100, 'Dakota Johnson, Sean Penn, Marcos A. Gonzalez, Zora Lloyd, Shannon Gannon', '2024-06-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dyrCsHUhOfpuci51lHcdAnO3db0.jpg', '', '', '', 6.247, 0, 0),
(2762, 'La Leyenda de los Chaneques', 'Marvick Núñez', 'Animation, Comedy, Family, Horror', 'Mexico', 'es', 'Five years after giving up his powers and separating from his friends, Leo San Juan has started a new life trying to focus on his family and their bakery, staying away from danger and adventures. However, Leo knows that his plans are rarely fulfilled and this time is no exception: while traveling with Nando to Veracruz, things start to get weird, and from the depths of the Tuxtlas jungle, an ancient curse has returned and only Leo can face it.', 89, 'Benny Emmanuel, Emilio Treviño, Jorge Rafael, Mayté Cordero, Annie Rojas', '2023-07-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4f9ghI3utknpeBZSAzNuIKKATOA.jpg', '', '', '', 8.366, 0, 0),
(2763, 'The Three Musketeers: D\'Artagnan', 'Martin Bourboulon', 'Adventure, Action, Drama, History', 'Belgium, France, Germany, Spain', 'fr', 'D\'Artagnan, a spirited young Gascon, is left for dead after trying to save a noblewoman from being kidnapped. Once in Paris, he tries by all means to find his attackers, unaware that his quest will lead him to the very heart of a war where the future of France is at stake. Aided by King\'s Musketeers Athos, Porthos and Aramis, he faces the machinations of villainous Cardinal Richelieu and Milady de Winter, while falling in love with Constance, the Queen\'s confidante.', 121, 'François Civil, Vincent Cassel, Romain Duris, Pio Marmaï, Eva Green', '2023-04-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hfExJPcbBtDeFDEb7I1By72Drlr.jpg', '', '', '', 6.957, 0, 0),
(2764, 'Christmas with The Chosen: Holy Night', 'Dallas Jenkins', 'Music', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A young mother labeled impure. A shepherd boy considered “unclean\". Experience Jesus’ birth through their eyes in this blend of \"The Messengers\" and \"The Shepherd\" into one special remastered and re-scored story.', 104, 'Andrea Bocelli, Matteo Bocelli, Jonathan Roumie, Shahar Issac, Noah James', '2023-12-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gW5KgkZZYpiBWrEFT7Zin7hjgWu.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(2765, 'Peter Pan & Wendy', 'David Lowery', 'Family, Fantasy, Action, Adventure', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'Wendy Darling, a young girl afraid to leave her childhood home behind, meets Peter Pan, a boy who refuses to grow up. Alongside her brothers and a tiny fairy, Tinker Bell, she travels with Peter to the magical world of Neverland. There, she encounters an evil pirate captain, Captain Hook, and embarks on a thrilling adventure that will change her life forever.', 106, 'Alexander Molony, Ever Anderson, Jude Law, Yara Shahidi, Alyssa Wapanatâhk', '2023-04-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9NXAlFEE7WDssbXSMgdacsUD58Y.jpg', '', '', '', 5.471, 0, 0),
(2766, 'The Hill', 'Jeff Celentano', 'History, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'The story of Rickey Hill, who overcomes his physical disability and repairs his relationship with his father in a quest to become a major league baseball (MLB) player.', 121, 'Colin Ford, Dennis Quaid, Joelle Carter, Scott Glenn, Siena Bjornerud', '2023-08-18', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gKh28PVUqt1vY2oAdFlauXkDacW.jpg', '', '', '', 7.684, 0, 0),
(2767, 'To Live Through Death', 'Ren Gaoliang', 'Action, Crime', '', 'zh', 'On a certain island in the Pacific, an invincible human-smuggling organization kidnaps and defrauds Chinese people. In order to rescue his kidnapped adopted daughter, the usually taciturn Chen does not hesitate to reveal the secret past he has concealed for twenty years, and joins hands with the local young policeman Can to fight against a huge criminal organization, engaging in a life-or-death battle with evil forces.', 91, 'Louis Fan Siu-Wong, Andy On, Zhao Ziqi, Eleanor Lee, Yu Kang', '2024-07-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bhFurHAxVXS0vPYIPwU2fNGOUHk.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(2768, 'Init', 'Paul Michael Acero', 'Drama', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'When a young barrio lass moves in to the city to study, she lives in a boarding house with other college students. Unknown to them, behind her shy and timid personality is a woman with insatiable hunger for sex.', 49, 'Dyessa Garcia, Candy Veloso, Aica Veloso, Rash Flores, Ghion Layug', '2024-07-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fGY13rtdRzFqTkDMi5JayUWg6vL.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(2769, 'Warhorse One', 'Johnny Strong', 'Action, War, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A gunned down Navy SEAL Master Chief must guide a child to safety through a gauntlet of hostile Taliban insurgents and survive the brutal Afghanistan wilderness.', 125, 'Johnny Strong, Athena Durner, Raj Kala, James Sherrill, Siya Rostami', '2023-06-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1WYSPpjZ0zKr65yQes03QTPCrUh.jpg', '', '', '', 7.266, 0, 0),
(2770, 'Given the Movie: Hiiragi Mix', 'Noriko Hashimoto', 'Animation, Romance', 'Japan', 'ja', 'After Ritsuka Uenoyama hears Mafuyu Sato sing, he invites Mafuyu to join his band. Given auditions for a festival in Shibuya and falls short, though they continue to attract attention. At the same time, Mafuyu’s childhood friends, Shizusumi Yagi and Hiiragi Kashima, prepare to make their debut as the band “syh.” When they lose a guitarist, Hiiragi asks Ritsuka to join them for their big show.', 71, 'Shogo Yano, Takuya Eguchi, Yuma Uchida, Masatomo Nakazawa, Fumiya Imai', '2024-01-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3IvIJhgEzXa0E4wiXbVRxB6iwT1.jpg', '', '', '', 6.286, 0, 0),
(2771, 'How to Have Sex', 'Molly Manning Walker', 'Drama', 'Belgium, France, Greece, United Kingdom', 'en', 'Three British teenage girls go on a rites-of-passage holiday—drinking, clubbing and hooking up, in what should be the best summer of their lives.', 91, 'Mia McKenna-Bruce, Lara Peake, Enva Lewis, Samuel Bottomley, Shaun Thomas', '2023-11-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yQyoFCBLGJH5HXESmJAzaiXw9zU.jpg', 'Un certain regard Award, European Film Award for European Discovery of the Year', 'European Film Award for European Discovery of the Year', '2023 Cannes Film Festival', 6.254, 0, 0);
