(2824, 'Mothers\' Instinct', 'Benoît Delhomme', 'Thriller, Drama', 'Belgium, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'Housewives Alice and Celine are best friends and neighbours who seem to have it all. However, when a tragic accident shatters the harmony of their lives, guilt, suspicion and paranoia begin to unravel their sisterly bond.', 94, 'Anne Hathaway, Jessica Chastain, Anders Danielsen Lie, Josh Charles, Caroline Lagerfelt', '2024-01-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xscMEP5VsvCLxFvrDQD84biWsLA.jpg', '', '', '', 6.921, 0, 0),
(2825, 'Forbidden Fairytale', 'Lee Jong-suk', 'Comedy, Romance', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Dan-bi dreams of becoming a children\'s book author but finds herself starting her career as a rookie member of a Youth Protection Team that blocks illegal pornography. By a twist of fate, she ends up signing an unfair contract with CEO Hwang, a dominant figure in the web erotica industry, and is forced to moonlight writing erotica for him. Struggling with the unfamiliar genre, Dan-bi faces many challenges. However, with encouragement from her colleague Jung-seok, who is experiencing a mid-career slump, and inspiration drawn from her friends\' past sexual escapades, she unexpectedly discovers a hidden and divine talent within herself...', 110, 'Park Ji-hyun, Choi Si-won, Sung Dong-il, Park Geon-il, Hwang Se-on', '2025-01-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wKDCQpSfGJIyZmuXyZlnPmjV3QW.jpg', '', '', '', 7.3, 0, 0),
(2826, 'Wicked Little Letters', 'Thea Sharrock', 'Comedy, Drama, Mystery', 'United Kingdom, France', 'en', 'When the denizens of Littlehampton – including conservative Edith – begin receiving letters full of hilarious profanities, rowdy Irish migrant Rose is charged with the crime. Suspecting something amiss, the town\'s women band together to investigate.', 100, 'Olivia Colman, Jessie Buckley, Anjana Vasan, Timothy Spall, Gemma Jones', '2024-02-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/scAU7YudKNVeZlOfgSEWntAUSJ.jpg', '', '', '', 6.9, 0, 0),
(2827, 'Dragon', 'Ashwath Marimuthu', 'Romance, Comedy, Drama', 'India', 'ta', 'After a top student faces rejection and heartbreak, he cons his way into a finance career. But keeping up the facade proves tricky as the lies build.', 157, 'Pradeep Ranganathan, Anupama Parameswaran, Kayadu Lohar, Mysskin, Gautham Vasudev Menon', '2025-02-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vKNJPuejtE6Xrp6RK6LKsQcbL8L.jpg', '', '', 'Oz for Africa, Melodifestivalen 2024: 2nd preselection round', 7.786, 0, 0),
(2828, 'First Taste', 'Roman Perez Jr.', 'Romance, Drama', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Yuna, a woman engaged with her long time boyfriend, Nicco, starts to have second thoughts when she meets again her first love, Becca. Now she is torn between the man she loves and the woman she first loved.', 99, 'Angeli Khang, Robb Guinto, Matthew Francisco, Susan Africa, Audrey Avila', '2024-08-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oDWZS6LznvdH7mZOYfCro0ISJCM.jpg', '', '', '', 5, 0, 0),
(2829, 'Beautiful Wedding', 'Roger Kumble', 'Romance, Comedy, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Abby and Travis wake after a crazy night in Vegas as accidental newlyweds! With the mob on their heels, they flee to Mexico for a wild, weird honeymoon—but are they in for another disaster?', 95, 'Dylan Sprouse, Virginia Gardner, Austin North, Libe Barer, Rob Estes', '2024-01-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6214Uk9CZZcIibI84o5DEtbhfyk.jpg', '', '', '', 5.476, 0, 0),
(2830, 'Not Without My Shrink', 'Arnaud Lemort', 'Comedy', 'France', 'fr', 'A successful psychoanalyst\'s life is turned upside down by a very anxious and extremely clingy patient who starts dating his daughter.', 91, 'Christian Clavier, Claire Chust, Baptiste Lecaplain, Cristiana Réali, Rayane Bensetti', '2024-12-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/chl53EeJLqg7gkpiuay0Gf0SXL1.jpg', '', '', '', 4.684, 0, 0),
(2831, 'Cabrini', 'Alejandro Monteverde', 'History, Drama', 'Italy, United States of America', 'en', 'Italian immigrant Francesca Cabrini arrives in 1889 New York City and is greeted by disease, crime, and impoverished children. Cabrini sets off on a daring mission to convince the hostile mayor to secure housing and healthcare for society\'s most vulnerable. With broken English and poor health, Cabrini uses her entrepreneurial mind to build an empire of hope unlike anything the world had ever seen.', 142, 'Cristiana Dell\'Anna, David Morse, Giancarlo Giannini, John Lithgow, Romana Maggiora Vergano', '2024-03-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rBiHiN8W4BqMFrDozemzkof7GmF.jpg', '', '', '', 7.842, 0, 0),
(2832, 'Missing', 'Will Merrick', 'Drama, Mystery, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When her mother disappears while on vacation in Colombia with her new boyfriend, June’s search for answers is hindered by international red tape. Stuck thousands of miles away in Los Angeles, June creatively uses all the latest technology at her fingertips to try and find her before it’s too late. But as she digs deeper, her digital sleuthing raises more questions than answers... and when June unravels secrets about her mom, she discovers that she never really knew her at all.', 111, 'Storm Reid, Joaquim de Almeida, Ken Leung, Amy Landecker, Daniel Henney', '2023-01-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wEOUYSU5Uf8J7152PT6jdb5233Y.jpg', 'Palme d\'Or, Writers Guild of America Award, Academy Award for Best Writing, Adapted Screenplay, National Board of Review: Top Ten Films, SNEP gold single', 'Academy Award for Best Picture, Academy Award for Best Writing, Adapted Screenplay, Academy Award for Best Actor, Academy Award for Best Actress', '', 7.434, 0, 0),
(2833, 'Butas', 'Dado C. Lumibao', 'Drama, Thriller', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Witness how the lives of four young people who have various sexual quirks and inhibitions intertwine as they live together in a snug boarding house.', 112, 'Angela Morena, Angelica Hart, Albie Casiño, JD Aguas, Mosang', '2024-08-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2KObvBVle7HXXhj82EMKtizc051.jpg', '', '', '', 5.2, 0, 0),
(2834, 'Bila Esok Ibu Tiada', 'Rudi Soedjarwo', 'Drama, Family', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'Four adult siblings must set aside their differences after their mother\'s health declines, but can they come together and be a family again?', 104, 'Christine Hakim, Adinia Wirasti, Fedi Nuril, Amanda Manopo, Yasmin Napper', '2024-11-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dUVhcxEPaTw8ns1Q7NgKGdy5ag4.jpg', '', '', '', 6.5, 0, 0),
(2835, 'Noryang: Deadly Sea', 'Kim Han-min', 'War, Action, History, Drama', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'The Imjin War reaches its seventh year in December of 1598. Admiral Yi Sun-shin learns that the Wa invaders in Joseon are preparing for a swift withdrawal following the deathbed orders of their leader Toyotomi Hideyoshi. Determined to destroy the enemy once and for all, Admiral Yi leads an allied fleet of Joseon and Ming ships to mount a blockade and annihilate the Wa army. However, once Ming commander Chen Lin is bribed into lifting the blockade, Wa lord Shimazu Yoshihiro and his Satsuma army sail to the Wa army\'s rescue at Noryang Strait.', 153, 'Kim Yun-seok, Baek Yoon-sik, Jung Jae-young, Huh Joon-ho, Kim Sung-kyu', '2023-12-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sRvL19WMG883eFyfs3wBRxf6Vx0.jpg', '', '', '', 6.3, 0, 0),
(2836, 'White Bird', 'Marc Forster', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After being expelled from Beecher Prep for his treatment of a classmate with a facial deformity, Julian has struggled to fit in at his new school. To transform his life, Julian\'s grandmother finally reveals her own story of courage of her youth in Nazi-occupied France, where a classmate shelters her from mortal danger.', 121, 'Ariella Glaser, Orlando Schwerdt, Bryce Gheisar, Gillian Anderson, Helen Mirren', '2023-10-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s2igE99PVBEMsry3qEGEH3rM83K.jpg', '', '', '', 7.898, 0, 0),
(2837, 'May December', 'Todd Haynes', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Twenty years after their notorious tabloid romance gripped the nation, a married couple buckles under the pressure when an actress arrives to do research for a film about their past.', 117, 'Natalie Portman, Julianne Moore, Charles Melton, Cory Michael Smith, Elizabeth Yu', '2023-11-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zhV7B610l7hjlri4ywikJ18ONuq.jpg', '', '', '', 6.607, 0, 0),
(2838, 'Fight Against Evil 2', 'Qin Pengfei', 'Action, Crime, Drama', 'China', 'zh', 'Li Hongqi, a righteous Northeast police officer, accidentally discovers the existence of local bullies involved in pornography. As the investigation deepens, a gang of local tyrants who control and oppress women with drugs emerges and openly provokes the police. Li Hongqi has decided to fight to the end, and is bound to eradicate this \"pornography tumor\".', 89, 'Xie Miao, Zhang Li, Liu Fengchao, Xing Hanqing, Zhang Haosen', '2023-07-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uFUBRvuk6LzD9oEwSFAGZc2i1kn.jpg', '', '', '', 7.5, 0, 0),
(2839, 'Hagen', 'Cyrill Boss', 'Fantasy, Adventure, Action', 'Czech Republic, Germany', 'de', 'Hagen von Tronje, the Burgundian master-at-arms, holds his troubled kingdom together while hiding his dark past. The arrival of the unpredictable dragon slayer Siegfried threatens to upend the old order. As King Gunter seeks Siegfried\'s help to win the fierce Valkyrie Brunhild, Hagen faces a tragic choice between loyalty to the king and his own identity.', 135, 'Gijs Naber, Jannis Niewöhner, Lilja van der Zwaag, Dominic Marcus Singer, Rosalinde Mynster', '2024-10-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eQ1nTnV6neOhBeDJj87IUHDLwb0.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
(2840, 'Déjame estar contigo', 'Isaac Cherem', 'Romance, Comedy, Drama', 'Mexico', 'es', 'Lucía lives with an incurable disease, and Bruno was deported to Mexico with no place to sleep. An unexpected phone call brings them together in an emotional story of overcoming, reconstruction and hope.', 80, 'Andrea Sutton Chávez, Aksel Gomez, Silvia Navarro, Johanna Murillo, Anna Díaz', '2025-01-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zccT9ZXooAGbaZh6zZVPZbqcVFJ.jpg', '', '', '', 6.167, 0, 0),
