(2842, 'Dora: Say Hola to Adventure!', 'Don Kim', 'Animation, Family', '', 'en', 'It’s Dora, the world’s most famous exploradora, like you’ve never seen her before! Join her and ALL her friends for BRAND NEW, magical adventures in the rainforest!', 45, 'Diana Zermeño, Asher Colton Spence, Marc Weiner', '2023-11-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zN3BO43b0JAn1ZCpbwBH6KEP56U.jpg', '', '', '', 7.2, 0, 0),
(2843, 'You Can Live Forever', 'Sarah Watts', 'Drama, Romance', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'When Jaime, a gay teenager, is sent to live in a community of Jehovah\'s Witnesses in small-town Quebec, she falls madly in love with a devout Witness girl. The two embark on an intense affair with consequences that will reshape the rest of their lives.', 97, 'Anwen O\'Driscoll, June Laporte, Liane Balaban, Antoine Yared, Hasani Freeman', '2023-03-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6JllNMDqHasBeqM5vFVxp1rB9Fk.jpg', '', '', '', 6.675, 0, 0),
(2844, 'World\'s Best', 'Roshan Sethi', 'Music, Family, Comedy', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'Twelve-year-old mathematics genius Prem discovers his recently deceased father was a famous rapper and immediately sets out to learn more about his father’s life and passions. Empowered by imaginative hip-hop music-fueled fantasies, Prem is determined to find out if hip-hop truly is in his DNA.', 101, 'Manny Magnus, Punam Patel, Utkarsh Ambudkar, Max Malas, Jake Choi', '2023-06-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9xvEhZZMOmLIkqe4khrtF5TkOnO.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
(2845, 'Snoopy Presents: Welcome Home, Franklin', 'Raymond S. Persi', 'Animation, Family', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'Franklin is new to town and hoping to make friends, but his usual tactics don\'t work on the Peanuts gang. When the Soap Box Derby arrives, he\'s sure it\'s a chance to impress new pals and teams up with the only other unpartnered kid: Charlie Brown.', 40, 'Caleb Bellavance, Etienne Kellici, Isabella Leo, Wyatt White, Lexi Perri', '2024-02-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pjIrYzc31kHTySiovHAt0o3qDc2.jpg', '', '', '', 7.664, 0, 0),
(2846, 'Muay Thai Hustle', 'Ping Lumpraploeng', 'Comedy', 'Thailand', 'th', 'Saen San Phan San Su tells the story of \'Saen\', a down and out boxer whose future is about to end because of the goodwill of his friends, until the boxing industry turns its back on him. He returns to live with his mother in the province. Many things happen until he sees death as a warning, causing him to return to search for the legendary boxing teacher. And finally, he gets what he has dreamed of, plus a wife...', 119, 'Jirayu La-ongmanee, Sananthachat Thanapatpisal, Chinawut Indracusin, Supathat Opas, Auttawut Inthong', '2025-01-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uv0r02j8XCY7OSf0hhlLBdfBvZF.jpg', '', '', '', 5, 0, 0),
(2847, 'Something Blue', 'Camilo Abadía', 'Romance, Comedy', 'Colombia', 'es', 'Lifelong friends Óscar and Eli find themselves in a messy situation after a drunken night leads to unexpected consequences. Forced to replace a ruined wedding dress, they embark on a chaotic journey filled with setbacks and awkward run-ins with their exes.', 0, 'Tessa Ía, Ricardo Abarca, Ana María Estupiñán, Isabel Burr, Gerardo Oñate', '2025-02-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tdqzzSDXeCZzCEzZKPLYQuTwFdG.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(2848, 'Nefarious', 'Cary Solomon', 'Horror, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'On the day of his scheduled execution, a convicted serial killer gets a psychiatric evaluation during which he claims he is a demon, and further claims that before their time is over, the psychiatrist will commit three murders of his own.', 98, 'Sean Patrick Flanery, Jordan Belfi, Tom Ohmer, Glenn Beck, Daniel Martin Berkey', '2023-04-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xwjWUAajQJPj5aik1tounPguZbz.jpg', '', 'Golden Trailer Awards', '', 6.767, 0, 0),
(2849, 'The World Will Tremble', 'Lior Geller', 'Drama, War', 'United States of America, United Kingdom, Bulgaria, Israel', 'en', 'The incredible, untold true story of how a group of prisoners attempt a seemingly impossible escape from the first Nazi death camp in order to provide the first eyewitness account of the Holocaust.', 109, 'Oliver Jackson-Cohen, Charlie MacGechan, David Kross, Jeremy Neumark Jones, Michael Epp', '2025-03-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/31CKSlZdsvdY8bysV5WeR2YvTim.jpg', '', '', '', 7.8, 0, 0),
(2850, 'Humane', 'Caitlin Cronenberg', 'Thriller, Horror, Science Fiction', 'Canada', 'en', 'In the wake of an environmental collapse that has forced humanity to shed 20% of its population, a family dinner erupts into chaos when a father\'s plan to enlist in the government\'s new euthanasia program goes horribly awry.', 93, 'Jay Baruchel, Emily Hampshire, Sebastian Chacon, Alanna Bale, Sirena Gulamgaus', '2024-04-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ecOvKaoM1hwQbp0uTnULGrSV32e.jpg', '', '', '', 5.282, 0, 0),
(2851, 'Sniper: G.R.I.T. - Global Response & Intelligence Team', 'Oliver Thompson', 'Action, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When an international terrorist cult threatens global political stability and kidnaps a fellow agent, Ace Sniper Brandon Beckett and the newly-formed Global Response & Intelligence Team – or G.R.I.T. – led by Colonel Stone must travel across the world to Malta, infiltrate the cult, and take out its leader to free Lady Death and stop the global threat.', 92, 'Chad Michael Collins, Ryan Robbins, Luna Fujimoto, Josh Brener, Dennis Haysbert', '2023-09-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xpdM0RDM6lWgtLsYVb1XpYmNxzd.jpg', '', '', '', 6.583, 0, 0),
(2852, 'Maharaja', 'Nithilan Saminathan', 'Action, Thriller', 'India', 'ta', 'A barber seeks vengeance after his home is burglarized, cryptically telling police his \"Lakshmi\" has been taken, leaving them uncertain if it\'s a person or object, jeer at his request until they learn what they\'re really looking for.', 141, 'Vijay Sethupathi, Anurag Kashyap, Sachana Namidass, Natarajan Subramaniam, Abhirami', '2024-06-14', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3WgxA2nSzAgMR4DYDty0O9wx68x.jpg', '', '', '', 7.8, 0, 0),
(2853, 'Consent', 'Vanessa Filho', 'History, Drama', 'Belgium, France', 'fr', 'In 2013, Vanessa Springora recounts how she found herself under the influence of a famous writer. In 1986, she was 13; him, almost 50. The victim of a triple predation: sexual, literary, and psychic, there\'s more beyond her individual story. She questions the excesses of an era, and the complacency of an environment blinded by talent and celebrity.', 119, 'Kim Higelin, Jean-Paul Rouve, Laetitia Casta, Élodie Bouchez, Jean Chevalier', '2023-10-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8QTo3OgSqS09jFYPwQWXyx0fi2W.jpg', '', '', '', 6.874, 0, 0),
(2854, 'Finestkind', 'Brian Helgeland', 'Crime, Drama, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Two brothers from opposite sides of the tracks are reunited as adults. Desperate circumstances force them into a deal with an organized crime syndicate in Boston, and a young woman gets caught in the middle.', 126, 'Ben Foster, Toby Wallace, Jenna Ortega, Tommy Lee Jones, Ismael Cruz Cordova', '2023-09-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4Nj22XjqaOwc37IJ9WrOJ5UZi7q.jpg', '', '', '', 6.911, 0, 0),
(2855, 'In the Land of Saints and Sinners', 'Robert Lorenz', 'Action, Thriller', 'Belgium, France, Ireland, Switzerland, United States of America', 'en', 'In a remote Irish village, a damaged Finbar is forced to fight for redemption after a lifetime of sins, but what price is he willing to pay? In the land of saints and sinners, some sins can\'t be buried.', 106, 'Liam Neeson, Kerry Condon, Ciarán Hinds, Jack Gleeson, Colm Meaney', '2023-10-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uOa6TNXi3LUHrqIp9xiWNyOyyCF.jpg', '', '', '', 6.522, 0, 0),
(2856, 'Cursed', 'Carlos Marbán', 'Horror, Action, Drama', 'Spain', 'es', 'The lives of six girls belong to different worlds although connected to each other through a doll called Molly, whose existence dates back to 1976, when she appeared among the rubble of the great fire of the San Carlos orphanage, in northern Spain', 60, 'Daniela Casas, Noah Casas, Roxana Visan, Laila Núñez, Haizea Carneros', '2023-10-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nQlq8Dp0DiYbAmybZFwp2JvS2Ml.jpg', '', '', '', 6.306, 0, 0),
(2857, 'No Other Land', 'Rachel Szor', 'Documentary', 'Norway, Palestinian Territory', 'ar', 'This film made by a Palestinian-Israeli collective shows the destruction of the occupied West Bank\'s Masafer Yatta by Israeli soldiers and the alliance which develops between the Palestinian activist Basel and Israeli journalist Yuval.', 92, 'Basel Adra, Yuval Abraham, Farisa Abu Aram, Nasser Adra, Harun Abu Aram', '2024-11-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s7XYieuZg9kMe07i9VI4bfGN4Pw.jpg', 'Berlinale Documentary Award, European Film Award for Best Documentary, Academy Award for Best Documentary Feature Film', 'European Film Award for Best Film', '', 7.894, 0, 0),
