(2864, 'Love Forever', 'Staffan Lindberg', 'Romance, Comedy, Drama', 'Sweden', 'sv', 'A Stockholm couple plans to get married on the gorgeous island of Gotland, where family-imposed traditions turn their most important day into a disaster.', 96, 'Matilda Källström, Charlie Gustafsson, Kjell Bergqvist, Anja Lundqvist, Claes Malmberg', '2025-02-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e2yAyz0PR43aIxnGjv9HJryHBys.jpg', '', '', '', 4.838, 0, 0),
