(2932, 'Boy Kaldag', 'Roman Perez Jr.', 'Drama', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Boy Kaldag, a man infamous for his massive manhood — a gift that drives women wild and sparks envy among men. As his legend grows, Boy Kaldag plunges into a world of lust and chaos that comes with being so well-endowed. From a difficult birth, because he gets stuck on the way out because of his enormous endowment, to what seems like a curse, which befalls all that have relations with him, he has a problematic life. He recounts his life story to a late-night naughty-podcast host.', 95, 'Benz Sangalang, Dyessa Garcia, Aiko Garcia, Azi Acosta, Angeli Khang', '2024-12-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oP7KG48p8dbWFTykZDzrjxu2MUA.jpg', '', '', '', 4, 0, 0),
