(2934, '5lbs of Pressure', 'Phil Allocco', 'Thriller, Crime, Romance', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'Fresh out of prison after serving time for murder, Adam returns to his old stomping grounds to seek out a son who doesn\'t know him. Eli, the brother of the man he killed is looking for revenge. Mike, is trying to escape a life of crime living under the thumb of his gangster Uncle.', 111, 'Luke Evans, Rory Culkin, Alex Pettyfer, Rudy Pankow, Charlie Rawes', '2024-03-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/toEJOPYvM7Na0XwM8exg8aHq553.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
