(2948, 'Bionic', 'Afonso Poyart', 'Science Fiction, Action, Adventure', 'Brazil', 'pt', 'When the progress of robotics makes Paralympic athletes the new sports stars, Maria dreams of competing against her sister. For that, she will have to enter a world of crime and violence.', 110, 'Jessica Córes, Bruno Gagliasso, Gabz, Christian Malheiros, Nill Marcondes', '2024-05-28', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xVCYzdBE6lo3sUFK1OMZnXvpGtT.jpg', '', '', '', 5.997, 0, 0),
(2949, 'The Devil Conspiracy', 'Nathan Frankowski', 'Horror, Fantasy, Science Fiction, Thriller', 'Czech Republic, United States of America', 'en', 'A powerful biotech company has breakthrough technology allowing them to clone history’s most influential people with just a few fragments of DNA. Behind this company is a cabal of Satanists that steals the shroud of Christ, putting them in possession of Jesus’ DNA. The clone will serve as the ultimate offering to the devil. The Archangel Michael comes to earth and will stop at nothing to end the devil’s conspiracy.', 111, 'Alice Orr-Ewing, Joe Doyle, Eveline Hall, Peter Mensah, Joe Anderson', '2023-01-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1AWcMtUZjpkq4h52yDnNIp9FwEO.jpg', '', '', '', 6.51, 0, 0),
(2950, 'Pengantin Iblis', 'Azhar Kinoi Lubis', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'Ranti is very devoted mother and wife. Ranti has a daughter who she loves very much, but has been disabled since birth, Nina.  One day, Nina had a fatal accident that required immediate treatment. However, Ranti\'s husband, who works as a sailor, was not at home, and her extended family was also unable to help.  Ranti forced to accept the offer to become a Devil\'s bride in order to save Nina.  Finally, Nina can be cured, but there is another price that Ranti has to pay, which involves the lives of all her family members...', 102, 'Taskya Namya, Wafda Saifan Lubis, Arla Ailani, Givina Lukita, Bukie B. Mansyur', '2025-01-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6UWQVddCVCnFM4G7PSHcCc5NGtI.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
