(3048, 'Camp Crasher', 'Martino Zaidelis', 'Comedy, Romance', 'Argentina', 'es', 'In a bid to save her son\'s end-of-school camping trip, a single mom steps in as the bus driver while trying to show him she really can be a cool mom.', 95, 'Natalia Oreiro, Milo Zeus Lis, Pablo Rago, Dalia Gutmann, Sofía Morandi', '2024-12-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dsLTwYtpi7CtkA8ONH3CuYnjAXj.jpg', '', '', '', 6.8, 0, 0),
(3049, 'The Black Demon', 'Adrian Grünberg', 'Thriller, Horror', 'United States of America, Mexico, Dominican Republic', 'en', 'Oilman Paul Sturges\' idyllic family vacation turns into a nightmare when they encounter a ferocious megalodon shark that will stop at nothing to protect its territory. Stranded and under constant attack, Paul and his family must somehow find a way to get his family back to shore alive before it strikes again in this epic battle between humans and nature.', 101, 'Josh Lucas, Fernanda Urrejola, Julio Cesar Cedillo, Venus Ariel, Carlos Solórzano', '2023-04-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6ecSjKSjgIULyHfrfyyg9vgAI33.jpg', '', '', '', 5.961, 0, 0),
(3050, 'Art of Love', 'Recai Karagöz', 'Romance, Action, Drama', 'Turkey', 'tr', 'After learning that the art thief she has been chasing is her ex-lover, an officer working for Interpol concocts a plan to catch him red-handed.', 99, 'Birkan Sokullu, Esra Bilgiç, Fırat Tanış, Ushan Çakır, Hakan Ummak', '2024-03-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/niVtvS9Kf8G1VDPSqurqHkaSSwm.jpg', '', '', '', 6.4, 0, 0),
(3051, 'Mistress', 'Richard Kim', 'Drama', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'After finishing his long career as a government official in Hanyang, His Excellency returns home with his gisaeng lover. His mistress, who washed her identity as his foster daughter, can\'t adjust to the boring country life and becomes lonely. On the other hand, His Excellency keeps paying attention to his female servant, a familiar face in his hometown full of memories, and becomes increasingly neglectful of his mistress. The mistress, who is saddened by His Excellency\'s actions, receives comfort for her body and mind from his male servant. One day, an imperial scholar comes to visit and takes control of his mistress, but when His Excellency does not take any action, she becomes greatly disappointed. However, the male servant, who watched the scene, seeks revenge for her from the imperial scholar but is caught by His Excellency and beats him. At the end, his mistress decides to run away with the male servant in the middle of the night.', 75, 'Jo Wan-jin, Do Hee, Min Do-yoon, Im Cho-hee, Ha Yool', '2024-05-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6sTeWsvRtWSEU4BA6CpNP1FVukc.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3052, 'Smurfs', 'Chris Miller', 'Animation, Family, Fantasy', 'United States of America, Belgium', 'en', 'When Papa Smurf is mysteriously taken by evil wizards, Razamel and Gargamel, Smurfette leads the Smurfs on a mission into the real world to save him. With the help of new friends, the Smurfs must discover what defines their destiny to save the universe.', 0, 'Rihanna, James Corden, Nick Offerman, JP Karliak, Dan Levy', '2025-07-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vdSZpNDvoxmswp2OwUoMD1ypEMP.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3053, 'Puppy Love', 'Richard Alan Reid', 'Comedy, Romance', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After a disastrous first date, wild-child Nicole and socially-anxious Max vow to lose each other’s numbers until they learn that their dogs found a love match, and now puppies are on the way! The hilariously mismatched Nicole and Max are forced to become responsible co-parents, but may end up finding love themselves.', 106, 'Lucy Hale, Grant Gustin, Jane Seymour, Michael Hitchcock, Nore Davis', '2023-08-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8UOz1P7jFcGUT17EWfgWr2xl7v4.jpg', '', '', '', 7.05, 0, 0),
(3054, 'Boudica', 'Jesse V. Johnson', 'Action, War', 'United Kingdom', 'en', 'Inspired by events in A.D. 60, Boudica follows the eponymous Celtic warrior who rules the Iceni people alongside her husband Prasutagus. When he dies at the hands of Roman soldiers, Boudica’s kingdom is left without a male heir and the Romans seize her land and property.  Driven to the edge of madness and determined to avenge her husband’s death, Boudica rallies the various tribes from the region and wages an epic war against the mighty Roman empire.', 101, 'Olga Kurylenko, Peter Franzén, Clive Standen, Lucy Martin, Nick Moran', '2023-10-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ssEFC5wfFjj7lJpUgwJDOK1Xu1J.jpg', '', '', '', 5.904, 0, 0),
(3055, 'Trigger Happy', 'Tiffany Kim Stevens', 'Comedy, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A repressed husband attempts to murder his bread-winning wife for her life insurance policy in this madcap, 1950\'s-inspired satire.', 86, 'Tyler Poelle, Elsha Kim, Christina Kirkman, Matt Lowe, Tre Hall', '2024-03-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5YDdMeKhKCC3ojLM9WLioLZEDDx.jpg', '', '', '', 3, 0, 0),
(3056, 'Woman of...', 'Małgorzata Szumowska', 'Drama, History', 'Poland, Sweden', 'pl', 'Aniela has lived the first half of her life as a man: with an office job, a wife, and two children. But neither her family\'s opposition nor repression by the government in Poland can stop her from finally becoming the person she\'s always been.', 132, 'Małgorzata Hajewska-Krzysztofik, Joanna Kulig, Mateusz Więcławek, Bogumiła Bajor, Jerzy Bończak', '2024-04-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dM75IPA1B1tgEpXMg6rynbgJo38.jpg', '', '', '', 6.4, 0, 0),
(3057, 'Fountain of Youth', 'Guy Ritchie', 'Adventure, Fantasy, Mystery', 'United States of America, United Kingdom', 'en', 'A treasure-hunting mastermind assembles a team for a life-changing adventure. But to outwit and outrun threats at every turn, he\'ll need someone even smarter than he is: his estranged sister.', 0, 'John Krasinski, Natalie Portman, Eiza González, Domhnall Gleeson, Arian Moayed', '2025-05-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/meYlxtHSwBsXNtdQt1HKKMxp2jC.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3058, 'Transfusion', 'Matt Nable', 'Crime, Action, Drama', 'Australia, United Kingdom', 'en', 'Ryan Logan, a former Special Forces operative, is battling to cope with life after the loss of his wife.  He is thrusted into the criminal underworld to keep his only son from being taken from him.', 105, 'Sam Worthington, Matt Nable, Phoebe Tonkin, Edward Carmody, Susie Porter', '2023-01-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bxh5xCCW9Ynfg6EZJWUkc1zqTnr.jpg', '', '', '', 6.091, 0, 0),
(3059, 'Sijjin', 'Hadrah Daeng Ratu', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'Irma falls in love with Galang, her cousin who already has a wife and children. Irma is very obsessed and wants to be the only woman in Galang\'s life. Irma comes to the shaman to send black magic to Galang\'s wife. Since then terror and mystical disturbances, possession and death have occurred in Galang\'s house. However, the threat also targeted Irma herself.', 100, 'Ibrahim Risyad, Anggika Bölsterli, Keinaya Messi Gusti, Delia Husein, Niken Anjani', '2023-11-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dnKod1VGfTR44CCvsABd8D0ifVK.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
(3060, 'Am I OK?', 'Tig Notaro', 'Comedy, Romance, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Lucy and Jane have been best friends for most of their lives and think they know everything there is to know about each other. But when Jane announces she\'s moving to London, Lucy reveals a long-held secret. As Jane tries to help Lucy, their friendship is thrown into chaos.', 86, 'Dakota Johnson, Sonoya Mizuno, Jermaine Fowler, Kiersey Clemons, Molly Gordon', '2024-06-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qKkaG7HVFVe7C1JuxTGwNz0eSyL.jpg', '', '', '', 6.344, 0, 0),
(3061, 'Haunting of the Queen Mary', 'Gary Shore', 'Horror, Thriller, Mystery', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'When photographers Erin and Patrick are brought aboard the ship with their young son Lukas, they unleash a series of events that entwines their family with the ship’s dark past. As the terror unfolds around them they begin to realise there is more to this sumptuous ocean liner than meets the eye: its remarkable legacy masking violent secrets.', 124, 'Alice Eve, Joel Fry, Nell Hudson, Angus Wright, Jim Piddock', '2023-07-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/y8uEuy1NhOwltHePRqvxcDDUJg1.jpg', '', '', '', 5.311, 0, 0),
(3062, 'Shin Kamen Rider', 'Hideaki Anno', 'Action, Drama, Science Fiction, Adventure, Fantasy', 'Japan', 'ja', 'A man forced to bear power and stripped of humanity. A woman skeptical of happiness. Takeshi Hongo, an Augmentation made by SHOCKER, and Ruriko Midorikawa, a rebel of the organization, escape while fighting off assassins. What’s justice? What’s evil? Will this violence end? Despite his power, Hongo tries to remain human. Along with freedom, Ruriko has regained a heart. What paths will they choose?', 121, 'Sosuke Ikematsu, Minami Hamabe, Tasuku Emoto, Mirai Moriyama, Nanase Nishino', '2023-03-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9dTO2RygcDT0cQkawABw4QkDegN.jpg', '', '', '', 6.9, 0, 0),
(3063, 'Climax', 'Rodante Pajemna Jr.', 'Documentary', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'With 12M+ fans, VMX turned up the heat in 2024 with record-breaking, steamy films from top Filipino directors, starring your fave crushes and fresh faces. Join Robb Guinto & Apple Dy as they dive into the hottest scenes that left us sweating!', 71, 'Robb Guinto, Apple Dy', '2024-12-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oZ3Q2BBOtNYk1UR0gXeMgsUrGOx.jpg', 'Sitges Film Festival Best Feature-Length Film award', 'IFFR audience award', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3064, 'Crew', 'Rajesh Krishnan', 'Comedy, Drama', 'India', 'hi', 'Three ordinary air hostesses from Mumbai embark on a journey to pursue their dreams but find themselves caught up in unexpected misfortunes.', 124, 'Tabu, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Kriti Sanon, Diljit Dosanjh, Rajesh Sharma', '2024-03-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8mnCtQngfhYt0W0BmkrCePutmvy.jpg', '', '', '', 6.858, 0, 0),
(3065, 'Sleep', 'Jason Yu', 'Horror, Mystery, Thriller', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Hyun-su and Soo-jin have just gotten married. Seemingly out of nowhere, he starts talking in his sleep. \'Someone’s inside.\' From that night forward, whenever he falls asleep, he transforms into someone else with no recollection of the night before. Soo-jin is overwhelmed with anxiety that he’d hurt her family while she sleeps and can barely sleep a wink because of this irrational fear. Despite sleep treatment, Hyun-su’s sleepwalking only intensifies, and she begins to feel that her unborn child may be in danger...', 95, 'Jung Yu-mi, Lee Sun-kyun, Kim Guk-hee, Lee Kyung-jin, Yoon Kyung-ho', '2023-09-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b4d90lpmSTLoCP9tkBU7QAQOhh0.jpg', '', '', '', 6.694, 0, 0),
(3066, 'Paupahan', 'Louie Ignacio', 'Drama', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'A struggling model scores a big rent discount on a small apartment. Thanks to the young caretaker who shows interest in him. Unknown to him, someone behind the mirrors is watching his every move.', 92, 'Tiffany Grey, Jiad Arroyo, Robb Guinto, Princess Zian, Aica Veloso', '2023-04-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2klatuhhRjeCORe9Yj8L2RUqPRG.jpg', '', '', '', 3.2, 0, 0),
(3067, 'Do Patti', 'Shashanka Chaturvedi', 'Thriller, Mystery, Drama, Crime', 'India', 'hi', 'A puzzling investigation leads a no-nonsense cop down a dark path involving the vicious rivalry between twin sisters and the volatile man they both love.', 128, 'Kajol, Kriti Sanon, Shaheer Sheikh, Tanvi Azmi, Brijendra Kala', '2024-10-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cqStHxRVUtFNaNnJtieHeXIackv.jpg', '', '', '', 7.151, 0, 0),
(3068, 'Lord of Misrule', 'William Brent Bell', 'Horror', 'Ireland, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'When the daughter of the town\'s new priest goes missing during the harvest festival, a desperate search begins, uncovering the town\'s dark history and resurfacing tales of a mysterious, malevolent spirit that demands sacrifice.', 104, 'Tuppence Middleton, Ralph Ineson, Matt Stokoe, Evie Templeton, Jane Wood', '2023-10-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eCNJuGsCNdf2yf4F3UcDg1WZTbo.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(3069, 'South Park: Joining the Panderverse', 'Trey Parker', 'Animation, Comedy, Science Fiction, TV Movie', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Cartman\'s deeply disturbing dreams portend the end of the life he knows and loves. Meanwhile, the adults in South Park are wrestling with their own life decisions, as the advent of AI is turning their world upside down.', 49, 'Trey Parker, Matt Stone, Janeshia Adams-Ginyard, Montana Jacobowitz, April Stewart', '2023-10-28', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/18IsRVfs5MkkTcqTGlUAnka6sCh.jpg', '', '', '', 7.686, 0, 0),
(3070, 'Umjolo: There Is No Cure', 'Mthunzi Dubazana', 'Romance, Comedy, Drama', 'South Africa', 'zu', 'After losing her title for publicly exposing a scandal, a former pageant queen works on a tell-all book — all while her love life remains unwritten.', 78, 'Nombuleleo Mhlongo, Busisiwe Mtshali, Tina Redman, Londeka Sishi, Yonda Thomas', '2025-02-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fLsqbS6polYms46pJ02nCmH5MjN.jpg', '', '', '', 6.8, 0, 0),
(3071, 'My Favourite Cake', 'Maryam Moghaddam', 'Drama, Comedy, Romance', 'France, Germany, Iran, Sweden', 'fa', 'Mahin lives alone in Tehran since her husband’s death and her daughter’s departure for Europe, until an afternoon tea with friends leads her to break her solitary routine and revitalize her love life.', 97, 'Lily Farhadpour, Esmaeel Mehrabi, Mansoureh Ilkhani, Soraya Orang, Homa Mottahedin', '2024-07-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gs6XHzRPZWBMUbFkZUwMDgNz0li.jpg', 'FIPRESCI Prize at Berlinale', '', '', 7.475, 0, 0),
(3072, 'Marco', 'Haneef Adeni', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', 'India', 'ml', 'The adoptive son of the Adattu family, Marco, sets off on a ruthless quest for vengeance after his brother is brutally murdered, finding only betrayal, loss and unimaginable brutality at every step.', 145, 'Unni Mukundan, Siddique, Ishan Shoukath, Jagadish, Abhimanyu Thilakan', '2024-12-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/il3ao5gcF6fZNqo1o9o7lusmEyU.jpg', '', '', '', 6.241, 0, 0),
(3073, 'Skincare', 'Austin Peters', 'Thriller, Drama', 'France, Italy, United States of America', 'en', 'Famed aesthetician Hope Goldman is about to take her career to the next level by launching her very own skin care line. However, she soon faces a new challenge when a rival opens a boutique directly across from her store. Suspecting that someone is trying to sabotage her, she embarks on a quest to unravel the mystery of who\'s trying to destroy her life.', 96, 'Elizabeth Banks, Lewis Pullman, Michaela Jaé Rodriguez, Luis Gerardo Méndez, Nathan Fillion', '2024-08-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ikPzv7el0RcBhtXj3ElCoH54icd.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(3074, 'A Legend', 'Stanley Tong Gwai-Lai', 'Action, Fantasy, Adventure, Romance', 'China, Hong Kong', 'zh', 'An archeologist noticed that the texture of the relics discovered during the excavation of a glacier closely resembled a jade pendant seen in one of his dreams. He and his team then embark on an expedition into the depths of the glacier.', 129, 'Jackie Chan, Zhang Yixing, Guli Nazha, Aarif Rahman, Jerry Lee', '2024-07-05', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qbImUt1d3itXcB81BCItPZlfbyr.jpg', '', '', '', 5.8, 0, 0),
(3075, 'Borgo', 'Stéphane Demoustier', 'Drama, Crime', 'France', 'fr', 'Melissa is an experienced, exemplary prison guard. But a dangerous spiral is set into motion when she transfers to a Corsican jail, where she accepts help and protection from inmate Saveriu to get her bearings. Upon his release, he contacts Melissa expecting to collect.', 118, 'Hafsia Herzi, Moussa Mansaly, Florence Loiret Caille, Pablo Pauly, Cédric Appietto', '2024-04-17', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/48xwJpo5tecapOAEq0Gio1LQ3Q1.jpg', '', '', '', 6.823, 0, 0),
(3076, 'Cassino in Ischia', 'Frank Ciota', 'Comedy, Action', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A former film star travels to Italy to work with a struggling director in order to revitalize his career.', 113, 'Dominic Purcell, Ugo Dighero, Miriam Candurro, Marcello Romolo, Carlotta Natoli', '2024-09-30', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3HNFnLe9DcDt3ZcytxOXzeToEvQ.jpg', '', '', '', 4.885, 0, 0),
(3077, 'Agak Laen', 'Muhadkly Acho', 'Comedy, Horror', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'Four friends, working in a haunted house ride at a night market, unintentionally cause the death of an elderly man with heart disease through fright. They decide to bury his body within the haunted house, which turns out to be beneficial for the attraction... at least for a little while.', 119, 'Oki Rengga, Boris Bokir, Bene Dion Rajagukguk, Indra Jegel, Tissa Biani', '2024-02-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lUOwyPbDD9Agl3pHQVHGbZE0TvI.jpg', '', '', '', 7.8, 0, 0),
(3078, 'The Infallibles', 'Frédéric Forestier', 'Comedy, Action', 'France', 'fr', 'When a gang of robbers provokes chaos in Paris and humiliates the police, the Minister of the Interior wants new blood at the helm of the investigation: Alia is from Marseille, fiery-tempered and unmanageable, Hugo is Parisian, valedictorian and meticulous. In short, they have every reason to hate each other. A forced alliance, for better or for worse, or maybe blossoming into something else?', 99, 'Inès Reg, Kévin Debonne, Vincent Rottiers, Moussa Maaskri, François Neycken', '2024-06-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7PoIAvL3Io5v0HyBliXfXZruQTi.jpg', '', '', '', 6.3, 0, 0),
(3079, 'Baby John', 'Kalees', 'Action, Drama, Thriller, Crime', 'India', 'hi', 'John\'s peaceful life with daughter Khushi is disrupted by a sex-trafficking gang. Revealing his past as DCP Satya, he seeks revenge for his family\'s murder, saving minor girls and punishing the criminals, before starting anew.', 162, 'Varun Dhawan, Keerthy Suresh, Wamiqa Gabbi, Rajpal Yadav, Sheeba Chaddha', '2024-12-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5Oqsh17dq0cIRFPynPNy5elmyxW.jpg', '', '', '', 5.231, 0, 0),
(3080, 'Un/Dressed', 'Tim Trachte', 'Thriller, Romance, Drama', 'Germany', 'de', 'Elle is a young entrepreneur who wants to lead her grandmother Margot\'s fashion house into a new era. She is in a relationship with Thilo, the son of an influential Hamburg family. After Elle\'s grandmother receives anonymous threats, Ben, who has been in prison, is assigned as her bodyguard. Elle is torn between Thilo and Ben. As Elle delves deeper into Ben\'s world, she learns secrets about Thilo that could jeopardize her grandmother\'s life\'s work.', 103, 'Lena Meckel, Malik Blumenthal, Gerrit Klein, Brigitte Karner, Roman Knižka', '2024-09-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xSKuXQb1VAUlyULUE4tkGTDbGdQ.jpg', '', '', '', 5.8, 0, 0),
(3081, 'Crescent City', 'RJ Collins', 'Crime, Thriller, Mystery', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When a ruthless serial killer terrorizes a small Southern town, everyone becomes a suspect -- including local authorities. As the body count rises and the dark mystery deepens, the chief detective becomes haunted by the horrors of his past.', 103, 'Terrence Howard, Esai Morales, Nicky Whelan, Alec Baldwin, Michael Sirow', '2024-08-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kWwIkWextuqVUvAEM9DwJfEfkKe.jpg', '', '', '', 5.962, 0, 0),
(3082, 'Champions', 'Bobby Farrelly', 'Comedy, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A stubborn and hotheaded minor league basketball coach is forced to train a Special Olympics team when he is sentenced to community service.', 124, 'Woody Harrelson, Kaitlin Olson, Cheech Marin, Matt Cook, Ernie Hudson', '2023-03-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/i46Gke8Kg3uH2K5eM0rDo4HzPtq.jpg', 'Czech Lion Awards, Czech Lion for Best Supporting Actor, Czech Lion Awards', 'International Submission to the Academy Awards', '', 6.725, 0, 0),
(3083, 'The Corpse Washer', 'Hadrah Daeng Ratu', 'Horror, Drama, Thriller', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'Lela, a mortician, finds something odd about the body of her mother who died suddenly. Trapped in sacred tension and a tense horror journey, Lela discovers another oddity in the body of the corpse she was bathing.', 107, 'Aghniny Haque, Djenar Maesa Ayu, Ibrahim Risyad, Ruth Marini, Vonny Anggraini', '2024-02-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1ZTrQWpuhxMr32uC1fQBRnkVYlf.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0),
(3084, 'Dunki', 'Rajkumar Hirani', 'Adventure, Comedy, Drama', 'India', 'hi', 'Four friends from a sleepy little village in Punjab share a common dream: to go to England. Their problem is that they have neither the visa nor the ticket. A soldier alights from a train one day, and their lives change. He gives them a soldier\'s promise: He will take them to the land of their dreams. What follows is a hilarious and heartwarming tale of a perilous journey through the desert and the sea, but most crucially through the hinterlands of their mind.', 159, 'Shah Rukh Khan, Taapsee Pannu, Vikram Kochhar, Anil Grover, Boman Irani', '2023-12-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kPRb1mbVHGop0egQ7153y0lhzGL.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
