(3110, 'Pippa', 'Raja Menon', 'War, Drama', 'India', 'hi', 'The story of Captain Balram Singh Mehta of India’s 45 Cavalry regiment who, along with his siblings, fought on the eastern front during the Indo-Pakistani war of 1971. Named after the Russian amphibious war tank “PT-76”, which floats on water like an empty ‘pippa’ (tin) of ghee, the film traces Mehta\'s coming-of-age as he steps up to prove himself in a war to liberate Bangladesh.', 140, 'Ishaan Khatter, Mrunal Thakur, Priyanshu Painyuli, Soni Razdan, Soham Majumdar', '2023-11-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7bD664CWGigcjlT8wf2VR3KZCtK.jpg', '', '', '', 4.9, 0, 0),
