(3240, 'Pantasya ni Tami', 'Easy Ferrer', 'Drama, Romance', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Tami, with the help of her fubu photographer, Ken, sells sexy photos of herself. When she meets her fan, Gelo, who loves her as she is, she is torn whether to leave cosplaying or leave Gelo.', 114, 'Azi Acosta, Ali Asistio, Jiad Arroyo, Shiena Yu, Zia Zamora', '2024-01-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iej9tjZsnWbfn6BirakJAygfaEq.jpg', '', '', '', 4.5, 0, 0),
(3241, 'Brothers', 'Olivier Casas', 'Drama', 'France', 'fr', 'Two young brothers are abandoned by their mother during summer of 1948, they run into the forest and survive there for seven years.', 105, 'Mathieu Kassovitz, Yvan Attal, Anaïs Parello, Cécile Morel, Alma Jodorowsky', '2024-04-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5FmRJCoCmPWxZhJ0gE6vwSzx4pP.jpg', 'Sundance Film Festival - Audience Award – Best Foreign Feature Film', 'Locus Award for Best Short Story, Jameson People\'s Choice Award for Best Actress, European Film Award for Best Composer, European Film Award for Best Screenwriter, European Film Award for Best Actor, Jameson People\'s Choice Award for Best Actor, European Film Award for Best Director, European Film Award for Best Film, European Film Award for Best Actress, International Submission to the Academy Awards, Locus Award for Best Short Story', '18th European Film Awards, 22nd European Film Awards', 7.099, 0, 0),
(3242, 'La Chimera', 'Alice Rohrwacher', 'Drama, Fantasy, Comedy', 'France, Italy, Switzerland, Turkey', 'it', 'Just out of jail, rumpled English archaeologist Arthur reconnects with his wayward crew of tombaroli accomplices – a happy-go-lucky collective of itinerant grave-robbers who survive by looting Etruscan tombs and fencing the ancient treasures they dig up.', 131, 'Josh O\'Connor, Carol Duarte, Alba Rohrwacher, Isabella Rossellini, Vincenzo Nemolato', '2023-10-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lDaUha09CumsoSAt9MIRbS9WBNH.jpg', '', '', '', 7.3, 0, 0),
(3243, 'Scooby-Doo! and Krypto, Too!', 'Cecilia Aranovich', 'Animation, Family, Mystery, Fantasy, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'When the Justice League goes missing and villains overrun Metropolis, there\'s only one team that can solve this mystery: Scooby-Doo and the gang! But wait, there\'s a new dog in town – Krypto – Superman\'s Superdog with Super Powers. Mystery Inc. will need all the help it can get when phantoms menace the Justice League\'s headquarters.', 79, 'Frank Welker, Grey DeLisle, Matthew Lillard, Kate Micucci, P.J. Byrne', '2023-09-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kllOhDl3DyApQZ78pffMH1C2ZIn.jpg', '', '', '', 7.6, 0, 0),
(3244, 'Locked In', 'Nour Wazzi', 'Thriller', 'United Kingdom', 'en', 'A kindly nurse tries to unlock the secrets of a coma patient\'s injuries — and discovers the bitter rivalry, infidelity, betrayal and murder behind them.', 96, 'Famke Janssen, Rose Williams, Alex Hassell, Finn Cole, Anna Friel', '2023-11-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/blQaj6biyBMLo34cuFKKwbgjIBz.jpg', '', '', '', 5.313, 0, 0),
(3245, 'Richard the Stork and the Mystery of the Great Jewel', 'Mette Tange', 'Animation, Adventure, Comedy, Family', 'Belgium, Germany, Norway', 'en', 'Richard, a sparrow adopted by a stork family, is wintering at the Great Lake in Northern Africa. When he realises that he won’t be the one to lead his flock back North, Richard decides to travel on his own and crosses paths with Samia and her sparrow flock, who are being held captive by evil marabous under the control of greedy peacock Zamano. The only chance of freedom for the sparrows is to solve a riddle and find the Great Jewel, which will call upon teamwork, trust and most of all- spork (sparrow + stork) skills.', 84, 'Jonathan Failla, Jeffrey Hylton, Dulcie Smart, Erik Hansen, Mala Ghedia', '2023-03-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oaWFUwAI9KMFN6w02wiI8crPrga.jpg', '', '', '', 6.7, 0, 0),
(3246, 'Good One', 'India Donaldson', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'On a weekend backpacking trip in the Catskills, 17-year-old Sam contends with the competing egos of her father and his oldest friend.', 90, 'Lily Collias, James Le Gros, Danny McCarthy, Sumaya Bouhbal, Diana Irvine', '2024-08-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dd5FO4vMKDXrvf81XJGAle0Zba1.jpg', '', '', '', 6.333, 0, 0),
(3247, 'Reality+', 'Coralie Fargeat', 'Science Fiction', 'France', 'fr', 'Vincent, a young Parisian uncomfortable with his appearance, installs a brain chip named Reality+ which allows users to see themselves and fellow users with their dream body. However, Reality+ only works over 12-hour intervals, proving infuriating for Vincent as he falls for Stella, another user.', 22, 'Vincent Colombe, Aurélien Muller, Vanessa Hessler, Aurélia Poirier, Samuel Trépanier', '2025-01-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sm2iLVqpik0EBC8KlIzxgx8Jnme.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(3248, 'Marvel Studios Assembled: The Making of Deadpool & Wolverine', 'Brad Baruh', 'Documentary', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Hugh Jackman, Ryan Reynolds, and director Shawn Levy sit down and spill the proverbial beans about how \"Deadpool & Wolverine\" was conceived, carried to term, and then birthed.', 59, 'Shawn Levy, Ryan Reynolds, Kevin Feige, Hugh Jackman, Wendy Jacobson', '2024-11-12', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3dQyDFxTY6o3v67ncYCExog6aPH.jpg', '', '', '', 6.8, 0, 0),
(3249, 'Bihter: A Forbidden Passion', 'Mehmet Binay', 'Drama, Romance', 'Turkey', 'tr', 'Bihter, who is desperate for love, sees Adnan, a wealthy and respected older guy, as a way out of the stereotype that society and her materialistic mother have given her. But she soon discovers that she is not satisfied with his attention and has other needs.', 113, 'Farah Zeynep Abdullah, Boran Kuzum, Osman Sonant, Hande Ataizi, Helin Kandemir', '2023-11-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/80LYrmrs3EcW0hj9aXAwglmXtJF.jpg', '', '', '', 5.1, 0, 0),
(3250, 'Next Goal Wins', 'Taika Waititi', 'Comedy, Drama', 'New Zealand, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'Dutch coach Thomas Rongen attempts the nearly impossible task of turning the American Samoa soccer team from perennial losers into winners.', 104, 'Michael Fassbender, Oscar Kightley, Kaimana, David Fane, Rachel House', '2023-11-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xTQCL1zGugIck8MgvJ2lXSrxENR.jpg', '', '', '', 6.4, 0, 0),
(3251, 'Fear', 'Deon Taylor', 'Horror, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An author\'s celebration with friends at a woodland cabin takes a terrifying turn when an airborne virus emerges at the same time supernatural forces target the group.', 98, 'Joseph Sikora, Andrew Bachelor, Annie Ilonzeh, Ruby Modine, Iddo Goldberg', '2023-01-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/asCLy4s7HYP3zSRlLP4Qgme5L0A.jpg', '', 'International Submission to the Academy Awards', '', 5.3, 0, 0),
(3252, 'Lisa Frankenstein', 'Zelda Williams', 'Comedy, Horror, Romance', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In 1989, a misunderstood teenager has a high school crush — who just happens to be a handsome corpse! After a set of playfully horrific circumstances bring him back to life, the two embark on a murderous journey to find love, happiness…and a few missing body parts along the way.', 102, 'Kathryn Newton, Cole Sprouse, Liza Soberano, Henry Eikenberry, Joe Chrest', '2024-02-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jAW7ZdIm4HLKB3g15uMOWYNdU8r.jpg', '', '', '', 6.327, 0, 0),
