(3321, 'Sympathy for the Devil', 'Yuval Adler', 'Thriller, Action', 'United States of America', 'en', 'After being forced to drive a mysterious passenger at gunpoint, a man finds himself in a high-stakes game of cat and mouse where it becomes clear that not everything is as it seems.', 90, 'Joel Kinnaman, Nicolas Cage, Alexis Zollicoffer, Cameron Lee Price, Oliver McCallum', '2023-07-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/afGdVMa80LMs6ibLP22CwM5uI4e.jpg', 'Q123472301', '', '', 5.965, 0, 0),
(3322, 'Totto-chan: The Little Girl at the Window', 'Shinnosuke Yakuwa', 'Animation, Drama, Family', 'Japan', 'ja', 'This engaging series of childhood recollections tells of an unconventional school in Tokyo during World War II that combined learning with fun, freedom, and love. The school had old railroad cars for classrooms and was run by an extraordinary man – its founder and headmaster, Sōsaku Kobayashi – who deeply valued children\'s independence, and who was a firm believer in freedom of expression and activity.', 114, 'Liliana Ohno, Koji Yakusho, Shun Oguri, Anne Watanabe, Karen Takizawa', '2023-12-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/65krUIOaBNkLa4t3wiKmt76hjBq.jpg', 'Paul Grimault Award', '', '', 7.9, 0, 0),
(3323, 'Green and Gold', 'Anders Lindwall', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'With American farms disappearing, a fourth-generation dairy farmer and his granddaughter fight to preserve their way of life. Facing foreclosure, they wager everything on their beloved Green Bay Packers in a Hail-Mary effort to save their little chunk of dirt.', 95, 'Craig T. Nelson, Brandon Sklenar, M. Emmet Walsh, Madison Lawlor, Charlie Berens', '2025-01-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5emph2FJDFsIGlOEyxCCdjqrNX2.jpg', '', '', '', 5, 0, 0),
(3324, 'Exchange Wife 2', 'Lee Si-young', 'Romance, Drama', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Kyeong-soo, an art dealer who specializes in painting, goes to evaluate the requested painting and accidentally damages it. Chang-in, the owner of the painting, suggests one thing from Kyung-soo, who was at a loss.', 89, 'Lee Soo, Do Hee, Jo Wan-jin, Min Jo-ah, Sang Woo', '2023-02-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9ZzZUuMNoCRdPpNrSKYZSvRzc5w.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3325, 'Katie\'s Mom', 'Tyrrell Shaffner', 'Comedy, Drama, Romance', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A recent divorcee\'s holiday celebration with her adult children derails when she falls for her daughter\'s charming new boyfriend. A comedy influenced by \"The Graduate,\" told from the perspective of a protagonist inspired by Mrs. Robinson.', 111, 'Dina Meyer, Aaron Dominguez, Julia Tolchin, Colin Bates, Jason Wiles', '2023-07-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mhQTMw2YyGqsMR1DLNxIZY2516j.jpg', '', '', '', 3.778, 0, 0),
(3326, 'Retro', 'Karthik Subbaraj', 'Romance, Action, Drama, Crime', 'India', 'ta', 'In the 1990s, the son of a dreaded gangster attempts to leave his violent life for his true love.', 0, 'Suriya, Pooja Hegde, Jayaram, Joju George, Nandita Das', '2025-05-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bN5r5RX4ynZm50qhDGWdTRgI1Yv.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3327, 'Conquer: Lahad Datu', 'Zulkarnain Azhar', 'War, History, Thriller, Action, Crime, Drama', 'Malaysia', 'ms', 'When hundreds of militants invade eastern Sabah, the Royal Malaysia Police sends in an elite force to respond to the incursion.', 120, 'Syafiq Kyle, Kamal Adli, Fikry Ibrahim, Anding Indrawani, Eman Manan', '2024-08-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jpyuq6ClXoTyeNnjRKO5iI6v4SM.jpg', '', '', '', 8.1, 0, 0),
(3328, '¿Quieres ser mi hijo?', 'Ihtzi Hurtado', 'Comedy, Romance', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Lu, a conformist woman in her forties, learns that her 15-year partner has been having extramarital affairs. Starting from scratch, she gets involved in an unexpected relationship with a young womanizer.', 100, 'Ludwika Paleta, Juanpa Zurita, Hernán Mendoza, Harold Azuara, Agustín Arana', '2023-09-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9GuvODahvuFqdhuZ16aBLR4UJoP.jpg', '', '', '', 8.576, 0, 0),
(3329, 'The Magician\'s Elephant', 'Wendy Rogers', 'Animation, Adventure, Family, Fantasy, Comedy', 'Australia, United States of America', 'en', 'Peter is searching for his long-lost sister when he crosses paths with a fortune teller in the market square. His only question is: is his sister still alive? The answer, that he must find a mysterious elephant and the magician who will conjure it, sets Peter off on a journey to complete three seemingly impossible tasks that will change the face of his town forever.', 99, 'Noah Jupe, Mandy Patinkin, Brian Tyree Henry, Natasia Demetriou, Sian Clifford', '2023-03-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cAoAgzOCxSytYBqqCQulhXNR3LB.jpg', '', '', '', 6.91, 0, 0),
(3330, 'Batman: The Doom That Came to Gotham', 'Sam Liu', 'Animation, Fantasy, Action, Mystery', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Explorer Bruce Wayne accidentally unleashes an ancient evil, and returns to Gotham after being away for two decades. There, Batman battles Lovecraftian supernatural forces and encounters allies and enemies such as Green Arrow, Ra\'s al Ghul, Mr. Freeze, Killer Croc, Two-Face and James Gordon.', 86, 'David Giuntoli, Patrick Fabian, John DiMaggio, Karan Brar, Navid Negahban', '2023-03-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sKWN5ZzDxnfVixUavs09HfBCCA3.jpg', '', '', '', 6.643, 0, 0),
(3331, 'Justicia para Diego', 'Jorge Valcarcel', 'TV Movie, Documentary', 'Spain', 'es', '', 0, '', '2025-01-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eKQqBFIXiFy34mWeEd2YvVFzwXc.jpg', '', '', '', 9, 0, 0),
(3332, 'Jesus Revolution', 'Brent McCorkle', 'Drama, History', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In the 1970s, aimless teenager Greg Laurie searches for all the right things in all the wrong places until he meets Lonnie Frisbee, a charismatic hippie/street preacher. Together with local pastor Chuck Smith, they open the doors of a languishing church to an unexpected revival.', 120, 'Joel Courtney, Kelsey Grammer, Jonathan Roumie, Kimberly Williams-Paisley, Anna Grace Barlow', '2023-02-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A3qqrl8lJvlpRCwkbUEADXzVaDC.jpg', '', '', '', 6.652, 0, 0),
(3333, 'Kingdom III: The Flame of Destiny', 'Shinsuke Sato', 'Action, Adventure, War', 'Japan', 'ja', 'To defend their kingdom against a sudden invasion, a mighty general returns to the battlefield alongside a war orphan, now grown up, who dreams of glory.', 129, 'Kento Yamazaki, Ryo Yoshizawa, Kanna Hashimoto, Nana Seino, Amane Okayama', '2023-07-28', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7cIqNt2YPK1nCf904NFISEScCzk.jpg', '', '', '', 7.516, 0, 0),
(3334, 'La Cocina', 'Alonso Ruizpalacios', 'Comedy, Drama', 'Mexico, Sweden, United States of America', 'es', 'It is the lunchtime rush at The Grill, a New York tourist trap that serves thousands of customers on a regular Friday like today. Money has gone missing from the till and all the workers are being questioned.', 139, 'Raúl Briones, Rooney Mara, Anna Díaz, Motell Gyn Foster, Laura Gómez', '2024-10-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2zhdUl8KWK8QGATbWTRGexYthZT.jpg', '', '', '', 6.771, 0, 0),
(3335, 'Rascal Does Not Dream of a Sister Venturing Out', 'Soichi Masui', 'Animation, Drama, Fantasy', 'Japan', 'ja', 'After a draining December, Sakuta is quickly nearing the end of his second year of high school. Since Mai is a third-year student, they don\'t have much time left together before graduation rolls around. Meanwhile, his sister, Kaede, is slowly but steadily venturing outdoors again. Just as she begins to find her footing, she announces her most ambitious goal yet—attending her brother\'s high school! Sakuta knows better than anyone how difficult this will be for Kaede, and he\'s ready to support her however he can. He\'s just not sure if that\'s what\'s best for her...or what she really wants...', 74, 'Kaito Ishikawa, Asami Seto, Yurika Kubo, Nao Toyama, Atsumi Tanezaki', '2023-06-23', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o3Yc0plKnzpck0SM3rQLjWBHel8.jpg', '', '', '', 7.531, 0, 0),
(3336, 'Come Out Fighting', 'Steven Luke', 'War, Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In WWII, a squad of U.S. African-American soldiers are sent on a rescue mission behind enemy lines to locate their lost commanding officer and a downed fighter pilot.', 86, 'Kellan Lutz, Dolph Lundgren, Aaron Courteau, Mike Dittmer, Vicellous Shannon', '2023-05-19', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sERwJxz0sqsbcUoTm66l9pI6HcH.jpg', '', '', '', 4.7, 0, 0),
(3337, 'Akaal: The Unconquered', 'Gippy Grewal', 'Action, History, Drama', 'India', 'pa', 'Set in 1840s Punjab, Sardar Akaal Singh and his village as they face a vengeful assault by Jangi Jahan and his forces after the death of Maharaja Ranjeet Singh. Amid broken truces and escalating tensions, the fearless Sardars must rise against overwhelming odds to protect their land. Will they prevail against this formidable foe?', 137, 'Apindereep Singh, Gippy Grewal, Nimrat Khaira, Nikitin Dheer, Gurpreet Ghuggi', '2025-04-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pzf5rPLoE5DdYkcZlvYbrH554rE.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 4),
(3338, 'Almarhum', 'Adhe Dharmastriya', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Indonesia', 'id', 'Mr. Mulwanto\'s tragic death on Tuesday Kliwon was the beginning of disaster for the Nuri family. It is said that anyone who dies on that day will invite their family members to join them in dying. The families left behind were also asked to undergo a series of rituals to prevent this. Wisesa, the eldest child who works as a doctor, rejected the ritual because it was unreasonable and chose to accompany his mother who was still devastated. However, a strange and terrible incident that happened to Nuri and her sister, Yanda, forced them to find out about the truth behind the myths and rituals.', 103, 'Safira Ratu Sofya, Alzi Markers, Rukman Rosadi, Nova Eliza, Dimas Aditya', '2025-01-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bHmtY7LUn27DGaQlZLKhROdrLrh.jpg', '', '', '', 5, 0, 0),
(3339, 'The Surfer', 'Lorcan Finnegan', 'Thriller, Drama', 'Australia, Ireland, United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'A man returns to the idyllic beach of his childhood to surf with his son. But his desire to hit the waves is thwarted by a group of locals whose mantra is \"don\'t live here, don\'t surf here.\" Humiliated and angry, the man is drawn into a conflict that keeps rising in concert with the punishing heat of the summer and pushes him to his breaking point.', 100, 'Nicolas Cage, Julian McMahon, Justin Rosniak, Alexander Bertrand, Rahel Romahn', '2025-04-03', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zYClQYdiGADZ9rFKx4PjfnUO4XQ.jpg', '', 'Locus Award for Best Novella', '', 8, 0, 0),
