(3384, 'Problemista', 'Julio Torres', 'Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Alejandro is an aspiring toy designer from El Salvador, struggling to bring his unusual ideas to life in New York City. As time on his work visa runs out, a job assisting an erratic art-world outcast becomes his only hope to stay in the country and realize his dream.', 104, 'Julio Torres, Tilda Swinton, RZA, Isabella Rossellini, Catalina Saavedra', '2024-03-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8R5s0optPNlTncP876bK8gWGkRK.jpg', '', '', '', 6.752, 0, 0),
(3385, 'Out of Season', 'Stéphane Brizé', 'Drama', 'France', 'fr', 'Mathieu lives in Paris, Alice in a small seaside resort in Western France. He is a famous actor, about to turn fifty. She is a piano teacher in her forties. They were in love fifteen years ago, then separated. Time has passed. They each went their ways and slowly healed. When Mathieu goes try to overcome his melancholia in a thermal spa, he stumbles upon Alice.', 116, 'Guillaume Canet, Alba Rohrwacher, Sharif Andoura, Emmy Boissard Paumelle, Marie Drucker', '2024-03-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nLbFUAhAKJJRACzSQ1pQoeQkarR.jpg', '', '', '', 6.475, 0, 0),
