(3589, 'Bureau 749', 'Lu Chuan', 'Action, Adventure, Science Fiction', 'China', 'zh', 'A traumatized young man with physical abnormalities is forced to join a mysterious bureau to confront a disaster spreading across the earth caused by an unknown creature. He embarks on an adventure uncovering mysteries about his life.', 123, 'Karry Wang, Miao Miao, Ryan Zheng, Ren Min, Xin Baiqing', '2024-10-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/flykCMw22y6yv8vKnBjmsW3pneo.jpg', '', '', '', 3.2, 0, 0),
