(3683, 'Exorcism Chronicles: The Beginning', 'Kim Dong-chul', 'Animation, Fantasy, Horror, Action', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'A doctor-turned-priest, Father Park was excommunicated for performing exorcisms by a church that refused to believe in the supernatural beings preying on the innocent. When his long-time friend, a monk from a secretive and magic-wielding temple, calls upon him to protect a naïve yet powerful child from his corrupt master, Father Park must face his inner demons to rescue the boy or risk repeating the same tragedy that he took up the cross to prevent.', 86, 'Choi Han, Nam Doh-hyeong, Jung Yoo-jung, Kim Yeon-woo, Hong Seung-hyo', '2025-02-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j1avSbVgXaEFw6QfPMTsnmH8bQf.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3684, 'Weapons', 'Zach Cregger', 'Horror, Mystery', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An interrelated, multistory horror epic that revolves around the disappearance of high schoolers in a small town.', 128, 'Josh Brolin, Julia Garner, June Diane Raphael, Austin Abrams, Alden Ehrenreich', '2025-08-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l2RlrXnc5QRmUf6WeNF22tTZSzt.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3685, 'Cora', 'Sonny Laguna', 'Science Fiction, Thriller, Horror', 'Sweden', 'en', 'Cora is set decades into the future, after a deadly mist has covered earth, effectively wiping out most of humanity. Now, we follow Cora, a woman working for an organization trying to reverse the effects of the apocalypse.', 100, 'Thomas Lennon, Andreas Rylander, Felicia Rylander, Patrick Saxe, Alec Toselli', '2024-05-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jBi5ZHxoRwjlPzPlBTMKRopC76i.jpg', '', '', '', 5.308, 0, 0),
(3686, 'The Master and Margarita', 'Michael Lockshin', 'Drama, Fantasy', 'Russia', 'ru', 'Moscow, 1930s. A prominent writer\'s works are suddenly censored by the Soviet state and the premiere of his theatrical play about Pontius Pilate is canceled. He\'s kicked out of the Soviet Writer\'s Union, and quickly turns into an outcast with no means to survive.  Inspired by Margarita - his lover, he begins working on a new novel in which all the characters are satirically reinterpreted from his life. The novel\'s central character is Woland - a mystical dark force who visits Moscow to revenge all those who caused the writer\'s downfall.  As the Master sinks himself deeper and deeper into his novel, adding himself and Margarita as characters, he gradually stops noticing as the border between reality and his imagination fades away.', 157, 'Yevgeni Tsyganov, Yuliya Snigir, August Diehl, Yuri Kolokolnikov, Leonid Yarmolnik', '2024-01-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jw172VAlwfYtWNWvhVrXZPW3jGT.jpg', 'Le Monde\'s 100 Books of the Century', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(3687, 'A Part of You', 'Sigge Eklund', 'Drama', 'Sweden', 'sv', 'A teenager struggles to pick up the pieces of her shattered world in this emotional and bittersweet coming-of-age drama about those who are left behind.', 101, 'Felicia Truedsson, Edvin Ryding, Zara Larsson, Ida Engvoll, Mustafa Al-Mashhadani', '2024-05-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rv3FLJ4kLoeFpL6sLSB3tCWLO9f.jpg', '', '', '', 6.701, 0, 0),
(3688, 'The Braid', 'Laetitia Colombani', 'Drama, Comedy', 'Belgium, Canada, France, Italy', 'en', 'India. Smita is an untouchable. She dreams of seeing her daughter escape her miserable condition and enter school. Italy. Giulia works in her father’s workshop. When he has an accident, she discovers that the family business is ruined. Canada. Sarah, a successful lawyer, is about to be promoted to the head of her firm when she learns that she is ill. Three lives, three women, three continents. Three battles to fight. Although they don’t know each other, Smita, Giulia and Sarah are unknowingly linked by their most intimate and singular bond.', 121, 'Kim Raver, Fotinì Peluso, Mia Maelzer, Katharine King So, Avi Nash', '2023-11-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tJnYgLeefl3ebgB5mHwSstSRreF.jpg', '', '', '', 7.683, 0, 0),
(3689, 'Breaking Point', 'Yvan Attal', 'Thriller, Crime', 'France', 'fr', 'Mathieu owes everything to his friend Vincent : his house, his job, and even his life, ten years ago. With their wives, they are an inseparable quartet, and live the easy life on the French Riviera. But Mathieu discovers Vincent is cheating on his wife.', 84, 'Yvan Attal, Maïwenn, Guillaume Canet, Marie-Josée Croze, Alma Jodorowsky', '2024-01-24', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kMfzNO3lpATB5mxc8D06PR9T2nO.jpg', '', '', '', 5.793, 0, 0),
(3690, 'Rob Peace', 'Chiwetel Ejiofor', 'Drama, History', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An underprivileged, gifted young black man from Newark reaches Yale University, only for shadows and injustices from his past to threaten his future.', 120, 'Jay Will, Mary J. Blige, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Camila Cabello, Michael Kelly', '2024-08-02', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1BwKbTidW5QaEKb1pVY3p4u9cVg.jpg', '', '', '', 6.705, 0, 0),
(3691, 'It Lives Inside', 'Bishal Dutta', 'Horror, Mystery', 'Canada, United States of America', 'en', 'Desperate to fit in at school, Sam rejects her East Indian culture and family to be like everyone else. However, when a mythological demonic spirit latches onto her former best friend, she must come to terms with her heritage to defeat it.', 99, 'Megan Suri, Neeru Bajwa, Mohana Krishnan, Betty Gabriel, Vik Sahay', '2023-09-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/73gIfV8gDwkVgUrFDzt4TfZC9Zc.jpg', '', '', '', 5.706, 0, 0),
(3692, 'Night Train', 'Shane Stanley', 'Action, Thriller, Crime', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Mother Holly McCord is driven to extremes to save the life of her young son. Even if it means hauling black market drugs in her souped-up truck, with the Feds in hot pursuit. With two bounties on her head and her son’s life on the line, Holly climbs behind the wheel of “Night Train,” ready to outrun, out gun, and outlast them all.', 96, 'Danielle C. Ryan, Diora Baird, Joe Lando, Abraham Benrubi, Joseph D. Reitman', '2023-01-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gZFSc3BqUyAvuakHSs7qaWJZnGN.jpg', '', '', '', 6.075, 0, 0),
(3693, 'Origin', 'Ava DuVernay', 'Drama', 'United States of America', 'en', 'While investigating the global phenomenon of caste and its dark influence on society, a journalist faces unfathomable personal loss and uncovers the beauty of human resilience.', 141, 'Aunjanue Ellis-Taylor, Niecy Nash-Betts, Jon Bernthal, Emily Yancy, Finn Wittrock', '2023-12-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dY0m1fypdNPp61kcmLdsk7KIR7C.jpg', '', 'Locus Award for Best Science Fiction Novel, Kurd Lasswitz Award for Best Foreign Work', '', 6.586, 0, 0),
(3694, 'What You Wish For', 'Nicholas Tomnay', 'Thriller, Horror', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A talented chef with gambling woes flees to a Latin American villa to visit an old friend who appears to be living an extraordinary life as a private chef. Envy soon turns to greed and then to something deeply unsettling for the chef when he assumes his friend\'s life and discovers the motives of his mysterious clients.', 102, 'Nick Stahl, Tamsin Topolski, Randy Vasquez, Penelope Mitchell, Brian Groh', '2025-01-09', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9T6ww265pozXkNPKl26hRhIpbxt.jpg', '', '', '', 6.556, 0, 0),
(3695, 'Kasalo', 'Howard Yambao', 'Drama, Romance', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Two strangers meet through a ride-sharing app and find themselves sharing more than what\'s expected. Both having problems with their respective marital lives, they find comfort in each other\'s company.', 48, 'Albie Casiño, Vern Kaye, Rash Flores, Mia Cruz', '2024-03-26', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aQkunFEjLqm4CDPtkjjXfFxwkuj.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 0),
(3696, 'Confidential Informant', 'Michael Oblowitz', 'Thriller, Action, Mystery, Crime', 'United States of America', 'en', 'During a crack epidemic two narcotics agents hunting for a cop killer. Hoping for leads, Moran and Thorton pay off a junkie informant. To provide for his wife and son, Moran involves the stool pigeon in a deadly scheme. This causes the partners to come under the scrutiny of a suspicious internal affairs agent.', 88, 'Dominic Purcell, Kate Bosworth, Mel Gibson, Arielle Raycene, Nick Stahl', '2023-06-27', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p3MqxGqMdq4eqzWN6H7ugEdYv1W.jpg', '', '', '', 5.8, 0, 0),
(3697, 'The Good Mother', 'Miles Joris-Peyrafitte', 'Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A journalist and her son\'s pregnant girlfriend attempt to track down those responsible for the murder of her estranged son. Together, they confront a world of drugs and corruption in the underbelly of their small city in upstate New York, where they uncover an even darker secret.', 90, 'Hilary Swank, Olivia Cooke, Jack Reynor, Dilone, Hopper Penn', '2023-08-31', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/whwxm3JUXNiGvqZWcRC6g6kAHm1.jpg', '', '', '', 4.922, 0, 0),
(3698, 'The American Society of Magical Negroes', 'Kobi Libii', 'Fantasy, Comedy', 'United States of America', 'en', 'A young man, Aren, is recruited into a secret society of magical Black people who dedicate their lives to a cause of utmost importance: making white people’s lives easier.', 105, 'Justice Smith, David Alan Grier, An-Li Bogan, Drew Tarver, Michaela Watkins', '2024-03-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/czV7JRPPPGk9bqUsnJuJUYn34mM.jpg', '', '', '', 4.816, 0, 0),
(3699, 'Flora and Son', 'John Carney', 'Music, Comedy, Drama', 'Ireland, United States of America', 'en', 'Single mom Flora is at a loss about what to do with her rebellious teenage son, Max. Her efforts to keep him out of trouble lead to a beat-up acoustic guitar, a washed-up LA musician, and harmony for this frayed Dublin family.', 97, 'Eve Hewson, Orén Kinlan, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Jack Reynor, Marcella Plunkett', '2023-09-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pq2p8ovf8PZps2HafvJaLrZK8gS.jpg', '', '', '', 6.914, 0, 0),
(3700, 'Janet Planet', 'Annie Baker', 'Drama', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'In rural Western Massachusetts, 11-year-old Lacy spends the summer of 1991 at home, enthralled by her own imagination and the attention of her mother, Janet. As the months pass, three visitors enter their orbit, all captivated by Janet.', 113, 'Julianne Nicholson, Zoe Ziegler, Will Patton, Sophie Okonedo, Elias Koteas', '2024-06-21', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qoKeP2PmDL6pshodCv6czlMZD3u.jpg', '', '', '', 6, 0, 0),
(3701, 'This Is Me…Now', 'Dave Meyers', 'Drama, Music', 'United States of America', 'en', 'An intimate, fantastical and narrative-driven reflection of Jennifer Lopez\'s journey of self-healing and self-love in an immersive world where music and visuals intertwine, revealing the challenges faced and the triumphs achieved.', 66, 'Jennifer Lopez, Ben Affleck, Idaliz Christian, Fat Joe, Matthew Law', '2024-02-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nEMSjYpT0B7uxNwu1kEU8fTycs4.jpg', '', '', '', 5.3, 0, 0),
(3702, 'Jagun Jagun', 'Adebayo Tijani', 'Action, Drama', 'Nigeria', 'yo', 'A young man determined to become a powerful warrior joins an elite army, encountering the wrath of a maniacal warlord and the love of a fierce woman.', 134, 'Femi Adebayo, Lateef Adedimeji, Odunlade Adekola, Ibrahim Yekini Itele, Bukunmi Oluwashina', '2023-08-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uPZtE5DSo9VIX2N3NPtmTayhgP8.jpg', '', '', '', 6.6, 0, 0),
(3703, 'Sons of the Neon Night', 'Juno Mak', 'Action, Crime, Thriller', 'Hong Kong', 'cn', 'A detective goes against the successor to a drug-trafficking crime syndicate, who aspires for a society free of drugs by orchestrating anarchy in Hong Kong.', 0, 'Takeshi Kaneshiro, Sean Lau, Tony Leung Ka-Fai, Louis Koo, Gao Yuanyuan', '2025-05-13', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mini5t3eavhgv0dDgGl9sWxnoQq.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3704, 'The Roommate', 'Pedro Pablo Ibarra', 'Comedy', 'Mexico', 'es', 'Vivi is a young writer who is forced to find a roommate to pay the mortgage on her apartment. What she does not suspect is that Roy, the supposed perfect partner she found, has a peculiar lifestyle: he never pays rent.', 99, 'Fiona Palomo, José Eduardo Derbez, Giuseppe Gamba, Bárbara de Regil, Maite Perroni', '2024-01-18', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zaRzz2BxjxIVb7ja0gSedj1Hn1E.jpg', '', '', '', 7.626, 0, 0),
(3705, 'Hell Hole', 'John Adams', 'Horror, Science Fiction', 'United States of America', 'en', 'Far away, in the desolate Serbian wilderness, a U.S.-led fracking crew uncover a dormant monster gestating inside a centuries-old French soldier. Now awakened and exposed in its most dangerously fragile state, it tears through the men on the grounds in search of a new womb.', 92, 'Toby Poser, John Adams, Max Portman, Anders Hove, Olivera Peruničić', '2024-07-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/icqY4HTfrCwR4J8NqvcnGsKCp6S.jpg', '', '', '', 5.281, 0, 0),
(3706, 'Things Will Be Different', 'Michael Felker', 'Horror, Science Fiction, Thriller', 'United States of America', 'en', 'In order to escape the police after a robbery, two estranged siblings lay low in a metaphysical farmhouse that hides them away in a different time. There they reckon with a mysterious force that pushes their familial bonds to unnatural breaking points.', 102, 'Adam David Thompson, Riley Dandy, Chloe Skoczen, Justin Benson, Sarah Bolger', '2024-10-04', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8vpYPns2SjbmgqkE72e69knRMGY.jpg', '', '', '', 5.713, 0, 0),
(3707, 'Gaami', 'Vidyadhar Kagita', 'Adventure, Thriller, Science Fiction, Fantasy', 'India', 'te', 'Shankar is a wounded, reluctant and reclusive aghora on a quest to find the cure for his very rare human condition – the one that will be cured, only when he can confront and conquers the haunting ironical questions of his life.', 147, 'Vishwak Sen, Mohammad Samad, Harika Pedada, Chandini Chowdary, Abhinaya', '2024-03-08', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nruKcKWmuP7ce7sBGBNViHJaZrZ.jpg', '', '', '', 6.6, 0, 0),
(3708, 'Sound of the Divine Bell', 'Hwang Ji-eun', 'Horror, Mystery', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Susanna is about to become a nun in three days, and she finds herself sharing a room with an older nun, Teresa. This situation leaves her feeling confused and uncertain about whether she can successfully go through with the profession rite.', 29, 'Oh Woo-ri, Lee Joo-sil, Nam Kee-ae, Nam Myung-ryeol', '2024-07-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rdIymBG32CjzpknZNQLm9YfkSLg.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3709, 'The Inventor', 'Pierre-Luc Granjon', 'Animation, Drama, Family, History', 'France, Ireland, United States of America', 'en', 'The insatiably curious and headstrong inventor Leonardo da Vinci leaves Italy to join the French court, where he can experiment freely, inventing flying contraptions, incredible machines, and study the human body. There, joined in his adventure by the audacious princess Marguerite, Leonardo will uncover the answer to the ultimate question – \"What is the meaning of it all?\"', 92, 'Stephen Fry, Daisy Ridley, Marion Cotillard, Matt Berry, Natalie Palamides', '2023-09-15', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/489kEvaylSuutUJ0GVVs6gUmirB.jpg', '', '', '', 6.3, 0, 0),
(3710, 'Sapta Sagaradaache Ello – Side A', 'Hemanth M. Rao', 'Romance, Drama', 'India', 'kn', 'In the heart of \'Sapta Sagaradaache Ello’ (Somewhere Beyond the Seven Seas), resides an ardent love story between Manu and Priya. Set in 2010, the couple hails from a middle-class background. Circumstances land Manu in jail, putting his relationship with Priya in jeopardy.', 140, 'Rakshit Shetty, Rukmini Vasanth, Sharath Lohitashwa, Ramesh Indira, Pavitra Lokesh', '2023-09-01', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qjvSMN5dhSh7cymjj6if2aJ4ejW.jpg', '', '', '', 8.2, 0, 0),
(3711, 'The Siege', 'Brad Watson', 'Action, Thriller', 'United Kingdom, United States of America', 'en', 'International assassin Walker is compromised during a mission and sent to a reassignment center for a new identity. During his stay at the facility, a ruthless assault team storms the compound searching for someone their boss has lost. Walker begrudgingly falls in with skilled hitwoman Elda and her mysterious ward Juliet in order to survive the night.', 97, 'Daniel Stisen, Lauren Okadigbo, Yennis Cheung, Byron Gibson, Steven Blades', '2023-03-10', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hVh4hMzkXNLnScudbid6hDvjMPk.jpg', '', '', '', 5.214, 0, 0),
(3712, 'Touch', 'Baltasar Kormákur', 'Romance, Drama', 'Iceland, United Kingdom', 'is', 'Soon after the break of the pandemic and realizing that his clock is ticking, Kristofer gets the urge to embark on a journey to try to find out what really happened when his Japanese girlfriend mysteriously vanished without a trace from London fifty years earlier.', 121, 'Egill Ólafsson, Kōki, Pálmi Kormákur Baltasarsson, Masahiro Motoki, Yōko Narahashi', '2024-05-29', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yNXfG1CBVzffksd2EkEpJ9NXFOT.jpg', '', '', '', 7.5, 0, 0),
(3713, 'A Great Friend', 'Éric Besnard', 'Comedy', 'France', 'fr', 'Vincent is a famous successful entrepreneur. One day, a car breakdown on a mountain road temporarily interrupts his frantic lifestyle. Pierre, who lives apart from the modern world in the middle of sublime nature, comes to his aid and offers him his hospitality. The meeting between these two men, who are opposites will upset their respective beliefs and they will find themselves laughing. The question is...deep down, are they really each living the lives they want to live?', 95, 'Grégory Gadebois, Lambert Wilson, Marie Gillain, Betty Pierucci Berthoud, Magali Bonat', '2023-02-22', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/70GmOX3yhKETP4KzXmeH3OQOQ0h.jpg', '', '', '', 6.593, 0, 0),
(3714, 'A Lagos Love Story', 'Chinaza Onuzo', 'Drama, Romance', 'Nigeria', 'en', 'When she\'s hired to plan a huge festival in Lagos, Promise unexpectedly finds herself falling for the brash Afrobeats star at the center of it all.', 104, 'Mike Afolarin, Jemima Osunde, Susan Pwajok, Kalu Ikeagwu, Chimezie Imo', '2025-04-11', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8NsTGWJLxxsuUCyrNkY1NytlJGu.jpg', '', '', '', 5, 0, 0),
(3715, 'Hear Me: Our Summer', 'Cho Sun-ho', 'Romance, Drama', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'A job seeking dreamer Yong-jun works part-time at his parents\' lunch box house. Yeo-reum lives only to support for hearing-impaired swimmer sister. One day, Yong-jun meets Yeo-reum while delivering lunch boxes and falls in love at the first sight. Yeo-reum slowly opens her heart to warm-hearted Yong-jun.', 109, 'Hong Kyung, Roh Yoon-seo, Kim Min-ju, Jung Yong-Ju, Jeong Hye-young', '2024-11-06', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/i4VmtHRy4xRkxIRc1VihCnHXdFr.jpg', '', '', '', 7.7, 0, 0),
(3716, 'Couple Exchange', 'Jang Kwon', 'Romance', 'South Korea', 'ko', 'Nan-hee, who wants to enjoy her newlywed life, feels something wrong with her husband, Moo-yeong\'s body. No matter how much she tries to seduce him every night, Moo-yeong is unable to use his strength. One day, Nan-hee\'s high school classmate Yoo-na moves in next door. Nan-hee begins to heal Moo-yeong through Yoo-na\'s shocking suggestion.', 90, 'Min Jo-ah, Do Hee, Min Do-yoon, Sang Woo, Lee Soo', '2023-03-16', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7WFlsCBnVyVfJxZWprAkU4poCaJ.jpg', '', '', '', 9.5, 0, 0),
(3717, 'Bugaw', 'Yam Laranas', 'Drama, Thriller', 'Philippines', 'tl', 'Siblings Dolores and Isaac were known as the town\'s prostitutes But when a corrupt police officer holds them captive, they are forced to make a young girl named Lydia, the town\'s newest prostitute.', 90, 'Alexa Ocampo, Clifford Pusing, Ataska Mercado, Jay Manalo, MJ Cayabyab', '2023-07-07', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qAFj79V1KC8PVW6mfAnyI5dJI8v.jpg', '', '', '', 2, 0, 0),
(3718, '裏垢男子とAV男優どっちがエロい？素顔の美谷朱音を２人きりの空間でイカせまくる本気の生々ハメ撮り中出し', 'Desconocido', 'Documentary', 'Japan', 'ja', '', 0, 'Akari Mitani', '2025-02-25', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Do6kj4TBZs51jzHmmaoX7Z8iq1.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0),
(3719, 'LUPIN THE 3rd vs. CAT\'S EYE', 'Kobun Shizuno', 'Animation, Action, Adventure, Comedy, Crime', 'Japan', 'ja', 'Lupin III competes with the Kisugi sisters to steal a triptych of paintings that once belonged to their father, and which hold the key to a long-unsolved mystery.', 92, 'Kanichi Kurita, Akio Otsuka, Miyuki Sawashiro, Daisuke Namikawa, Koichi Yamadera', '2023-04-20', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t9XXivYtzap9TPNQ5CWskzh5agF.jpg', '', '', '', 6.2, 0, 0),
(3720, 'Influencer', 'Kurtis David Harder', 'Horror, Mystery, Thriller', 'Thailand, United States of America', 'en', 'While struggling on a solo backpacking trip in Thailand, social media influencer Madison meets CW, who travels with ease and shows her a more uninhibited way of living. But CW\'s interest in her takes a darker turn.', 92, 'Cassandra Naud, Emily Tennant, Rory J. Saper, Sara Canning, Paul Spurrier', '2023-05-18', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mtXV301BF7pqwvRjsWhQo6sD10F.jpg', '', '', '', 6.141, 0, 0),
